(38, 'NEWS What is Halloween? And How is Halloween Celebrated Today?', 'news-what-is-halloween-and-how-is-halloween-celebrated-today', 'Halloween.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Do you love Halloween? Of course, you do. Who doesn’t love Halloween? It is one of the most favorite cultural events around the globe. Surely, your childhood is full of those scary pranks and Halloween memories.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Even though we celebrate the day with the best effort, some of us don’t really know its origin. What is Halloween, where does it come from, or why do we even celebrate such a day! There are many questions like that.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Our review is to let you know the history behind Halloween and&nbsp;how we celebrate it today. Are you excited to learn about your favorite holiday? Let’s jump into the depth of history.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What is Halloween?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">So, what is Halloween? It is an easy question to understand. But, it is a little bit complex to answer. Probably, the day where we put on scary costumes and do horrible pranks on others! But, this is not the only thing we do. Treating others, joining in a party, and so many other things are there.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In short, Halloween is a day that we celebrate to enjoy dark fantasy. Although, this type of definition is a bit scary when most of the day we spend collecting and sharing lots of candies! Horror, dark fantasy, and this type of thing give us an amazing thrill! That’s why we love to watch horror movies, even if it steals our sleep. Halloween is the day when we enjoy those thrills to their best.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What Does the “Halloween” Word Mean?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Halloween comes from the Scottish All Hallows’ Eve. This means a Hallowed evening. It indicates the day before All Saints Day. As a reminder, the day we celebrate now is not similar to its origin. It is a day used to pray for the souls. Later in the 18th century, it became a popular day to enjoy like how we do nowadays.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3292 size-full\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Halloween-bb.jpg\" alt=\"Halloween Celebrated \" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Halloween-bb.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Halloween-bb-300x169.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Halloween-bb-768x432.jpg 768w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Halloween-bb-400x225.jpg 400w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Halloween-bb-600x338.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">When is Halloween?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Halloween in the USA is on 31st October. Although, there are restrictions in many countries. Even though this day is popular around the world, every country doesn’t celebrate this day. Some countries believe that this day welcomes a lot of bad habits, rituals, paranormal things that&nbsp;may increase the crime rate. So, this day is not a global celebration day.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Halloween is only for countries that allow it and celebrate. Some countries celebrate a similar day with different cultures or a totally different event during Halloween.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Behind History of Halloween and Where Does Halloween Come From?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">We mentioned the origin of the Halloween word. As for the origin, there is no distinct information about this event. Previously, this day was the day before All saints day that used to pray for the souls. All those mysterious beliefs lead us to the connection with souls make us believe that this was the origin and ancient history of Halloween.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Although, some believe that the ancient Gaelic Event of Samihan is the origin of Halloween. It was a festival where people tried to connect with the dead souls. People of that time believed that the boundary between living and dead became narrow during the festival period. So, they tried to connect with the souls to earn knowledge and power. Thus, many believe that it is the origin of Halloween. There are many cases where people tried to do that type of ritual to connect with souls. Many countries don’t allow Halloween because of such paranormal practice.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How is Halloween Celebrated Today?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Even though there are many scary theories behind Halloween, our current festival is nothing like those fantasies. We enjoy this amazing holiday with so many great cultural events. Of course, wearing scary costumes and doing cosplay is part of it. But, the most important part is sharing. We share happiness by giving and receiving treats. Besides, many schools or home parties are there as well.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">But, the real celebration can be a bit different. As it is a holiday, many people wait for promotional offers. This way, they can get a lot of necessary things at a lower cost. Take CBD users as an example. Usually, the best CBD sales come during this type of holiday. Suppose you search online with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/halloween-cbd-sales-and-deals/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Halloween&nbsp;CBD sales and deals,</a>&nbsp;Best CBD Halloween Sales, or similar tags. In that case, there will be tons of promotional discounts! So, every CBD user can get as many items as needed with a huge price cut.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Such promotions come for almost all types of products in the market. So, you can aim for Halloween shopping to&nbsp;get the best out of this day. Let’s have a look at the major event during Halloween.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Trick or Treating</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Trick or Treatise is the most popular quote on Halloween. It means either you trick me or give me a treat. The trick part is mostly known as a prank. Treat can be anything. Although, most treats are chocolates, candies, and other sweet stuff. People from every age like kids, young or old people go to their neighborhood and other places.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">By knocking on the door, they ask for a trick or treat. You can trick them by doing some sort of pranks or treat them with a happy smile. Weel, no one said you couldn’t treat them with a scary smile! It’s Halloween, after all.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Pumpkin Carving</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Pumpkin Carving is another favorite decoration event. People carve a scary face into a pumpkin and put light into it. The glowing eyes with scary eyes perfectly make the Halloween environment go wild. Although, it is not limited to only pumpkin. Many people used different types of dolls, statues, or other fruits to do Halloween decorations.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Costume Parties</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Costume parties are simply what makes Halloween so lively. Everyone tries different types of costumes. There is no limit to it. You can go for scary costumes to prank on people or do a scary look for the day. You can also try your favorite costume to portrait the character. It’s not weird if you see a couple of Deadpools walking through the street with a bag full of candies. You can even see a superman coming behind you to ask for a spicy treat!</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Halloween at Schools</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Most schools do Halloween events to give a wide space for the children. Their celebration may not always suit how an adult enjoys the day. So, each school performs its Halloween event to make sure every kid learns the culture and enjoys it with their friends. It is a whole new system of teaching communication and sharing. They do everything from the costume, carving, trick or treat, and more. There can be singing, dancing, or even watching Halloween shows together.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Halloween Today Traditions</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As we mentioned, cosplaying, carving, singing, dancing, playing, eating, watching shows, joining parties, going outside are all part of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/item/today-in-history/october-31/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">today’s Halloween&nbsp;celebration</a>. There is no limit to how we can celebrate the day.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You can see lazy people enjoying themselves by having a full day of sleep. Probably, he is enjoying Halloween in the dreams! But, many people try to do unauthorized works like extreme pranks, crimes, rituals, and some similar things. Those types of things are prohibited and not part of Halloween. So, be careful to select your activities during the event.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">What is Halloweenis a question hard to answer. But do we love Halloween? Yes, there is no doubt about it. It is a day full of extreme thrill and entertainment. We get to do so many things with friends and families. We also put on our favorite costumes and run around everywhere. This is a day full of surprises as most people love to do unique tricks and pranks.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Even countries that don’t celebrate Halloween also love to watch the beautiful activities of the day. Everyone around the globe looks forward to enjoying Halloween. If you celebrate the day, make sure to do a lot of fun and share with others. Happy Halloween!</p>', 14, '3', '2021-11-15 07:39:16', '2021-10-25 04:57:48', '2021-11-15 01:39:16', '10/02/2021 4:57 PM', 'James Trotta', 'what-is-halloween', 3, 'Yes'),
(39, 'The Canadian Federal Election Results', 'the-canadian-federal-election-results', 'Canada-election.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While there have been doubts concerning the necessity of the polls, the prime minister who won for the third term was optimistic that it was necessary. He argues that the election was pivotal for the country, for it grants them a chance to choose what they want in the next stages of a pandemic.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It was obvious from the recent polls that Trudeau was destined to win. However, they were wrong in their prediction to win the majority in the house of commons. May experts agree that the just concluded election is a replica of what happened during the 2019 elections.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The ended elections saw the 49-year-old leader of the center-left party now form the minority, something they might have planned for because of Trudeau’s confidence in the majority government. There was speculation that the liberals’ popularity had fallen after they announced their august election call.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3238\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Canada-electionbb.jpg\" alt=\"Canadian Federal Election\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Canada-electionbb.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Canada-electionbb-300x169.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Canada-electionbb-768x432.jpg 768w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Canada-electionbb-400x225.jpg 400w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Canada-electionbb-600x338.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Canadians were uncertain about the election because they had issues with the necessity of the need for an election. They could not understand how a nation can involve itself in an election amid a pandemic. Mr. Justin Trudeau could not get a smooth path due to the old political scandals. The uncertainties that were common in Mr. Trudeau campaign is among the reason the two parties were on a statistical political tier at a first place.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Final Results</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The recent annunciation on Tuesday confirms&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/justin-trudeau-wins-canadas-snap-election/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Mr. Justin Trudeau as a third-term prime minister in Canada</a>. While Mr. Trudeau is already on the Lead against the O’Toole party, he has an uphill after failing to garner majority seats that will have been good when forming a majority government. He now needs to work with other parties to enable them to pass any legislation.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While speaking to Montreal during the early Tuesday Address, Mr. Trudeau acknowledges that the Canadians want to go back to the things they love most. The citizens had no issues with the election or the pandemic. Despite the decision to hold an election so unpopular, he Acknowledges that the citizens send them with a clear mandate, and they pledge that.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It was evident from the preliminary results that the liberal party could not manage to form a majority government because they could not meet the threshold of 170 that was necessary to form a majority government.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">O’Toole’s party came close with 122 seats that saw the liberals party seeking a minority government. They are left with no choice but to form a part with other small parties to allow them to pass any legislation. There have been speculations on the prime ministers’ motives for calling an election in August in the midst of a pandemic. Perhaps the prime ministers had an intention to capitalize on the government pandemic response. The rival party was not to take this lying because by calling a foul against the prime minister. They term the elections as a Vanity project because it was the fourth Wave of Coronavirus.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While O’Toole was conceding to the elections, he terms it as a quick power grab on Tuesday. While addressing the supporters after the loss, he castigates Mr. Trudeau for asking for a majority Government, yet the Canadians were unwilling. He comments that the Canadians sent the prime minister back to the minority government after spending 600 Dollars.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The opposition conservatives were leading during the national popular vote, which had raised the hopes for the conservatives. The Tuesday result was then proving them wrong because they had to concede the defeat. The liberal party is now marking six years in power, extending that after a recent win. The Conservative party has had a long trek searching for power since 2011, which was the last time they won.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">O’Toole agrees that the conservatives party has increased in popularity, though it could not propel them to win an election. He believes that they can do better in the future, while he plans to stay as a leader and lead Canada in this journey.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Though there was speculation on the progressive New Democratic party picking an electoral seat, they fell short of the seats, and their kingmaker status was never to be. Jagmeet Singh party is yet to prove if they can attain the kingmaker status in the Canadian election.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Mr. Singh conceded defeat while affirming that their fight was still on. Now that the Liberal government will be forming a minority government, they might capitalize on Singh’s hopes to support the liberal party policies. Perhaps, the progressive party will support Mr. Trudeau’s policies to enable them to pass the legislation.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is prudent to note that Mr. Trudeau had 155 seats while heading to the election with 155 seats while the conservatives had 119 seats. The Bloc Quebecois held 32 seats, while the NDP held 24 seats. It was unfortunate for the green party, who only won two seats. Five independent MPS were also on the winning lists.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Mr. Trudeau expects to win majority support from the parliament following. The C$10per day child care seems to augur well with all parties. The liberal party lost two cabinet ministers, Maryam Monsef, who held the position for women and gender equality. Bernadette Jordan is also another woman who was standing for a fisheries minister.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The contester in the green party, Annie Paul, had many challenges in the recent past and was set for a bitter loss. The peoples’ party of Canada, Maxime Bernier, had other reservations for running against the people’s will. He was opposing the Covid-19 measures such as&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.hhs.gov/coronavirus/covid-19-vaccines/index.html\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">vaccines</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/prevent-getting-sick/about-face-coverings.html\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">masks</a>. Critics had no good words for that, terming it as a Xenophobic and racist idea.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In Summary, the liberals’ party did not win 170 seats to form a majority Government. Liberals won 158 seats that were insufficient to form a majority government, and they will settle for a minority one.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Conservatives come next with 122 seats. Bloc Quebecois took the third position with 34 seats, New democrats took the fourth position with 25 seats, and the green party won 2 seats. The people’s party had no seats.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The liberal party will form a minority government after failing to win the majority seats. It is interesting to watch how other parties partner with the liberal’s party to support their policies. Mr. Trudeau was on record saying that working on policies in a minority government may be a challenge.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Source Links</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-58573882</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/sep/21/canada-election-result-trudeau-forecast-to-win-third-term-after-early-vote-gamble</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2021-canada-election-live-results/</li></ul>', 14, '3', '2021-11-15 07:45:30', '2021-10-25 05:07:41', '2021-11-25 04:08:46', '10/26/2021 5:07 PM', 'James Trotta', 'canada-federal-election', 7, 'No'),
(40, 'NEWS Children Age 5 to 11 Can Get a Pfizer Covid-19 Vaccine', 'news-children-age-5-to-11-can-get-a-pfizer-covid-19-vaccine', 'Pfizer-says-COVID-19-vaccine-works-in-kids-ages-5-to-11.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Kids can now get a vaccine if Pfizer Covid-19 vaccine gets authorization. The Monday report suggests that the company is currently seeking approval from the US government to see a mass vaccination of the youngsters. It is prudent to note that the Pfizer vaccine is available for anyone aged 12 and above. The new developments will extend the age to 5.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">All eyes are now on the US government, considering the spread of the Covid-19 variant, which is raging among the vulnerable kids. Parents and institutions are anxious since there has been a surge in pediatric infections. It will be a milestone when they get a vaccine for their young ones.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How Will the Pfizer Vaccine Work for Kids?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Kids do not need a larger dose like adults. The elementary school kids will use a much lower amount, which is one-third of the actual shot that older adults get. They may not require the third dose because children between ages 5 to 11 will develop an antibody against Corona Virus. According to Dr. Bill Gruber, the Pfizer senior vice president, the kids will develop a robust antibody that serves the same purposes as teenagers and young adults.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Perhaps, you are worried about the safety of the Vaccine.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/covid-19-vaccines\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">The Covid-19 vaccine passed the safety test for the kids</a>, with reservations on temporary side-effects that adults also experience. They include sore arms, a fever, and machines. Teens can expect this side-effect, though it may not be universal to all. Some may not even experience any side effects after that dose. Gruber believes that their invention is the sweet spot. Everyone is concerned about the kids’ safety, and such an invention is a milestone for the world.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">More Related</span>:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/keep-your-children-safe-from-coronavirus\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Tips to Keep Your Children Safe from Covid-19</a></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3203 size-full\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Pfizer-says-COVID-19-vaccine-works-in-kids.jpg\" alt=\"Pfizer Covid-19 Vaccine for kids\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Pfizer-says-COVID-19-vaccine-works-in-kids.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Pfizer-says-COVID-19-vaccine-works-in-kids-300x225.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Pfizer-says-COVID-19-vaccine-works-in-kids-768x576.jpg 768w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Pfizer-says-COVID-19-vaccine-works-in-kids-180x135.jpg 180w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Pfizer-says-COVID-19-vaccine-works-in-kids-400x300.jpg 400w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Pfizer-says-COVID-19-vaccine-works-in-kids-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What is Next for Pfizer Company?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The company now has some tasks to fulfill before beginning the vaccination process for kids aged 5 to 11. Pfizer is applying to the food and drug administration by the end of the month for emergency use. They seek approval to use the Pfizer vaccine in the kids while working on a process to seek permission from European and British regulators.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The FDA chief, DR peter Marks, promise to work faster to assess the data and the study results from Pfizer. He affirms that the agency will work speedily in the verification process to establish if the claims are valid and if they are safe and effective for the kids.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is imperative to note that western nations are now vaccinating kids between the age of 12. while hopes are high that the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/fda-approved-the-pfizer-vaccine\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">FDA will approve the Pfizer Covid-19 vaccine</a>&nbsp;for the teens, they express similar worries about the kids’ side effects. They are now awaiting confirmation and the correct dose for the kids between 5 and 11. it is prudent to note that Cuba is on with mass vaccination of kids from the age of 2 using their homegrown vaccines. At the same time, the Chinese government already cleared their vaccines for use with children under the age of 3. two Vaccines are now available for kids from the age of 3 in China.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Why is This Vaccine Necessary?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You should note that the Covid-19 pandemic affects all people. Over 5 million kids have tested positive for Coronavirus. Based on the American Academy of Pediatrics reports, out of the 5 million positive cases, over 460 children have succumbed to the disease. The encroachment of delta Variant has seen the instances surge, and it is now sweeping throughout the country.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Kids are at a lower risk of severe illness than older people. Still, it does not warrant us to take chances now that new variants are developing. Gruber feels the fight is not yet over until the Vaccine is available for all. Parents need to have peace when their kids are out for school. It will be such an honor for parents to see their kids resuming their everyday routines.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The Vaccine is necessary because parents dodge questions from their kids who think they are not valued. Parents feel sad that they are running to seek a vaccine when their young ones are not. They are out there with nothing to safeguard them. It might be true, they are less exposed to the risk, but it is a challenge to explain that to a kid who knows that the parents and elder siblings are safe while they are not.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><a href=\"https://www.pfizer.com/news/press-release/press-release-detail/pfizer-and-biontech-conclude-phase-3-study-covid-19-vaccine\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">According to the study by Pfizer</a>, the kids only needed an immune bridging study. Younger kids may develop antibody levels, according to the evidence from the study. The antibody development is proving that the Vaccine can work for kids. Pfizer is on the record for reporting this during the Monday News though it is not a scientific publication.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is imperative to note that the study is still ongoing. The whole conclusion shall be available once sufficient data on those vaccinated and those not vaccinated are made available. Comparing the corona-virus cases on the vaccinated and those given placebos will prove the vaccine’s effectiveness.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The Pfizer company may be anxious about the latest invention, but all eyes are now on the regulators. The study’s sample size is insufficient to detect exceedingly unusual side effects, such as heart inflammation. The condition can develop after the second dose and is particularly common in young males. However, it may not be limited to men alone. Women can still suffer the same condition, but they are less familiar with women.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The research regulations make it a challenge to develop conclusive results about Pfizer’s effectiveness in kids. According to Marks of the FDA, pediatric studies should be large enough to rule out increased danger to young children. Pfizer’s Gruber states that upon approval, they will be closely watching for unique concerns.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Moderna, a second American vaccine company, is also testing its vaccines in elementary school-aged youngsters. Pfizer and Moderna are also researching infants as young as six months old. The results will be available later this year. The studies are prudent to ascertain the effectiveness of the vaccines in children. The Covid-19 vaccine research is targeting children from the age of 5 to 11. Hopefully, FDA will give Pfizer the go-ahead so that the kids can also get a Covid-19 vaccine.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Reference</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">https://www.latimes.com/science/story/2021-09-20/pfizer-covid-19-vaccine-5-to-11</li></ul>', 14, '3', '2021-11-15 07:45:41', '2021-10-25 05:10:49', '2021-11-15 01:45:41', '10/25/2021 5:10 PM', 'James Trotta', 'pfizer-says-covid-19-vaccine-works-on-kids', 0, 'No'),
(41, 'Justin Trudeau Wins Canada’s Snap Election But Falls Short of Seats', 'justin-trudeau-wins-canadas-snap-election-but-falls-short-of-seats', 'Justin-Trudeau-will-form-next-government.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">According to CNN(Montreal) reports, Canada’s liberal party will form the next government following their narrow win against Erin O’Toole’s rival party. Justin Trudeau’s Liberal party won the election despite garnering fewer seats necessary to form the majority government.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The reports from CNN show that the liberals had garnered 157 seats while their close competitors had 122 seats as of 2 am ET. The results herein depict the position after 95% of the polls across the country. The remaining seats are to be shared by the Quebec-based separatist party bloc and the new democratic party.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What Made Justin Trudeau Win?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/canada-federal-election/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Trudeau called the election in mid-August</a>, just two years into his minority administration, hoping to gain a majority by exploiting his&nbsp;<a href=\"https://oxfordmedicine.com/view/10.1093/med/9780199600830.001.0001/med-9780199600830-chapter-9\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">pandemic management</a>. It was after O’Toole’s conservative party efforts that reversed the Liberals’ plans. Over the past few days, the tracking surveys were strongly pulling to the tier, leaving the liberals with no options.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While Trudeau was addressing the supporters from Montreal on Tuesday after the win, he was confident that they were ready to take Canada through the Corona period. He agrees that the citizens of Canada were sending them with a clear mandate. Trudeau agrees that the citizens are ready for a progressive plan following the millions of voters who trust them. Despite the foreseen division during the campaigns, the results were proving otherwise, according to Justin.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3197 size-full\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Justin-Trudeau.jpg\" alt=\"Justin Trudeau Wins Canada\'s Snap Election\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Justin-Trudeau.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Justin-Trudeau-300x200.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Justin-Trudeau-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Despite Trudeau capitalizing on the issues affecting Canadians, some experts do not find the snap election unnecessary. They cite the Covid-19 pandemic to justify their reasons by claiming that many voters cannot identify a transparent ballot box to justify the snap election. Trudeau had issues such as handling Covid-19, working on climate change, controlling the guns, and affordable housing as the critical areas on his manifesto.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Was O’Toole Wrong on His Perception?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">O’Toole might have been wrong on his campaign plan, where he had capitalized on criticizing Justin. His campaign was solely on the perception that Trudeau was only after his political ambition rather than leadership. O’Toole was not happy with the results terming the snap election as a “quick power Grab.”</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While addressing the supporters on Tuesday, O’Toole had no good words for Justin Trudeau. He castigated Trudeau’s comments that a minority government was unworkable. H further narrates that after spending 600 million dollars in a snap election, Trudeau is willing to form the same government. He sarcastically says the Canadians were unwilling to give Justin a majority mandate but rather a minority characterized with divisions.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">During the campaign, O’Toole seems to disagree with Trudeau in a way uncommon in Canadian politics. O’Toole believes Trudeau’s self-interest was the reason for holding an election amid pandemics. He argues that they are always looking for a number one position, terming the election as expensive and unnecessary. O’Toole believes that such actions are unnecessary, and it was the utmost show of poor leadership.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While Trudeau was responding to O’Toole’s attacks on his perceived character, he committed to serving Canadians. His robust comments seem to incline that O’Toole belongs to the group he terms as proxies and anti-vaxxers movement. He says that they are the gun lobby group that never gave people the freedom of choice.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Issues That Raised Controversy, and the Final Thoughts</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The focus on cultural ideas, abortion rights, and Gun control seem to create more polarization in the US. Despite the candidates trying to engage on significant issues, voters tend to find a way to cause a separatism agenda. A small and fierce group opposes the Covid-19 protocols, such as the Vaccines and masks mandates. Some voters even expressed a grave hostility towards Justin Trudeau by throwing gravels to express their dissatisfaction with handling the Covid-19 pandemic.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Therefore, Justin will form a minority government after failing to attain the threshold voter capacity to acquire 170 seats.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Reference</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">https://edition.cnn.com/2021/09/20/americas/canada-election-results-trudeau-o-toole-intl/index.html</li></ul>', 14, '3', '2021-11-15 07:45:47', '2021-10-25 05:14:54', '2021-11-15 01:45:47', '10/24/2021 5:13 PM', 'James Trotta', 'justin-trudeau-wins-canadas-snap-election', 0, 'No');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(49, 'Young People are Worried About Climate Change', 'young-people-are-worried-about-climate-change', 'Climate-change-Young-people-very-worried.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">A recent Global survey came up with results that portray the anxiety young people are now experiencing due to climate change. The research found out that about 60% of young people express anxiety and extreme anxiety. 45% of the sample population felt that climate change was affecting their daily lives. Although another group had a different idea about the earth being doomed, it all expresses the anxiety around climate change.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What Does Climate Change Imply to the Young Population?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While many young people were expressing anxiety about climate change, a 16-year-old teenager had a different opinion about the destruction of the earth. The 16-year-old believes that the destruction of the earth is personal.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">According to the survey that Bath University led in collaboration with other five universities. The research Avaaz group was responsible for the support and financing of the research. The research ranks among the biggest ever, having questioned over 10000 sample population of young people aged 16 to 25.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">According to the sample group, it is evident that the young people believe that humanity is doomed, and the government is taking no action about it. Some youths feel ignored, abandoned, and betrayed by the older people and the political class. They do not take part in political opinions, neither do they have a platform that they can use to air their views.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Many young people believe that climate change is profoundly affecting a larger population of young people. Youths are now experiencing chronic stress, which is a result of climate change. The increase in high temperatures due to climate change increases the risk of mental and physical problems. There is an expectation of a mental health effect if the weather changes persist among young people.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">According to the report from the research by Bath University, it is evident that young people are affected by climate fears, making them develop psychological, social, and physical fear towards the climate. Caroline Hickman, the lead author from bath university, confirms Eco- anxiety in youths. She reports that Eco- anxiety is not just for environmental destruction but has an intrinsic link to the government inaction on climate change.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Climate change is also affecting the population in terms of marriages and procreation. According to the study, it is evident that the young population is hesitant towards bearing children. A probability of 0.4 among the research population does not believe in bearing children. They feel that the government should be listening to what the scientist is saying, rather than pathological on young people’s anxiety.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Portugal, for instance, was one of the wealthiest nations that were ranked the most worried following the research by Bath university. Portugal has seen many wildfires repeatedly and maybe a reason for the increased anxiety among the youths.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3144\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Young-people-very-worried-Climate-change.jpg\" alt=\"UK Students Strike Over Climate Change\" width=\"688\" height=\"449\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Young-people-very-worried-Climate-change.jpg 688w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Young-people-very-worried-Climate-change-300x196.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What Do Experts Say About Youths Being Anxious?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Tom Burke from the think tank E3G believes that it is rational for the youth to be anxious. He reports to BBC news that the knowledge that the young people have about climate change is not sourced from the media alone, but from what they can experience from their own eyes.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">According to the authors of the research, they attribute climate change and increased anxiety among the youths to the failure of the government to set up legislation that will gap the increase in hot days. The research notes an ongoing case about the Portuguese government where six young people took the government to court for failing to enact legislation that governs climate change.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">More Topic:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/fireworks-effects-on-the-environment\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Fireworks Effects on the Environment</a></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">In Summary</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The young people had the following answers concerning the questions;</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">83% of the young people agree that people have failed to care for the planet.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">75% of the study population believe that the future is uncertain and frightening.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">65% of the population is from Portugal, Brazil, the Philippines, Nigeria, and Australia. The US agrees that the government is failing the youths.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">31% of the youths trust the government. It implies that a larger population of 69% do not trust the government.</li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2981856/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">According to the authors of the report</a>, they are concerned about the young population’s distress. They quote a young youth who can stand dying, but he believes that living in a country that does not care about the environment and animals is not worth living.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Final Thoughts</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is evident from the research that young people are apprehensive about climate change, and governments should take responsibility to safeguard the situation.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Source Links</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-24021772</p>', 14, '3', '2021-11-15 07:45:56', '2021-10-26 00:12:57', '2021-11-15 01:45:56', '10/19/2021 12:12 PM', 'James Trotta', 'young-people-are-worried-about-climate-change', 0, 'No'),
(50, 'NEWS Cristiano Ronaldo Rape Allegations: What will Happen Now', 'news-cristiano-ronaldo-rape-allegations-what-will-happen-now', 'Cristiano-Ronaldo-Explaining-the-rape-allegations-against-Manchester-United-football.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Cristiano Ronaldo will make his second debut for Manchester United this weekend. After having completed his £19.8 million moves from Juventus last month.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The Old Trafford crowd saw him score 118 goals in 292 appearances and win a string of significant honors at United before leaving for Real Madrid in 2009. They will give him a warm welcome.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The five-time Ballon d’Or winner has only enhanced his status as one of the greatest players of all time. Since then, he has been winning four Champions Leagues during his time at Madrid.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However, a few years ago, Cristiano’s image was attacked when Kathryn Mayorga, 37, accused Cristiano Ronaldo of rape. The model alleges that the footballer raped her in a hotel in Las Vegas (Nevada, USA) in 2009. The Portuguese player vehemently denies all the accusations made against him.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Criminal charges were not filled, as prosecutors confirmed that Mayorga couldn’t prove anything more than a doubt. Mayorga’s lawyers have explained that the #MeToo movement against sexual harassment inspired her to speak out. Here is everything you need to know about the Cristiano Ronaldo rape allegations.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Court documents unveiled by The Mirror newspaper claim that the alleged rape took place in a Las Vegas hotel room in 2009 after they met that same night at the RAIN nightclub. The model provides a list of witnesses her legal team wants to see testify. This one includes former British star Jasmine Lennard, 35. Here is everything about Cristiano Ronaldo’s rape allegations.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3134\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Cristiano-Ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo\" width=\"800\" height=\"487\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Cristiano-Ronaldo.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Cristiano-Ronaldo-300x183.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Cristiano-Ronaldo-768x468.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What are the Accusations Against Ronaldo?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Cristiano Ronaldo’s legal dispute against a woman who accuses him of raping her while she was in the Portuguese player’s suite at a Las Vegas resort more than ten years ago is working in the state of Nevada (USA).</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In July 2019, the Clark County District Attorney’s Office in Las Vegas, USA, terminated the prosecution against Cristiano Ronaldo. After a lengthy investigation that ended in a statement that there was insufficient evidence on whether he raped model Kathryn Mayorga in 2009.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Now, a U.S. district judge had reopened the case to decide on Mayorga’s&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/mentalhealth/index.htm\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">mental health</a>&nbsp;when she signed a confidentiality agreement in 2010. This dramatically complicates the Portuguese soccer player’s situation.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The Manchester forward was accused by Mayorga of raping her in his Las Vegas hotel room on June 13, 2009. The former teacher and model signed a secret agreement with the 35-year-old Ronaldo’s representatives a year later. Who paid the woman $375,000? In 2018 Mayorga decided to break her silence and file a lawsuit for bribery and extortion. Which she finally withdrew in May 2019.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Now Judge Jennifer Dorsey will hear arguments and decide whether Kathryn Mayorga was mentally competent to sign that agreement. Suppose the complainant manages to prove that she was not mentally well when she received the money. In that case, the Manchester striker will have to sit in the dock again, charged with the crime of rape.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">New Accusations</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">New information about Mayorga’s demand is here. This woman was the one who denounced Ronaldo for rape. According to her, the soccer player sexually abused her 12 years ago. Finally, in 2019 the case was nothing due to lack of evidence, and the model withdrew the lawsuit. But now, the model is claiming compensation for the damages suffered.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The case came to light in April 2017 and in 2018 lived its most intense moments. The model sued the footballer accusing him of rape and that he had sexually assaulted her. After that, the model and the footballer secretly agreed to pay USD 375,000.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Regarding that agreement, she explained before the courts that she was “mentally incapacitated” when she signed it. But then, the plaintiff dropped the lawsuit in June 2019. Later the case was closed for lack of evidence, and everything was left up in the air.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><a href=\"https://amazingtimesgh.com/2021/04/30/model-kathryn-mayorga-claims-56-million-prior-to-damages/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">According to documents accessed</a>&nbsp;by the British site Mirror, Mayorga claims financial compensation commensurate with the consequences she suffered: the model wants 18 million euros.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The striker has publicly denied the allegations. He never appeared in court but left the case in the hands of his lawyers. They want to be famous by naming me. It is part of my job. It is normal. Everything is fine,” he had declared in September 2018.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This article will attempt to expand on previous allegations Cristiano has faced concerning alleged abuse and address more recent ones.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The event occurred on the night of June 13, 2009, in Las Vegas. Her job was to be a presence in bars and nightclubs in the city.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Cristiano Ronaldo, who was about to sign a millionaire contract with Real Madrid for USD 100 million, spent at least a week in North American. He stayed at the Palms Casino Resort in a suite with a jacuzzi cost around 6,300 euros per night.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">One of those nights, the Portuguese decided to go to the VIP section of Rain. This is a nightclub at the Palms Casino Resorts. It was there where he met Kathryn Mayorga, along with other models.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In 2018, the German newspaper Der Spiegel made public the photos of that night. According to the woman, the party moved to the suite of the former Manchester United player. It was there when he took her to another room where the abuse allegedly took place.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Later, according to her word, Ronaldo and his lawyers offered her an out-of-court agreement to keep silent. The amount was 375 thousand dollars. She accepted for fear of any retaliation against her and her family.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This is everything you need to know about the rape accusations against Cristiano Ronaldo. The United striker hopes to resolve this as soon as possible to continue to wreak havoc in the opposition net. United fans are hoping for the same to enjoy the striker to the fullest as they did before.</p>', 14, '3', '2021-11-15 07:46:09', '2021-10-26 00:15:25', '2021-12-08 04:38:23', '09/16/2021 12:13 PM', 'James Trotta', 'cristiano-ronaldo-rape-allegations', 7, 'Yes'),
(51, 'Can a Chiropractor Help with Weight Loss? Procedure & Additional Support', 'can-a-chiropractor-help-with-weight-loss-procedure-additional-support', 'Can-a-Chiropractor-Help-with-Weight-Loss.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Chiropractic Weight Loss Program is one of the trendy treatments for weight loss. As science is developing, we are introducing a lot of new procedures to deal with physical management. Chiropractic is one of those methods. It is a bit different from regular weight loss projects. It combines a series of procedures that are more patient-oriented and have a higher success rate.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This program monitors a patient from multiple angles and decides which support is necessary for a&nbsp;natural weight reduction. Food selection, energy level, bone and joint adjustment, exercise selection, counseling, and similar surveys are all part of this program. If you are having overweight issues, then contact a&nbsp;chiropractor for weight loss. You are bound to be surprised by its amazing approach that will improve weight and your lifestyle.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What is A Chiropractic Weight Loss Program?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Certainly, being overweight is a crucial problem. There is no direct solution to lose weight. You need to work hard for it. But, if you want to lose weight faster, then there are a couple of medical solutions. Some people get surgery or strong&nbsp;weight-reducing medicine.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Unfortunately, those types of solutions can put a lot of toll on your body. It can also show side effects that can harm the physical state permanently. Thus, there are innovative systems like&nbsp;Chiropractic Weight Loss Program.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This program doesn’t focus only on exercise. Most weight loss programs only ask you to take less energetic food and do a lot of exercise. Exercise is inevitable for weight reduction, but there are more things into it. Thoroughly researching your lifestyle, it is possible to take care of the weight more naturally. As the name says, it includes different types of chiropractic support to improve the physical condition.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3449 size-full\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Can-a-Chiropractor-Help-with-Weight-Loss-BB.jpg\" alt=\"Chiropractic Weight Loss Program\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Can-a-Chiropractor-Help-with-Weight-Loss-BB.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Can-a-Chiropractor-Help-with-Weight-Loss-BB-300x188.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Can-a-Chiropractor-Help-with-Weight-Loss-BB-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Chiropractic Care and Weight Loss</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">So,&nbsp;can a chiropractor help with weight loss? As you already know, chiropractic helps you to adjust any physical imbalance like tight joints,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.frontiersin.org/articles/10.3389/fbioe.2020.00560/full\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">bone positioning</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://medlineplus.gov/muscledisorders.html\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">muscle disorder</a>, and so on. These types of issues can cause a significant disturbance in our life. Probably, you can’t even move efficiently. Exercise is the most important part of weight loss treatment. If you can’t even move the body freely, then how can you do the exercise?</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">So,&nbsp;chiropractic care for weight loss&nbsp;starts with physical observation. It completes if you have any type of imbalance. Then, the process continues to observe your diet and exercise routine. With a combination of such weight reduction mechanisms, a patient steadily gets into a natural fitness. It doesn’t put any pressure on the body and makes sure that you are feeling comfortable.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How Chiropractic Treatment May Help You Lose Weight</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">A chiropractor knows the body much better than a gymnastic expert. They believe that a lot of weight gain issues come from problematic physical conditions. If your body is not in the best condition, many external effects keep on rising. Thus, they focus on chiropractic and adjust any bone, muscle, or joint imbalance.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Surprisingly, it gives a huge boost to the patient. Practically, it has been one of the most successful practices that definitely improves our physical condition to lead an everyday life. Chiropractic has become a trend because of its successful impact.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">When you get an active body without any restrain, the body starts to work at its best. Later, the treatment procedure aims for nutrient control. If you don’t follow a proper diet, then the body will start gaining more and more weight. This is the last thing an overweight person should do. So, they make sure that your diet is giving enough&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/six-essential-nutrients\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">essential nutrients</a>. But, it will not exceed the energy level putting more calories into the body.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Besides, it also determines if you need&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-a-dietary-supplement\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">supplements to maintain the diet</a>. Then, the focus goes into the major part, exercise. Although, other parts of this treatment keep on going with the exercise. With regular counseling, the process goes through a bunch of exercises depending n your health condition. But, the process is a bit steady as they continuously check your progression. Depending on your health, you can get additional massage or exercise to improve your weight loss.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">So, not only chiropractic gives you more stability in your physical condition, but it also improves your mental condition. Under regular observation and counseling, it gives you the most smooth procedure to manage weight loss.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What Does Research Show About Chiropractic Therapy for Weight Loss?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/chiropractic-therapy\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Chiropractic Therapy</span></a>&nbsp;doesn’t help you with weight loss directly. It does the job passively. For weight loss, you need to maintain a good meal and do lots of exercises. There is no exception to it. What chiropractic does is boost those procedures. With therapy, you get more stability in health. With counseling, you get immediate advice and direction for the next step. Under observation, your weight loss procedure goes smoothly, which has little chance of getting wrong.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As it is a new process, the progression is still under development. But, theoretically and practically, it is a much better approach than the existing procedure we have. In most cases, we just go on doing rough exercises and getting a series of recommended foods. But, each body has different development, so the same process may not be suitable for everyone. In that case, you should definitely go to a&nbsp;chiropractor for weight loss&nbsp;treatment.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">As an Alternative Medicine, How Can CBD Help You Lose Weight?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If you want&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-alternative-medicine/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">alternative Medicine</a>, there are only a few available options. In most cases, experts may suggest extra medicine like tablets or injections. But, there are some other ways to do so. Using CBD products like&nbsp;CBD oil&nbsp;is one of them. Do you know&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-cbd\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">what CBD is</span></a>? It is a supporting element that can improve your physical condition. Metabolism, inflammation, pain, anxiety, stress, low sleep, and many other things can be balanced with CBD.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Surprisingly, a lot of weight gain issues are enhanced with mental conditions. So, CBD really helps you to maintain those conditions and become more active. Eventually, you get less weight and even burn more fats, which leads you to deal with weight problems much better. You can have a decent meal and lots of exercise with an energetic and happy mind. There are many&nbsp;CBD products for different health issues.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Among the best&nbsp;CBD products and weight loss,&nbsp;CBD oil&nbsp;is the more popular one. As we mentioned, it covers up a lot of issues like inflammation, metabolism, and similar effects. Which eventually lets you lose more weight when&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/about-plank-exercise\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">doing exercise</a>. If you have a lot of physical stress from exercise, then use CBD tinctures to reduce the pain.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Some people may face skin issues from exercise. In that case, you can use CBD salves. Even more, there are CBD drinks that can enhance your physical relief even more. So, CBD products can be your supportive companion during the&nbsp;weight-loss treatment. Make sure to take advice from your chiropractor before using them.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Going to a&nbsp;chiropractor for weight loss&nbsp;will be a smart thing to do. Just doing random exercise to burn fat and get muscle is not the right way of losing weight. You need continuous observation to improve your health condition. Each body adapts differently. So, you need to figure out how your body will adapt to the&nbsp;weight loss treatments.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Additional support,&nbsp;chiropractic therapy, massage, exercise, meal choice, supplements, and more stuff can be managed by a chiropractor. So, if you have weight issues, then try&nbsp;chiropractor weight loss treatment&nbsp;without any worry. For additional support, try some&nbsp;CBD products. It is a much better procedure than the ones we had.</p>', 15, '3', '2021-11-15 07:46:19', '2021-10-26 00:18:43', '2021-11-15 01:46:19', '10/08/2021 12:18 PM', 'Leonel Escobedo', 'chiropractor-for-weight-loss', 0, 'Yes'),
(52, 'HEALTHY LIVING Best Ways to Stay Healthy in Winters: 9 Tips to Stay Healthy', 'healthy-living-best-ways-to-stay-healthy-in-winters-9-tips-to-stay-healthy', 'Best-Ways-to-Stay-Healthy-In-Winter.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Winters can be a great chance for people after really hot summers. Even though the weather conditions might be changing, it must be noted that this change in weather can accompany many of the changing health conditions. During this time, it is mandatory to check for the best ways to stay healthy in winters. Health conditions like flu, throat infections, etc., may take over, and it can harm your health. Therefore, to stay clear of these issues and stay healthy, it is essential to take the following precautions.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How Can We Stay Healthy During Winter Season?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Once we are past the question of why to stay healthy in summer, we need to approach the question of how to stay healthy during the winter season. So, without any further delay, let’s look at some of the steps that could be taken to ensure your health during the wintertime.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Eat Immune Boosting Foods</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The immune system is responsible for regulating your bodily functions, and it possesses the ability to fight against health issues. Hence, it is essential to adjust your diet in such a way that it incorporates immune-boosting Food in your daily diet. The best sources of immune-boosting food are foods rich in Vitamin C, mainly from&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.hsph.harvard.edu/nutritionsource/what-should-you-eat/vegetables-and-fruits/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 110, 224);\">vegetables and fruits</span></a>; zinc, which can be obtained through nuts and seeds and various other animal products; and lastly, iron, which is contained in lentils, meat, and spinach. Eat immune-boosting foods to ensure good health in winters!</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Keep Exercising</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Staying active is imperative to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/maintaining-a-healthy-lifestyle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 110, 224);\">maintain your health</span></a>, especially in winters. It is immensely hard to motivate yourself to leave your warm bed and work out winters can be harsh, so how to keep excising in winters? For starters, set goals and then start with simpler exercises. You can also spike up your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-motivation/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 110, 224);\">motivation level</span></a>&nbsp;and join yoga or dance classes to stay consistent in your workout routine.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3377 size-full\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Best-Ways-to-Stay-Healthy-In-Winter-BB.jpg\" alt=\"Stay Healthy in Winters\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Best-Ways-to-Stay-Healthy-In-Winter-BB.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Best-Ways-to-Stay-Healthy-In-Winter-BB-300x188.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Best-Ways-to-Stay-Healthy-In-Winter-BB-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Drink More Water</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Dehydration is another issue that you face when winter approaches, as people tend to drink less water during winters. One of the many important tips to follow during the winter seasons is to drink more water. Water is needed to cleanse your body of all the toxins present in the body, so in winters, when the intake of water drops, the body cannot remove the toxins, which can lead to various health issues. So, in order to stay healthy, it is essential to drink more water in winters.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Drink More Milk</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Loaded with calcium, milk is very healthy for the body, and in winters when your body is not well hydrated or lacking&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/six-essential-nutrients\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 110, 224);\">essential nutrients</span></a>. Consuming hot milk in winters can keep you active and healthy during winters. In addition, make sure that you do not consume cold milk as much because this can lead to flu or throat issues. Hence, to stay healthy in winters, drink more milk.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Try to Avoid Drinking Alcohol</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Alcohol must also be avoided in the winter season. Alcohol makes your body prone to an increase in temperature. It can cause contraction in the blood vessels that can hinder many bodily functions. This contraction makes you sensitive to the weather. You may have to lower your intake of alcohol to retain your senses and avoid them getting numb.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Getting Vitamin D</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Vitamin D is a great nutrient to maintain the overall health of your body, and the sunlight is the main source to acquire Vitamin D. in winters, we tend to be less exposed to sunlight. Hence, our Vitamin D intake drops. Acquiring this vitamin is essential in winter as it is responsible for bone and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.healthypeople.gov/2020/about/foundation-health-measures/General-Health-Status\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 110, 224);\">general health</span></a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Even though vitamin D is essential, you can still get sunburned, so it is mandatory to apply sunscreen while leaving your home. However, if you need some additional Vitamin D, feel free to take a stroll in the sunlight to reap all the benefits of vitamin D.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Try to Stay Warm and Keep Active</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Staying warm in winters is very important as it helps you maintain your body temperature and keep you healthy. To ensure that you stay warm in winters, try drinking hot drinks and consuming hot food in nature. You can also stay warm by working put as it helps in maintaining&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/facts-about-body-temperature\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 110, 224);\">body temperature</span></a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">When your body stays active, you will be able to keep yourself warm and in control. Therefore, it is important to keep yourself active in winter. Go out with friends, work out, take dance or yoga classes, and stay motivated. This would assist you in maintaining your health during the wintertime and to helping you avoid all the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://training.seer.cancer.gov/anatomy/cells_tissues_membranes/tissues/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 110, 224);\">bodily tissues</span></a>.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Practice Better Hygiene</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Flu and cold are some of the major issues that accompany the winter season. They spread through the transference of germs from one individual to another. Hence, during winters, it is essential to practice better hygiene. Make sure to wash your hands regularly and before you start preparing food. Also, be cautious while coughing or sneezing as it can spread germs. If you feel sick, it is best to stay at home and avoid any potential transference of germs.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Sleep Well</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Sleeping for a good number of hours is pertinent for your health even though it is bad to hibernate, but ensure enough sleep to function properly throughout the lazy winter days.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">The Bottom Line</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">To sum up, it is mandatory to stay fit in winter. The aforementioned techniques are some of the best ways to stay healthy in winters. Moreover, to practice the best routine, stay focused and follow all the ways to stay in shape. Health wealth is a famous proverb, and you indeed need to have better health to enjoy every walk of life. Stay happy and healthy in winters.</p>', 15, '3', '2021-11-15 07:46:28', '2021-10-26 00:35:36', '2021-11-15 01:46:28', '10/06/2021 12:34 PM', 'Leonel Escobedo', 'best-ways-to-stay-healthy-in-winter', 0, 'No');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(53, 'What is Ketoconazole Shampoo? The Best Comprehensive Guide', 'what-is-ketoconazole-shampoo-the-best-comprehensive-guide', 'What-Is-Ketoconazole-Shampoo.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">What is ketoconazole shampoo? A frequently asked question of the folks. In the dermatological world, dandruff is one of the common yet irritating skin problems.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Whenever you go to the doctor with severe dandruff issues, mainly, the doctors prescribe this shampoo. However, why do they suggest this one? What is the specialty of this shampoo? Are there any possible risks of using it?</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Well, we have got your back, mate. This complete guide on ketoconazole shampoo covers almost all the unknown questions. And we strongly recommend you to go through this feature carefully before you decide to use it. Let us explore the essential facts on this medicinal shampoo.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What Is Ketoconazole Shampoo?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Before we answer- “what is ketoconazole shampoo?” let us briefly explain the term “ketoconazole.” Well, ketoconazole is a type of drug used as an antifungal remedy. To be specific, it’s an artificial antifungal agent.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Basically, for the skin issues like athlete’s foot, ringworm or yeast infections, ketoconazole is available in various forms. Apart from cream or gel, ketoconazole shampoo is available in the market. Also, you will find it as an OTC or prescription shampoo.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You can purchase ketoconazole shampoo 1% or 2%, depending on the concentration of ketoconazole. There is an over-the-counter 1% shampoo. However, the more powerful 2% form requires a doctor’s prescription.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3443 size-full\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/What-Is-Ketoconazole-Shampoo-BB.jpg\" alt=\"Ketoconazole Shampoo\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/What-Is-Ketoconazole-Shampoo-BB.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/What-Is-Ketoconazole-Shampoo-BB-300x188.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/What-Is-Ketoconazole-Shampoo-BB-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 0.8em auto;\"><br>Different Types of Ketoconazole Shampoo</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As we have mentioned before, you can find this shampoo as OTC(Over-the-counter) and with a doctor’s recommendation. To add, the most known OTC (generally with 1% ketoconazole) brand is Nizoral. Many supermarkets carry it, and it is also available online. Also, the shampoo brands which require a doctor’s prescription are – Ket Med, Ketozal, Ketozolin.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How Does Ketoconazole Shampoo Work to Treat Your Scalp Issues?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You have already understood -” what is ketoconazole shampoo.” Maybe you would like to explore the ketoconazole shampoo benefits further.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Here is an interesting fact.<br>Do you know what causes that utterly frustrating dandruff on your head? Yes, nothing but a fungus named Malassezia. However, genetics and environment play a role in Malassezia’s development. Several factors affect fungus growth, including body hormones, environment, plus diet.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Naturally, the scalp cells grow. However, Malassezia causes inflammation, stimulating the regeneration procedure of our scalp cells. So, it develops the turnover of cells. Moreover, the growth of the dead cells is also increased. Thus, the condition leads to scalp itching, shedding, and dandruff.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Ketoconazole, as an antifungal remedy, is effective against Malassezia. The salicylic acid in ketoconazole shampoo helps to control dandruff and itching. Besides, it also lessens inflammation, which is why ketoconazole shampoo can slow down the shedding process.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How to Use This Medicine</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Ketoconazole shampoo is only for your external users. As always, verify that you are following the instruction manual fully. As suggested by the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://my.clevelandclinic.org/health/drugs/20386-ketoconazole-shampoo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 110, 224);\">Cleveland Clinic</span></a>, users should wash both hands before and after the application. This is because ketoconazole is a strong chemical. Then, before applying it over the scalp, wet the scalp thoroughly. Take enough amount so that the lather can cover the affected areas.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Afterward, give it at least 5 minutes to get the best results. You are all set! Rinse it off entirely with enough water. Well, avoid getting it in your eyes or other sensitive areas. However, if it gets in the eyes, rinse the eyes quickly with water.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Who Can Use This?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Let us tweak the question a bit. Like-<br>Who should not use this shampoo? Normally, dermatologists don’t prescribe this shampoo to patients who are sensitive to ketoconazole. Further, first-time users should check the other active components of this shampoo. If they are allergic to any of them, they should avoid using this product.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Additionally, pregnant or breastfeeding women should not use this shampoo without a doctor’s consultation. The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/09546634.2019.1573309?journalCode=ijdt20&amp;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 110, 224);\">latest 2019 research</span></a>&nbsp;on ketoconazole suggests that people can apply it topically. Moreover, it can be used safely for dandruff and other scalp problems recovery purposes.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Nevertheless, we recommend applying a small portion at first. If the first application occurs any irritation, you should not continue the usage. And in any severe skin irritation, experts advise seeking medical help. However, the extreme reaction is somewhat rare. We are going to discuss the possible side effects in the next segment.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Risks and Side Effects of Ketoconazole Shampoo</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Ketoconazole shampoo rarely causes any serious side effects. Yet, some probable reactions could be-</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26);\">Face, tongue, or lips inflammation</span></li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><a href=\"https://medlineplus.gov/rashes.html\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Skin rash</a></li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><a href=\"https://medicine.wustl.edu/news/acute-itching-in-eczema-patients-linked-to-environmental-allergens/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Itching</a></li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26);\">Numbness</span></li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(14, 16, 26);\">Dry or flaky skin</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However, it is not necessary to seek emergency medical assistance for those issues. But if they persist or become too bothersome, you should consult your physician.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How Often Do You Use It?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Does ketoconazole shampoo work more efficiently if you apply it more? Maybe then dandruff won’t return. Well, that is not the case, unfortunately. According to the ketoconazole percentage (1% or 2%), the dosage will vary.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Usually, as for prescription ketoconazole, applying twice a week for dandruff is enough. Moreover, thrice a week is generally suggested to prevent hair loss. And you can use the OTC version almost every day, depending on your symptoms.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Does Ketoconazole Shampoo Interact with Other Drugs?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It may happen in some cases. To add, the interaction could be of severe, serious, or moderate types. Therefore, the healthcare professional should inform you about any potential drug interaction. To be safe, consult your physician when starting, stopping, or changing the dosage. Also, you must tell the doctor as well as the pharmacist of any of your current medications.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It’s time to wrap up, guys. All in all, we want to remind you about its usage once more, as this product is not any typical perfumed shampoo. For example, do not use ketoconazole shampoo as per your wish. Plus, only follow the prescription or the user instructions. Then, you can expect to see the effects within several weeks.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However, the result will differ according to the severity of the problem. After a month, if you don’t notice any visible improvement, consult your doctor. Hence, trying other options is better if ketoconazole shampoo doesn’t work. We hope now you have got a detailed answer to the question- what is ketoconazole shampoo? Stay well and healthy. Thanks for stopping by!</p>', 15, '3', '2021-11-15 07:46:36', '2021-10-26 00:47:30', '2021-11-25 03:20:21', '10/17/2021 12:47 PM', 'Leonel Escobedo', 'ketoconazole-shampoo', 1, 'No'),
(54, 'Vibration Therapy Explained: The Simplest Comprehensive Guide', 'vibration-therapy-explained-the-simplest-comprehensive-guide', 'Vibration-Therapy.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Do you think we can face the process of getting older with pre-planned insights? Well, dealing with aging and other health problems possesses some unavoidable parts. However, diverse medical remedies are there to aid people in that case. And vibration therapy is&nbsp;one of them.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In most cases, finding some cures with zero side effects is impossible. Also, irrespective of gender and age, people keep experiencing unexpected health issues. Nevertheless, a relatively simple therapy like this can-do wonder. Here in this article, our discussion has taken this path of explaining the relevant query regarding it. So, let us delve into some research on this 19th-century technology!</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What is Vibration Therapy?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The method of vibration therapy involves vibration of the whole body to recover physical health. Also, it maintains good body well-being as well. Since its inception, personal trainers, players, and healthcare practitioners have widely researched this method. To add, they are applying this process for its multiple health benefits.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In the Russian space program, the doctors observed bone loss plus fractures in astronauts. And it happened at a young age which was not expected. Then, this therapy with vibration supported astronauts in strengthening their bones and muscles. NASA still uses this therapy to prevent early bone loss.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How Does Vibration Therapy Work?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Basically, two types of vibration therapy exist:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Whole-body</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Localized</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Whole-Body</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This one requires standing, sitting, or lying on a machine. And the device has a vibrating platform attached to it. Also, the therapist might ask you to kneel in a half-squat position.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Localized</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As for the second one, it involves some specific body parts. Your therapist will use a hand-operated vibrating machine to apply the localized vibration. For instance, they may set it on the patient’s calf muscles. Activities of the Therapy.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Afterward, as the vibrations reach your body, the body muscles start to contract. Also, the vibrations make them relaxed. Additionally, specific vibrations can increase osteoblast production. These cells are responsible for making bone.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The mechanism of this treatment may depend on its intensity cum direction. For example-some therapy machines generate vertical vibrations. And some vibrations go upward and downward as well as forward and backward. However, the best vibrations for creating muscle contractions are those that drive up and down.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What Research Shows About Vibration Therapy Health Benefits</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Vibration therapy is likely to have health benefits as well as risks. It’s a no-brainer that more research is essential. Benefits of vibration therapy include bone&nbsp;density improvement, muscle mass growth, and better blood circulation.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Moreover, it works as a stress reliever plus a metabolism booster in some cases. Body pain reduction is also on the list. Hence, according to proven studies, it may treat several conditions. However, it may also cause some risks. We are going to highlight both topics now.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Improves Bone Density and Muscle Strength</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><a href=\"https://www.healthline.com/health/vibration-therapy#risks\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">A feature in Clinical Rehabilitation</a>&nbsp;had reviewed the effect of the therapy. It was about the therapy’s benefits on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/how-to-increase-strength\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">improving muscle strength</a>. Also, it had added an impact on bone density. The authors showed evidence that this therapy can help regain leg muscle strength in older folks<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">.</span></p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Benefits in Parkinson’s Disease</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Parkinson’s disease patients may get short-range benefits from this therapy.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/20037223/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">A Neuro Rehabilitation study</a>&nbsp;stated&nbsp;that. For instance, it can help reduce muscle stiffness plus tremors. Nevertheless, more research is essential in this field also.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3096 size-full\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Therapy-Vibration.jpg\" alt=\" Vibration Therapy taken\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Therapy-Vibration.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Therapy-Vibration-300x200.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Therapy-Vibration-768x513.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">May Heal Muscle Pain</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Often after exercise, people suffer from muscle soreness. The Journal of Athletic Training published a research article, and it showed the solution. According to the report, whole-body vibration therapy prevents muscle pain after cardio exercise and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-weight-training\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">weight&nbsp;strength training</a>. However, the authors had mentioned the requirement of in-depth study regarding this issue.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Risk of Vibration Therapy</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Sometimes high-intensity vibrations may be harmful to the body. Thus, the effect may end up causing extreme back pain or other lumbar issues. Hence, we suggest consulting your physician before going through this therapy. Usually, the following issues discourage the treatment-</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">History of heart disease</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Pregnancy</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Diabetes</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Those who are on blood-thinning medicines</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Is Whole-Body Vibration Therapy Good for Weight Loss?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Whole-body vibration provides several fitness rewards. In it, with the machine vibration, your whole body feels like exercising. And this process allows your muscle to relax multiple times per second. According to advocates, 15 minutes of full-body therapy thrice a week may speed up the weight loss process. Besides, it may aid fat burning, body flexibility, etc.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Nonetheless, it may not be a proper alternative to your day-to-day workout. It is not still sure whether the procedure can replace&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-cardio\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">cardio exercises like</a>&nbsp;walking, running, biking, etc. Hence, only all-inclusive research on whole<span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">–</span>body vibration therapy may&nbsp;clear the doubts in the future.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">So, we recommend going for a balanced diet first. Alongside, try some daily physical movements. Afterward, if you maintain the therapy, include aerobic and other strength training also.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">More Topic:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/chiropractic-therapy\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Chiropractic Therapy: What is It, Treatments, Benefits, and Side Effects</a></p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Are Vibration and Percussion Therapy the Same?</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Some also consider percussion therapy instead of vibration. Well, both the treatments are mostly regarded as uniformly effective. But their activities are different. Percussion therapy is helpful for instant body comfort plus relief. Alternatively, in terms of lessening muscle soreness and exhibiting positive results, vibration therapy is more beneficial.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">More Topic</span>:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-reiki\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">What Is Reiki? Everything You Need to Know</a></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Throughout this article, we have mentioned that vibration therapy still needs ample and advanced research. Curing serious diseases entirely may not be the case with this therapy yet. And vibration intensity may influence its effectiveness. However, its health benefits are evident.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">So, as you have got fair enough ideas about the ins and outs, now it’s time for the decision. We have explained the benefits along with the risk sides. Thus, we hope you can opt for it easily. To finish, your physician’s recommendation will play a significant role in this matter. Therefore, assessing potential advantages and risks is possible with their advice.</p>', 15, '3', '2021-11-15 07:46:45', '2021-10-26 00:51:16', '2021-11-15 01:46:45', '10/28/2021 12:51 PM', 'Leonel Escobedo', 'vibration-therapy', 0, 'Yes'),
(55, 'What Is Reiki? Everything You Need to Know', 'what-is-reiki-everything-you-need-to-know', 'What-Is-Reiki.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">What is Reiki? How does this technique work? Is Reiki helpful for everyone? If you have these questions in mind, this article points at everything you need to know.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What Is Reiki?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Reiki is a Japanese procedure that uses an energy transfer healing technique to manage disease symptoms and improve general well-being. In this technique, the practitioner employs universal positive energies and transfers them to you by placing their hands either directly on you or just above different areas of your body.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It’s a common belief that the practitioner stimulates your body’s natural remedial abilities through this technique. Let’s dive into the article with us to know about the history, benefits, and side effects of this therapy.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Where Does Reiki Come from Exactly?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In the early 1920s, Mikao Usui in Japan introduced the term ‘Reiki’ with his intense spiritual practices and techniques. During the last four years of his life, Usui worked with Hayashi- a retired naval officer, to excerpt the healing practices and opened a Reiki clinic in Tokyo. After that, Takata- a Japanese- American, became the devoted student of Hayashi after receiving Reiki for a number of her medical conditions.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">With Hayashi’s guidance, she brought this therapy technique to Hawaii and then to the US Mainland. She taught the Reiki to others. Subsequently, it gained fame and is now practiced all over the World, although not usually in the traditional form Takata taught. To sum up, that’s the Reiki history.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How Does Reiki Work for Wellness?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Are you wondering how does Reiki works for wellness? We know, for a fact, that it helps lessen the impact of stress, releasing tension from the entire system; however, how exactly does Reiki release tension and help to heal the body? Although there is no particular evidence, a few theories suggest how does Reiki perform.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">A popular belief suggests that Reiki, being a complex process, engages many bodily systems simultaneously and shifts them from sympathetic to the parasympathetic mode of action. That is to say, from ‘fight or flight response to relaxation mode and activates the body healing mechanisms by triggering on a sub-physical level.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Health Benefits of Receiving Reiki</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Reiki is an ancient yet effective therapy that offers promising results. Whether you are receiving Reiki for body ailments, mind relaxation, sleep deprivation, emotional trauma healing or, to enhance immune system response, Reiki exhibits endless health benefits. Let’s familiarize ourselves with the following benefits of receiving this therapy.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Cures Anxiety &amp; Depression</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Are you suffering from depression and anxiety issues for quite a long time? Are you tired of worthless medications and want a permanent stop to these problems? This therapy relieves depression by radiating universal positive vibes in young and older adults. It is effective in alleviating anxiety attacks, enhancing self-care and love.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Relieves Pain &amp; Fatigue</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Do you feel lethargic all the time and often experience body pain? Researches reveal that Reiki is as potent as physiotherapy for relieving lower back pain in patients suffering from a herniated disc. Moreover, it significantly reduces body pain and maintains breathing rate without affecting pulse rate or blood pressure.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Releases Tension &amp; Uplifts Mood</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Reiki session allows your mind to focus on current events without holding onto past mistakes, release muscle tension without fretting on anxieties about the future with its positive vibes. This therapy triggers the self-healing state and purifies your body from negative energies. It stimulates the release of hormones that soothe the jittering nerves and uplifts your mood.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Promotes Body Relaxation</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">What many people love about Reiki is that the magic starts within minutes of therapy. The positive vibe transfer clears your head of anxieties, releases the muscle tension &amp; stress of the day, releases neurotransmitters, and promotes body relaxation. People with this therapy showed impressive results with improved emotional and mental balance.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Alleviates Headache &amp; Migraine</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">How does Reiki work for headache and migraine problems? Is it successful in getting rid of this nerve-wracking and worrisome situation? Reiki takes a non-invasive yet efficient approach when it comes to dealing with headaches. The body releases neurotransmitters and hormones when the practitioner uses hands and transfers energy; thereupon, alleviating the migraine.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Enhances Immune System Response</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Do you have a weak immune system and want to improve it? The positive benefits of Reiki enhance immune system response by invoking the body’s natural healing process.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Furthermore, it reminds your body to develop the guard system, cleanse the toxins from the system and, protect the body from foreign substances.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Treats Insomnia</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">When you receive the therapy, your body loosens and relaxes, and a sense of calmness washes over. Hence, your eyes start drooping and, you feel sleepy. Recent researches revealed that it is effective in improving sleeping patterns &amp; mind relaxation, invigorating self-assurance by releasing hormones from the pituitary.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Effective for Other Issues</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Reiki targets more than one problem within your body by its energy transfer technique. In general, Reiki proves to be successful for diseases like cardiovascular issues, cancer, chorionic fatigue syndrome, infertility. Moreover, this therapy intends to cure disorders that affect your brain including, Parkinson’s or Huntington’s disease.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2806\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Reiki.jpg\" alt=\"About Reiki Treatment\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Reiki.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Reiki-300x200.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Reiki-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Are There Any Side Effects of Reiki?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Now that we figured the questions like what is Reiki? What are its benefits; let’s discuss its side effects. Although it is known to be a safe technique, you can experience the following side effects.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Discomfort Sensation</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">During reiki therapy, you lie on some massage table or stool in a dimly lit room; you need to stay as still as possible with the practitioner standing over your head. Henceforth, some people lose their calm and start getting a discomfort sensation in that atmosphere.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Sudden Drop in Blood Oxygen</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Although not necessary, sometimes the blood oxygen levels drop in patients dealing with any disorder. Researches revealed that some persons also feel dizzy while undergoing therapy.<br>Now the point is; the root problem can be either an inexperienced practitioner or the person itself.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How to Choose a Qualified Reiki Practitioner?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Are you thinking about how to choose a qualified reiki practitioner? Are you unfamiliar with this technique and find it difficult to trust the person? Don’t worry- no reiki trainer needs any particular background or credentials; however, experience matters for performing a therapy session. You can ask your friend who does Reiki, a healthcare professional or simply, look for them in your community.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Furthermore, word of mouth matters if you are looking for a repute reiki practitioner. You can get an appointment with them without a hitch through mobiles numbers and emails.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What Does Research Say About Reiki?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">To make a treatment reputed and recommended, healthcare practitioners need evidence that the treatment is safe and effective. Up to the present time, there have been no reported negative feedbacks related to Reiki and, that speaks volumes. Thus, medical researches include it among the effective therapies for restoring balance and treating ailments.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Furthermore, it regulates homeostasis by maintaining heart and breathing rate, blood pressure, and circulation, acting as a stress buster and anxiety reliever.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How and Where Can I Get Reiki?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Are you looking for the right place to get Reiki? Many medical clinics and hospitals offer reiki therapy. Moreover, suppose you are receiving Reiki for relieving&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.nccih.nih.gov/health/chronic-pain-in-depth\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">chronic pain</a>. In that case, many local groups that help people with fibromyalgia or cancer might help you find some practitioner in your area.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Now comes the question of how to get the right practitioner in the first place? It’s easy; make sure to check the background and working experience of the practitioner during your first visit. In addition, you can also ask them to describe the procedure and, you can make the right choice then.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Is Reiki and Chiropractic Therapy Same?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Let’s familiarize ourselves with chiropractic therapy before we move forward. Chiropractic therapy is a procedure that uses a hands-on approach or a small instrument to improve spinal motion and align the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.dmu.edu/medterms/musculoskeletal-system/musculoskeletal-system-diseases/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">musculoskeletal structures</a>&nbsp;properly. Now comes the question; are Reiki and chiropractic the same thing? Reiki uses an energy transfer procedure to stimulate the body’s natural healing process.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While, on the other hand, chiropractic therapy coaxes the body to release the tension or whatever it’s holding onto( even if it’s emotional tension) that promises more productive results. Now that we differentiated both the therapies, can they be used altogether? If you use Reiki along with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/chiropractic-therapy\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">chiropractic therapy</a>, it can do wonders for your body, and recent researches are living proof of the fact. It helped infertile women, persons dealing with anxiety, stress, and depression issues.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In our guide about ‘What is Reiki’ – were you able to find what you were seeking out? Researches revealed it’s a natural healing procedure that promotes mental and physical relaxation. In short, Reiki has the potential to bring about many impressive benefits with promising results.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">During a session, the practitioner reduces the stress and anxiety by transferring the healing energy that lasts for about 45-90 minutes. We recommend giving it a shot if you are interested even a bit in what it offers.</p>', 15, '3', '2021-11-15 07:47:01', '2021-10-26 00:53:05', '2021-11-15 01:47:01', '10/05/2021 12:52 PM', 'Leonel Escobedo', 'what-is-reiki', 0, 'No');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(56, 'How to Increase Strength: The Easy Ways That You Need to Know', 'how-to-increase-strength-the-easy-ways-that-you-need-to-know', 'How-to-Increase-Strength.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Are you one of those who have understood the value and importance of strength and now looking to gain some strength yourself? Well, as a beginner, it may seem very hard to do strength training. The weights, exercises, managing your body weight, and many cramps that come in the early days are no joke.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">All these can make your motivation go low, and you may have to try harder to hit the gym. But we assure you that if you stay committed, you will only come out happier and stronger. The best part about strength training is that it shows measurable results within a couple of weeks. That means if you stay put on your regime, you will realize how fruitful it is.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Once you get hold of the exercises and move, we assure you that you would start enjoying them all. So right now, if you are struggling to understand where you should start, keep reading.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Why Body Strength Should Be Increased&nbsp; &amp; Its Benefits</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Increasing body strength and working on your muscles can help you much more than just clicking good pictures for the gram. Yes, a photogenic body is a big plus point, but strength training has other significant benefits.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Strength training or resistance training keeps you fit and healthy for a long time. Combining strength training with a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/healthy-gut-diet-plan\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">special diet plan</a>&nbsp;can help you lose weight as muscle activation causes more burning of fat.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Not to forget, with a healthy body, you also have&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.niams.nih.gov/health-topics/kids/healthy-muscles\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">strong muscles</a>&nbsp;now. As the muscles get strong, they can prevent you from a lot of injuries.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Weak muscles are more inclined towards injuries. So, as you age, the strength of your muscles becomes much more beneficial. It helps you improve your balance, reduces the risk of falling, and, most importantly,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/build-healthy-bones\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">builds bone density</a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The best part about strength training is its helps to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/maintaining-a-healthy-lifestyle\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">maintain a healthy lifestyle</a>. That means, once you get the desired shape of your body and muscles, you can hit the gym for three days a week, and it would be enough to keep the shape intact.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How to Get Trained to Increase Your Strength</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As you are aiming to increase your overall strength in the body, understand that one exercise regime may not do the job for you. To gain a significant amount of strength, you can start with a combination of movements.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As a starter, you can add bodyweight exercises. The bodyweight exercises like pushups, squats, and planks can help you strengthen your muscles of both the upper and lower body.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Further, an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/about-plank-exercise\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">exercise like plank</a>&nbsp;can strengthen your core. Once you get hold of the bodyweight regime, then maybe add a pair of dumbbells or kettlebells in your regime.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You can do some squats with extra weight or maybe add any deadlift form in your regime. The extra weight would help you to maintain balance and will make your muscles strong.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Some other&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-weight-training\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">examples of strength training</a>&nbsp;exercises include squats, standing overhead presses, pushups, dips, bench presses, barbell box step-ups, and glute bridges. Common pulling exercises include rows and pull-ups.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Provide yourself two-five minutes of rest between sets to permit adequate recovery for your apprehensive framework and muscles. Otherwise, another set will enormously get affected.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You may not be able to maximize your exertion and concentrate on the ensuing set. This may sound like a part of rest on the off chance you’ve utilized to take after other programs. Still, it’s reasonably standard for a workout that’s centered particularly on picking up quality.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Lastly, perform one to three sets per exercise if you’re a beginner. Perform three to five sets for each movement as you become stronger.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Allow 48 hours of recovery (that is, no other heavy lifting of those muscle groups you worked) between workouts.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2754\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/increase-strength.jpg\" alt=\"increase strength\" width=\"620\" height=\"349\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/increase-strength.jpg 620w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/increase-strength-300x169.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/increase-strength-400x225.jpg 400w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/increase-strength-600x338.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Best Exercise to Increase and&nbsp;Maintain Your Strength</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If you are looking to start strength training, maybe we can guide you on where to start and what exercises you should do in the beginning.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Squats</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Squats are one of the best lower-body movements. The movement activates the muscles of the hips, thighs, and calves at the same time. It is a good bodyweight exercise for the beginner.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Once you get hold of this exercise, you can add some extra weight like a dumbbell and then perform squats while holding weight. Holding a barbell, you can do back squats or front squats. Exercise is the best movement, especially if you want to work on your lower body.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Single-Leg Moves</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Whether you are doing a single-left deadlift or single-leg step up, understand that single-leg moves help maintain balance in your body. It strengthens the muscles of your legs.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">A lot of core balance is required to make single-leg moves. So it helps in the movement of the core as well. Start with this movement if you aim to balance the body on one leg and make your legs stronger.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Bent-Over Row</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This exercise can be a great indicator of strength. For this movement, you would need a pair of dumbbells. Once you have your dumbbells, understand that the exercise aims to strengthen your upper body.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It activates the muscles of the chest, biceps, and shoulders. For this specific movement, you also need to place your legs and hips in a certain position. Thus, it puts a bit of pressure on the lower body as well.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Pushups</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The exercise does not require you to hit the gym or have fancy equipment around you. Rather it is just your body weight providing you with strength. Pushups can be tricky and difficult at the start.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However, an easy way to perform them as beginners is to place your hands on a chair or a bit upper surface than the floor. The more your hands would be placed high. The easier pushups would become for you. The movement focuses on your upper body, chest muscles, triceps, and arms.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Gluts Bridge</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Bridges target one of the biggest muscles in the lower half—the glutes. They’re also a major contributor to the development of power from the legs and core stabilization.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">So if your aim is towards making the body that has abs, or you aim to have a significant amount of strength in your lower body, this movement is for you.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Furthermore, for this movement, you would need a pair of dumbbells that you will place on your upper thighs while the elevation of your hips.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Hollow Body Hold</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This movement is primarily focusing on strengthening your core. It teaches you how a simple body movement can create tension in your body muscles. If your core is strengthened, it can help you a lot with other movements such as pushups and deadlifts.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">So this is one of the most important movements in strength training. As a beginner, if you cannot hold a traditional hollow body, you can modify it by bending your knees or moving your hands forward instead of overhead.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Deadlift</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The deadlift is the best exercise to strengthen your glutes and hamstrings. This is also a strength training exercise that you can measure. As you get hold of the exercise, you can always increase its difficulty level by adding weights to your dumbbells.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As you are standing in a firm position, it does not only help your back. It can strengthen your shoulder and chest muscles because the dumbbells are in your hands.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Moreover, it can also place a significant amount of pressure on your calves and hip muscles which can help you build your lower body. So as a beginner, we recommend you add this exercise to your strength training regime.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">To conclude, we can say that now you know where you should start. The above reading provides complete guidance for a beginner-level trainee. Understand that staying committed and consistent is the key.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If you are aiming to build muscles and strength, you need to stay firm. As a beginner, try to perform the above regime at least four to five times a week. Once you see your muscles’ differences and growth, you may hit the gym for three to four days a week.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As a beginner, you may find strength training very difficult. To make the training easy for you, modify the difficult movements a bit. As you get hold of the exercises, you can return to the traditional way of those specific movements.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">We recommend you to do them with an instructor who can guide you best according to your body needs and individual requirements.</p>', 15, '3', '2021-11-15 07:47:13', '2021-10-26 00:55:40', '2021-11-25 03:19:42', '09/28/2021 12:55 PM', 'Leonel Escobedo', 'how-to-increase-strength', 1, 'No'),
(57, 'What is Cardio? Here’s All What You Need to Know', 'what-is-cardio-heres-all-what-you-need-to-know', 'What-is-Cardio.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">When you talk to your friends about shedding some extra pounds, do they use the phrase “you should do cardio”? If yes, then this article discusses all the nitty-gritty details about Cardio. Still, before we move on, we need to know the answer to the question “what is cardio.”&nbsp;&nbsp;There are different techniques that could be incorporated into your daily routine. This form of exercise is loaded with a plethora of benefits. They can prove to be very helpful in losing weight and staying fit.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Furthermore, you can learn about various exercises that could be followed at home and are already a part of your daily routine. So, without any further delay, let’s get to know all about Cardio exercise.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What is Cardio Exercise?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You might have heard about aerobic exercise in your PE class or the gym or yoga center; it is basically a synonym for Cardio exercise. It is an excellent way to burn extra body fat and achieve your desired weight. This form of exercise works by boosting your heart rate to such an extent where your heart enters a targeted zone that is optimal for weight loss and fat burning.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If you are wondering that how Cardio is different from other exercises then, know that it involves an additional perk of strength training, which implies that the oxygen in the body is used while you are working out. Your ability to indulge in cardio exercises is influenced by genetics; hence it varies from person to person. However, note that women tend to have a lower Cardio work outdrive as compared to men.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">When answering the question of what cardio is, keep in mind that any exercise that enhances your heart rate and pumps blood fast is categorized as Cardio. The process works by delivering oxygen to your muscles, and the benefit of cardio exercise is that it can enhance the capacity of your body to lose weight fast.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Cardio exercise accompanies a plethora of benefits, and the topmost benefit is that it helps you in staying fit and losing weight. Cardio includes many different exercises such as high-intensity training and resistance training etc., that boosts your work outdrive. Not only do these exercises focus on weight loss, but they are an excellent way to improve your efficiency and keep you active.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/healthy-gut-diet-plan\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">you need to focus on your diet</a>&nbsp;as well if you want to get even better results from your Cardio exercise. It is essential to incorporate fruits, veggies, grains, etc., and lean proteins in your diet in order to lose weight fast and in a healthy way.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Why Do You Need Cardio Exercise as a Beginner?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Are you a newbie who wants to try some exercise to energize your body? If so, then let’s talk about the need to indulge in&nbsp;cardio exercise for beginners.&nbsp;You need to start with this form of exercise as it will promote stamina, and it will give you enough energy to move to various high-level strength training exercises. It is good to start with Cardio because it can help you in many ways.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">For instance, if you have never exercised in your life and want to incorporate this imperative part of life into your routine, then&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/best-indoor-cardio-workout\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Cardio is the best workout for you</a>. To add on, if you are someone who has been out of touch and has not exercised in a long while, but wants to get back to working out, then Cardio is the best starting buddy for you.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Further, as a beginner, you need this form of exercise because this is neither a light nor a very harsh form of exercise. It can help you boost your stamina to adopt a more rigorous regime gradually. Also, if you want to stay fit but you do not like cycling or swimming, you can adopt cardio methods to stay fit and in shape. Various practices like squats and lunges are great for strengthening your muscles and staying in shape. This makes it perfect for beginners.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">A-List for Best Types of Cardio Exercises That You Should Know</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Through this article, you would be able to identify the need to add cardio exercises to your daily routine, along with getting to know about “what is cardio.” It helps in weight management, guards you against various heart-related issues, improves your mood, and helps you live a happy, healthy life. Here is a&nbsp;list of cardio exercises&nbsp;that you need to know while starting Cardio:</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Skipping Rope</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Do you remember the last time you jumped rope? If your answer is no, you need to grab a rope and incorporate jumping rope into your daily routine. It is a great cardio exercise, and your entire body is indulged in this exercise, leading to faster weight loss. If you want to increase the difficulty level of your exercise, then try adding some weight to your back by wearing a backpack or suitcase while exercising.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Dancing</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Another easy yet effective form of Cardio is dancing. However, note that it does not involved your freestyle dancing, instead try to indulge in Zumba and move your body. Dancing, just like skipping rope, is great for involving your entire body in action. It can be highly effective in losing weight and staying fit and happy.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Sports</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Do you not want to go to the gym? No problem, try doing Cardio at home; Cardio does not essentially mean working out. You can simply indulge in your favorite sport like playing football or basketball for a few minutes daily. This is also categorized as Cardio, and it is an easy form to incorporate into your daily routine.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">When you play sports, your entire body is involved. It certainly increases your heart rate, which is the primary goal of Cardio. In addition, if you simply run around in a park or the football field for a few minutes, you would be able to stimulate your heart rate and enter the fat-burning zone.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Power Walking</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As mentioned above, it has been established that you do not need any fancy equipment or gym to incorporate Cardio in your daily routine. A task as simple as power walking is also a part of cardio exercises. If you take some time out of your routine and go for a walk where you walk briskly for some time at a fast pace, you would be able to burn many calories, and through this form of Cardio, you would be able to develop enough stamina to move to more heavy exercises.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Swimming</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Another mild form of Cardio that can accelerate your heart rate is swimming. It is a great type of workout as it can help you in toning your body while protecting your joints. However, if you are scared of swimming or are not a pro swimmer, then get yourself a kickboard and get to work, as this would involve your legs as well as your abs in the workout.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Many other forms of basic tasks, such as cycling, hiking, etc., are a part of cardio exercises that can give you initial strength and stamina to boost your work outdrive and engage yourself in heavy exercises.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2737\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Cardio.jpg\" alt=\"A women is doing Cardio\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Cardio.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Cardio-300x200.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Cardio-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How to Picks the Best Cardio Exercises</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Once you know about various forms of cardio exercises, it is integral to note that what type of cardio exercise is the best for you. Make sure that before you indulge in Cardio, you figure out the specific form of exercise that suits your body requirements and needs.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Cardio is not just about getting in shape; it is rather about staying fit by choosing a form of exercise that is easy, as well as enjoyable for you to add to your life. But why is it essential to enjoy Cardio, you ask? It is essential because if you do not like your exercise, you would not be able to stay consistent.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Keeping in mind the aforementioned point, choose wisely. For example, if you like to indulge in outdoor activities, then go for activities like running, cycling, walking, jumping, etc., as your cardio exercise. Whilst, if you are a gym-lover, then you should be more active in the gym and go for HITT training, treadmill, climbers, etc.; on the other hand, if you want to do&nbsp;cardio exercise at home&nbsp;then, you can for exercises like jogging in one place, jumping jacks, squats burpees, etc.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Initially, you may struggle a bit in finding your favorite workout routine but worry not. Just try various forms of cardio exercises and stick to the one you like the best. Please spend some time and try to find the best workout plan that fits your body needs and get to it.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Benefits of Cardio Exercises</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Given the aforementioned debate, cardio exercises can be immensely beneficial for people of all genders and ages. Not only is it good for weight loss, but it has numerous other health benefits that make it an ideal workout regime to add to your daily life. As established above, it could be seen that cardio exercises are great for burning fat and calories.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Hence, it is ideal for weight loss. Furthermore, one of the many&nbsp;benefits of cardio exercise&nbsp;is that it improves your sleep quality. If you are battling any sleep disorders, Cardio can help you acquire a good night’s sleep.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If you want to boost your sex life and sex drive, you must work out and incorporate cardio exercise in your daily routine. Through cardio exercise, your body would have a better chance at arousal. You would be able to get rid of any sexual dysfunction. Moreover, it is immensely efficacious in improving your lung capacity and increasing the capacity of air that your lung could hold.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In addition, if you feel fatigued throughout the day, then indulging in cardio exercise is an excellent way to give your body a boost of energy and helps you maintain your confidence. When you would stay in shape, you would certainly be finding your confidence and look your best self.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Moving on, it can keep you from developing risks of various hazardous diseases like heart problems, high blood pressure, diabetes, etc. It is seen to be very beneficial in protecting yourself against heart issues. It can lower your stress level and promote optimism.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How Does Cardio Exercise Burn Your Fat?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You must be wondering that there is a lot of content about Cardio exercises, but is this form of workout even credible? Therefore, to clear your confusion, the following studies can assist us in finding pertinent evidence that Cardio is very productive in burning fat.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Cardio helps in burning calories, and it helps by creating a calorie deficit which refers to the process where you are involved in burning more calories than you eat. As per many studies, you need to eat a balanced diet and indulge in cardio exercises if you want to burn fat.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">According to research, fast metabolic rate and fat burning are two deeply connected processes, supporting the latter. The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.healthline.com/health/what-is-basal-metabolic-rate\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">basal Metabolic rate</a>&nbsp;or BMR is a function that requires energy from your body to repair cells in the body and to improve your heart functions.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The main factors to influence your BMR include your sex, age, the muscular mass, etc. Alongside this, your body needs to stay active and indulge in activities so that it is able to absorb all the energy and burn the extra calories. Hence, it is proved by reaches that physical activities and Cardio go hand in hand if you want to lose weight.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How to Do Cardio Workouts at Home</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As discussed above, we have established that you can indulge in cardio workouts at home. There are several things that you would need to work out at home. You need to be persistent and follow a proper regime if you want to lose weight. At home, you can practice exercises like lunges, squats, push-ups, and various other workouts.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Moreover, you can segregate your workout into different days. For example, you can combine an entire circuit of leg exercises and follow those sets on a particular day. Likewise, you can make different circuits for the arm, belly, and lower body and practice them on various days.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Many exercises can be done in homes when it comes to Cardio. It is perfect for finding some simple exercises that could be practiced at home. Here is a list of cardio exercises that would be done at your homes without any equipment:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Squats</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Knee highs</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Mountain Climbers</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Burpee</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Stair sprints</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/about-plank-exercise\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Planks</a></li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Lunges</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Donkey Kicks etc.</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Are Cardio and Weight Training Same?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Many people&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-weight-training\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">think of weight training</a>&nbsp;and Cardio as the same. However, in reality, these two are not the same. Note that, even though they are not the same, Cardio and weight lifting can be a deadly combo against stubborn fat that you want to shed. Many of you might be confused about whether to focus on Cardio or weight lifting. So, the best solution to this problem is to compile both of these workouts and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.health.harvard.edu/staying-healthy/major-fat-burning-discovery\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">fat-burning methods</a>&nbsp;into one routine.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Through many types of research, it has been found that the impact of Cardio on weight loss outperforms the result of weight training. Despite the fact that weight training can boost your resistance and strength, Cardio works to strengthen the muscles of your entire body.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">To sum up, this article presents a small guide for anyone who is interested in knowing all about Cardio. This article is a crystal-clear depiction of everything related to cardio exercises. It tells us how we can employ various cardio exercises to lower your weight and reach your optimum weight. Moreover, cardio exercises are linked with many health benefits that can improve your overall health and keep you healthy and fit.</p>', 15, '3', '2021-11-15 07:47:26', '2021-10-26 01:17:22', '2021-12-08 04:48:20', '11/01/2021 1:16 PM', 'Leonel Escobedo', 'what-is-cardio', 30, 'No');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(58, 'LIFESTYLE Ways to Prepare Lawn for Winters: 7 Simple Tips', 'lifestyle-ways-to-prepare-lawn-for-winters-7-simple-tips', 'Ways-to-Prepare-Your-Lawn-for-Winter.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If you love lush gardens and greenery, it is imperative to search for ways to prepare your lawn for winter. Starting right in winters is a big no because it would take some time to prepare your lawn. Hence, the best time to commence the work on your lawn is the fall season. This would provide your lawn with enough time to flourish and grow. The key to getting the perfect lawn in winters is to plan and mow your lawn in autumn.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Best Ways to Prepare Your Lawn for Winter</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are many ways that you can use to bring improvements to your existing lawn or prepare for one for the winter season. So, let’s talk about some of the best ways to prepare your lawn for winter. If you live in a cooler region, then these techniques would immensely help you prepare your lawn for winter.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Clean the Leaves, Debris, and Thatch</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Basic measures must be taken before we reach the major steps to prepare your lawn for starters. It is integral to clean your lawn of all the debris, leaves, and thatch; otherwise, it would become very hard to start preparing for your lawn. Fall is the perfect weather for achieving a beautiful lawn with a lot of greenery. Nevertheless, it accompanies a lot of debris that can pose a hindrance when it comes to the preparation of your lawn. So, before you dive in, make sure to clean your lawn and remove all the leaves and sticks and other material because, in snow-capped lawns, there is a higher probability that debris-filled lawns attract more rodents.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Remove Weeds and Moss</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Another issue that can happen in your lawn is the development of moss in the area where the sunlight does not reach. The places where moss starts reducing give a great reseeding opportunity for the growth of new grass. If the soil is not&nbsp;<a href=\"https://theturfgrassgroup.com/turf-maintenance/lawn-care-with-beer-and-soap-these-are-the-top-nutrients-grass-needs-to-grow/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">nutritious for grass growth</a>, moss may also develop in that region. Hence, it is essential to deprive that area of moss before the preparation of grass. Moreover, ensure that you have all the needed types of equipment for raking out the weed. Moss and weed need to be removed, or they can ruin your grass and soil value.<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3382\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Ways-to-Prepare-Your-Lawn-for-Winter-BB.jpg\" alt=\"Prepare Lawn for Winters\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Ways-to-Prepare-Your-Lawn-for-Winter-BB.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Ways-to-Prepare-Your-Lawn-for-Winter-BB-300x188.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Ways-to-Prepare-Your-Lawn-for-Winter-BB-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Keep Your Grass Short</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">After you have started preparing your lawn, make sure that you keep the grass short, as it will help it thrive in a better way. The ideal length for your grass is between 1 to 1.5 inches. The real reason for keeping it short is that long grass can serve as a home to many rodents. Hence, keep it short if you want a perfect lawn.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Your Lawn Should Be Trimmed</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Just like your hair needs a good trim to look healthy, grass needs the same treatment. In winters, the grass is subjected to many issues like snow, etc., so in order to keep the grass healthy, it is important to trim it. This step would assist in damage control during the winter season.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Apply Fertilizer for Winter</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Fertilizers are food for your grass. As the human body needs food to survive, grass needs fertilizers. The fertilizers are packed with all the essential nutrients. Mainly the roots of the grass are in dire need of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cms.leoncountyfl.gov/waterresource/Protecting-and-Preserving-Our-Water-Quality/Pollution-Prevention/Fertilizer-Guidance\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">fertilization during the winters</a>. The aeration method would ensure that the fertilizers reach the root system of the grass and give it all the vital nutrients for growth.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Give a Break to Sprinklers</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is essential to modify your sprinkler settings because failing to change the setting or winterizing your sprinkler can result in major issues related to the repair of your system. Leakage in pipes or other issues in your sprinklers can damage your lawn. Therefore, it is essential to follow your instruction manual to ensure your sprinklers’ settings and reduce any plausible damage.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Give a Good Fall Seeding and Watering</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">After taking all the necessary steps, you reach the last one, where you finally get your lawn ready for winter. Once you have cleared the lawn and removed all the shrubs, moss, weed, etc., it is ready for seeding and watering. It is a good idea to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.extension.iastate.edu/news/2008/aug/081402.htm\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">overseed your lawn</a>&nbsp;initially in the fall to cover the soil quickly. This will improve germination and result in lush green grass. Then comes the step of watering, which is acute for the growth of your grass. Water your grass to keep it fresh and to keep your lawn green.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">The Bottom Line</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Winters can be pretty harsh for your lawn, and there is a fair chance that winter may damage your lawn and leave yellow patches. Thus, it is crucial to maintain your lawn and look after it. Preventative measures are needed to ensure the well-being of your lawn and ensure that it is lusher and stronger than before.</p>', 16, '3', '2021-11-15 07:47:46', '2021-10-26 01:25:38', '2021-11-15 01:47:46', '11/02/2021 1:24 PM', 'Kiprono Langat', 'ways-to-prepare-your-lawn-for-winter', 0, 'No'),
(59, 'What is Extrinsic Motivation? Examples, Effectiveness, and It’s Important', 'what-is-extrinsic-motivation-examples-effectiveness-and-its-important', 'What-Is-Extrinsic-Motivation.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Motivation is an integral part of human needs, as it works as a major driver for people to work effectively. Motivation can be either intrinsic or extrinsic, but what is extrinsic motivation? This motivation is achieved through external factors, such as some particular kind of reward or money. This concept is opposite to intrinsic motivation, which comes from within and individuals and provokes his capacity to work.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The perfect combination of these types of motivations will help an individual perform most efficiently and achieve the set goal within no time.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-motivation/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Motivation is needed in day to day life of every individual</a>, may it be a minute task of working out or a huge task within an organization of achieving a sales task.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What Is Extrinsic Motivation?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">When it comes to the concept of what is extrinsic motivation, it is obtained from purely outer means, and it is a type of external motivation. This kind of motivation is not linked to achieving a level of inner satisfaction. Still, extrinsic motivation is achieved to gain the reward of money or external means merely.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The reward is gained in return for not inner satisfaction but to gain material satisfaction. As this is gained for your material satisfaction, the outcome may vary with the level of your desire and vigor to complete the task. It can be stemmed from happiness or fear, but no inner satisfaction or inner motivation is involved in this process.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How Does Extrinsic Motivation Work?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Intrinsic and extrinsic motivation go hand in hand to achieve the utmost success level and get work done on time. Even though&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/intrinsic-motivation/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">intrinsic motivation takes the lead</a>&nbsp;here, as it comes from within, external or extrinsic motivation is also important as it gives maximum results when used properly.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The reward derived through this extrinsic motivation would help you achieve a good feeling, and this would be short-lived, and then it would trigger you to achieve a higher reward in the future; hence, the extrinsic motivation, even though it is just material, would instigate you to achieve a higher level. At some point, the feeling of accomplishment might vanish, and monotony in the task may take over.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Examples of Extrinsic Motivation</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are many examples of external or extrinsic motivation that will help you better understand the concept. You will be able to realize the importance of this kind of motivation. Starting with a very basic example, why do you think that students work hard in their exams? They certainly do that to achieve a good grade and attain a good position in their class.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Moreover, the students in the school sports teams and the players in the international football leagues work for the same purpose of achieving extrinsic satisfaction of either winning a gold medal in school or getting paid millions of dollars in rewards, respectively.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3165\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Extrinsic-Motivation.jpg\" alt=\"Extrinsic-Motivation\" width=\"800\" height=\"390\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Extrinsic-Motivation.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Extrinsic-Motivation-300x146.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Extrinsic-Motivation-768x374.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In addition, many people keep buying from the same shop to earn money credits and earn a loyalty card that will offer them discounts on further purchases. In many households, parents incentivize their children to clean their room and help their parents in their daily chores. Hence, this is purely an example of extrinsic motivation.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Effectiveness of Extrinsic Motivation</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">When it comes to the effectiveness and importance of extrinsic motivation, it can be immensely effective if done right. Let’s not go further and ponder over the examples near us; we can find myriads that show that we have done several things to get a reward in terms of material aspects.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In many firms, the employees are incentivized through monetary rewards to enhance their productivity. Many employees perform effectively while completing even the most boring tasks when it comes to monetary incentives. However, one thing to be noticed here is that extrinsic rewards may often backfire and may decrease the efficacy of intrinsic rewards.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How to Do Extrinsic Motivation</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The assessment of the situation is an immensely important task for motivating people to work in a better way. This method could be for employees when the employees are least interested in the task and when people fail to meet the work requirements.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In addition, if the business is training the employees to get started and gain expertise in a particular skill, the tool of extrinsic motivation can prove to be highly effective. Lastly, when the intensity of the task is immensely higher and needs immediate results, the company offers extrinsic rewards to its employees.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Why is Extrinsic Motivation Important?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Through past researches, it has been seen that intrinsic motivation is more important than extrinsic motivation. It often lowers the quality and creativity of the employees as all their interest lies in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pubag.nal.usda.gov/catalog/768580\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">extrinsic rewards</a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Nevertheless, despite many loopholes, this type of importance could be gauged from the fact that extrinsic rewards can be very effective when it comes to completing monotonous tasks.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is much needed in the sectors like workplaces and education. Further, in some cases, where intrinsic motivation fails, extrinsic motivation comes into play and helps in yielding results.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Extrinsic motivation In Parenting</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In Parenting, extrinsic motivation holds a great place. We see many parents motivating their children to work hard or perform better in school by offering them various prices and rewards. For example, when parents want their children to excel in their studies, they promise them various rewards to better their grades.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Similarly, when parents want their children to clean their rooms or garden, they offer a piece of cake, their favorite game or monetary reward to get the task done.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Extrinsic Motivation in Organizations</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Many management and motivation theories have talked about monetary rewards that fall under the category of extrinsic rewards. Salary is the fixed compensation, but many organizations offer bonuses to their employees to retain their effectiveness and efficacy.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Apart from that, holiday entitlements, etc. are other perks that fall under extrinsic rewards. The basic motive of offering these rewards is that the employees will be able to show better performance when they know about the money offered to them for their efforts.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As every individual has a variable potential and is searching for a different kind of motivation, may it be intrinsic or extrinsic? Both these types are great in yielding a better motivation level. They can help individuals test their potential and yield better results.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Not only is the motivation needed in the organization or the education system, but every person also requires some level of motivation to excel in their life and achieve even the bare minimum.</p>', 16, '3', '2021-11-15 07:48:08', '2021-10-26 01:30:14', '2021-11-15 01:48:08', '09/28/2021 1:29 PM', 'Kiprono Langat', 'extrinsic-motivation', 0, 'No'),
(60, 'All You Need to Know About Intrinsic Motivation', 'all-you-need-to-know-about-intrinsic-motivation', 'What-Is-Intrinsic-Motivation.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Intrinsic Motivation is all about Motivation coming from within. You don’t think about external rewards in such a case but all your drive to get up and work depends upon you. Now how it works and what it is a very important factor to understand. The following reading will take you step by step. Starting from the very basics of intrinsic Motivation is important. Moving forward, we can look at the theories that support the concept of intrinsic Motivation.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The difference between extrinsic and intrinsic Motivation is also important and is explained with the help of examples. There are different aspects of life like work, home, and parenting where the concept comes in handy. The following reading explores all these aspects and comes in handy for people who would like to practice it in their life.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What is Intrinsic Motivation?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The word intrinsic means coming from nature. The term intrinsic refers to the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-motivation/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Motivation</a>&nbsp;that comes from within. The strong drive to get up and pursue something not to gain the reward but to achieve that satisfaction is intrinsic Motivation. Intrinsic Motivation is a concept which states that to be successful, a person first needs to fulfill some inner needs.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Once the inner needs of a human being are fulfilled, one can move forward and look out for rewards and other external factors. Along with the satisfaction of internal psychological and biological needs, intrinsic Motivation also involves engaging in a task that is challenging and seems fun to an individual. It may differ and can be relative for different human beings.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3177\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/What-Is-Intrinsic-Motivation-b.jpg\" alt=\"Intrinsic Motivation\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/What-Is-Intrinsic-Motivation-b.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/What-Is-Intrinsic-Motivation-b-300x188.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/What-Is-Intrinsic-Motivation-b-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Theories of Intrinsic Motivation</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">One of the most important intrinsic motivation theories is Maslow’s hierarchy of needs. The hierarchy of needs defines that an individual always needs to fulfill his psychological, biological, and sexual desires before any external reward. If the task is presented and it fulfills the above requirement of an individual, they would be intrinsically motivated and do that without acknowledging a lot of external rewards attached to it.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Another theory that supports this concept can be the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.urmc.rochester.edu/community-health/patient-care/self-determination-theory.aspx\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">self-determination theory</a>. This theory states that the person’s need for autonomy and competence and triggers their intrinsic Motivation. The feeling of competence is one of the most significant factors, according to a lot of studies. The autonomy that you feel when you complete a difficult task also plays a part here.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Intrinsic Motivation vs. Extrinsic Motivation: What’s the Difference?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Intrinsic Motivation allows you to complete the task that fulfills your biological and psychological needs without any external reward. You do such tasks merely because you enjoy them, they feel challenging and make you feel empowered.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">On the other hand,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/extrinsic-motivation/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">extrinsic Motivation involves a task that has an external reward</a>&nbsp;attached to it. You would get motivated to do such tasks because the reward for them is important to you personally. The focus, in this case, is primarily on the outcome. The outcome could be money, recognition, or power that you may get after a task.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Examples of Intrinsic Motivation</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The following could be a good example of intrinsic Motivation.</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You are choosing an accounting major because you enjoy playing with numbers. (At this point, you don’t care about the job opportunities)</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Reading a biography of your favorite personality because you will enjoy reading through their journey.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Going for a walk to clear your head rather than&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/healthyweight/losing_weight/index.html\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">losing weight</a>.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Telling your friend that you are thankful to show your gratitude rather than following the social ethics of saying it.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Preparing your meal because it gives you satisfaction and not because you have to do it.</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Intrinsic Motivation in Organizations</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Intrinsic Motivation plays a huge role in organizations. If you are in an organization, you will get paid for the work you do. But at the same time, if you are working in a field that is your passion, intrinsic Motivation gets involved. For example, you are a singer who is working with a firm to produce a song.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The song that you sing and make would get you money, but at the same time, more than the money, you are involved in it because you are enjoying the song, and singing gives you inner satisfaction. In that case, intrinsic motivation derives from collaborating with the firm more than the money you will get for singing.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Intrinsic Motivation in Parenting</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Parents often use the reward to get their kids to do the homework or eat their veggies. However, there are ways through which you can motivate them intrinsically to get their work done. Rather than telling them&nbsp;<a href=\"https://psycnet.apa.org/record/2018-22169-002\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">about the reward</a>, tell them more about the activity and the ways through which they can enjoy it. Give them a choice.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The power to choose to make people feel that they are in control of their life. This factor can motivate kids to work and choose the option that they enjoy more. Lastly, make the tasks fun for them. Turn their reading into a game or them cleaning a room as a fun activity. This would allow them to start enjoying the task.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Intrinsic Motivation in Education</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In the education sector, the focus is usually on the grades that you get at the end. However, intrinsic Motivation can play a huge role here too. What if you choose a subject not for the grade but on the factor that you enjoy it? The studies would become much more fun. The motivation level to study will also change.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In the same way, rather than taking a class for attendance, if you go to class because you have affiliation with your classmates, this can motivate you to take the class. The Motivation to take the class in such a case will come not from the reward but from the internal association you have with your peers.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Why is Intrinsic Motivation Good for Every Age?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Intrinsic Motivation is good for everyone, whether making a child clean the room or a young adult going for the class. Intrinsic Motivation makes people persistent in what they do. They have a personal commitment to the task now. You are more committed now; thus, the chances to become successful at what you do increases. Creativity can also increase due to intrinsic Motivation since now you are doing the task with all your brain.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How to Practice Intrinsic Motivation Perfectly</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You can practice intrinsic Motivation in the following ways.</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Don’t think of your work as a “duty.” Rather involve your feelings and think of it as a personal commitment.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Make the work fun.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Don’t stress over it, and don’t think about the outcomes.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Focus on the present rather than the future.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Learn from the mistakes rather than getting frustrated from them.</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Intrinsic Motivation is a fun concept. It is fascinating how it can make a task easier and much more enjoyable for individuals. Intrinsic Motivation is the core concept that one needs to understand. If you practice it, the external baggage and extra stress will never bother you. You can live in the moment and would be fully committed to your present rather than thinking about the future a lot.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You can practice intrinsic Motivation in daily life whether you are a parent, a student, or an employee at a multinational. Intrinsic Motivation makes a person more committed and persistent over their work. Thus, the chances of them being successful also increase in the long run.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">References</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://www.verywellmind.com/what-is-intrinsic-motivation-2795385</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://www.healthline.com/health/intrinsic-motivation</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://www.healthline.com/health/intrinsic-motivation#extrinsic-motivation</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://www.parentingforbrain.com/intrinsic-motivation/</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://corporatefinanceinstitute.com/resources/careers/soft-skills/intrinsic-motivation/</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://www.healthline.com/health/intrinsic-motivation#in-parenting</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://www.verywellmind.com/what-is-intrinsic-motivation-2795385</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">https://www.healthline.com/health/intrinsic-motivation#in-practice</li></ul>', 16, '3', '2021-11-15 07:48:34', '2021-10-26 01:33:22', '2021-11-15 01:48:34', '09/27/2021 1:32 PM', 'Leonel Escobedo', 'intrinsic-motivation', 0, 'Yes');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(61, 'What is Motivation? Types, Theories, Features, Uses, and Impacts', 'what-is-motivation-types-theories-features-uses-and-impacts', 'What-is-Motivation.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Human beings are not passive by default. It is in our nature to thrive hard and get what we want. Some of us get exactly what we want, and some of us may have to wait a little more than others. But have you ever thought that what trait in you makes you want the thing that you need most? Or the trait which makes you put in the effort?</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is motivation deep down in you that makes you keep going on the same path to achieve the desired results. Motivation is the key component that differentiates us human beings from pandas. The following reading talks about the motivation, reason for motivation, how it works, and its impact.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What is Motivation?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Motivation is a crucial concept to understand. It is the force that helps us to keep our goal-oriented behavior alive. It initiates and guides us towards the best possible path which can take us to our goal.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Furthermore, motivation is the driving force that activates our cognitive, learning, and emotional behavior. Whether you want to get up and shower or make a movie, the internal driving force that helps you achieve both goals is motivation.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">What exactly lies behind motivation? Well, you will get a lot of answers to this question. Some theorists come up with motivation theories where they argue and give factors that motivate. On the other hand, some psychologists would present you with cognitive facts and psychological makeup responsible for the difference in motivation among individuals.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How Motivation Works</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If we talk biologically, the hormone dopamine in our brain gets us motivated. The imaginary happiness of reward that one would get after they achieve their goal produces dopamine. The dopamine, in return, activates certain nerves in our brain, which makes us put in the effort.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Without motivation, the work done wouldn’t contain our whole effort and dedication. Motivated people put in their true potential in work, which greatly impacts the quality of work. Motivation does not only increase the quality of work, but at the same time, it increases productivity and efficiency.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3170 size-full\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/What-is-Motivation-B.jpg\" alt=\"Motivation Tips\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/What-is-Motivation-B.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/What-is-Motivation-B-300x188.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/What-is-Motivation-B-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Types of Motivation</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The motivation primarily can be of two types. These are:</p><ol style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/intrinsic-motivation/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Intrinsic motivation</a></li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\"><a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/extrinsic-motivation/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Extrinsic motivation</a></li></ol><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Intrinsic motivation refers to the motivation that an individual gets from the inside. For example, you solve a very difficult sum of math. Once your brain got the idea that you can do it, you would feel the driving force and happiness. This driving force would make you solve the whole exercise, and at the same time, you would start enjoying your homework. Intrinsic motivation depends on a person’s mental processes, cognitive reactions, and willpower.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">On the contrary to this, extrinsic motivation stands. This motivation is the one that you get externally. For example, someone’s story of success inspires you because you were able to relate to them. This inspiration would activate your motivational behavior. Music, ted talks, motivational quotes, and movies can be the example of extrinsic motivation.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Why is Motivation Important?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Motivation helps us to get a better insight into&nbsp;<a href=\"https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/human-nature/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">human nature</a>. It is important for success. It is important for inner happiness, and most importantly, it is very important for satisfaction. An individual does not only need the motivation to get materialistic things or to achieve a goal.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Rather, it plays an important role in developing the self-confidence of the individual. It is also very important in building the internal self of the person. Motivated behavior allows you to compete with the world, get hold of the situation, and make difficult decisions. Thus, motivation is very important for the individual who wants to grow as a human being and professional.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Theories of Motivation</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are a lot of theories that you would find on motivation. The famous theories that you must have listened about are Maslow’s hierarchy of needs, McClelland’s acquired needs, The Hawthorne effect, and Vroom’s theory of expectancy. All these theories explain what the factors that motivate human beings are.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">For instance, Vroom’s theory of expectancy says that the level of expectations that people have from an individual is responsible for the motivation level in that person. On the other hand, Maslow’s hierarchy of needs explains how human beings are born with motivation and how biological and social factors play a role.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Features of Motivation</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The main features of motivation are listed below.</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Motivation is goal-oriented</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Motivation is a continuous process</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Motivation may be monetary or non-monetary</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Motivation is a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4675534/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">psychological phenomenon</a>&nbsp;that converts abilities into performance.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Motivation may be positive or negative</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Motivation may be considered in totality, not in piecemeal</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Uses of Motivation</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Motivation can have multiple uses. Some of them are:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">It helps you increase the quality and productivity of your work</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">It makes the person much more efficient</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">It helps the individual recognize his true self</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Helps to boost self-confidence</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Helps with hard decision making and makes people feel to have control over their life.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Helps them get promotions and other monetary benefits</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Increases the satisfaction and happiness in an individual</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Impact of Motivation</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The impact of motivation is evident. Once you get the motivation to do something, you initiate a plan. You prepare yourself mentally and make a road map on how you can get started. The second step is persistence.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Here you strive hard to achieve your goal. Persistence comes with motivation, and the last part is intensity. The intensity of your work depends totally on your level of motivation. Thus, motivation has a lot of impact on the way people perceive the task.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Tips to Get Motivation</h2><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Surround yourself with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.thehealthy.com/mental-health/happiness/be-optimistic/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">optimistic people</a>. People with a positive outlook do make a lot of difference.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Find a person who can mentor you.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Reflect upon your choices often and understand where you went wrong.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Do not go hard on yourself.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Focus on the process and outcome of the task.</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line&nbsp;</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Motivation is an important aspect that one should have to be successful. Even the smallest of the task would require your motivation. That derives from getting up and pursuing because of the outcome or the mere feeling of pleasure plays a huge role in who we are.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Motivation can affect your personal life, social life, and professional life majorly. Motivation makes you stay committed and on your toes till the task is completed and the outcome is visible. Thus, it is important to reflect upon the level of your motivation. You can always use the tips above to keep yourself motivated. Motivation does not only make you successful, but it also makes you happy and keeps you at peace.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Reference</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://www.verywellmind.com/what-is-motivation-2795378</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://managementisajourney.com/what-is-motivation/</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://www.verywellmind.com/what-is-motivation-2795378</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://positivepsychology.com/benefits-motivation/</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://www.hrzone.com/hr-glossary/what-are-motivational-theories</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">https://www.iedunote.com/motivation</li></ul>', 16, '3', '2021-11-15 07:48:43', '2021-10-26 01:36:46', '2021-11-15 01:48:43', '09/26/2021 1:36 PM', 'Kiprono Langat', 'what-is-motivation', 0, 'No'),
(62, 'Portland Travel Guide: A Potential Guide for Solo Travellers', 'portland-travel-guide-a-potential-guide-for-solo-travellers', 'Portland-Travel-Guide.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Every time someone goes on a trip, they need either someone or something guiding them. Nowadays, you can find a guide on your phone, and you might not even need to pay someone to do it. Most of the time, you can even find the guide in your native language!</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As you will learn, Portland is a city full of activities to do; while it is not a well-known city for tourists around the world, anyone making a trip to the USA should not miss it. There are great activities to do apart from the city being beautiful. You would be amazed if you happen to visit this great city.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are larger cities that happen to be more attractive for tourists, but Portland has many things those big cities don’t have. If you have the time, you should come to visit, and this Portland travel guide should help you!</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Why Everyone Should Visit Portland<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2979\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Portland-Travel.jpg\" alt=\"Portland\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Portland-Travel.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Portland-Travel-300x150.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Portland-Travel-768x384.jpg 768w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Portland-Travel-400x200.jpg 400w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Portland-Travel-600x300.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 0.8em auto;\"></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While there are other cities with many activities and places to visit, like New York or Washington DC, Portland is also a city with countless attractions. No matter your age or interests, you will always have something to do!</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If you are a wine fan, there are some great wineries; Portland is known for its parks and open spaces if you want to relax and walk around. Also, if you are a coffee fan, there are some of the most modern eco-friendly’s coffeehouses in the world. If you are a hiker, well, guess what?</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/best-places-to-travel-during-covid\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">some of the most beautiful places you could wish to go hiking</a>! That being said, everyone should have something that draws their attention to the city. Also, another point that some people consider is Portland not being a massive, big city full of people from around the world, you can be more relaxed, and you will not have hundreds of people around you taking pictures.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You will not need to be waiting in line for hours in every attraction, which many people consider tedious and time-consuming. Anyhow, there are attractions for everybody.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You will not experience a wrong time if you come to visit us! What are you waiting for? You should come to Portland and experience it yourself.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">When is The Best Time to Travel to Portland?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This is a question that does not have a definitive answer, and while the city might look better during some time of the year, some people instead go to visit the city at a different time compared to others. Why?</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Many reasons, but the weather is a big one. You might want to see the city in the snow because it looks good, but it also is freezing during the winter. There are some factors that you will have to consider to choose.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However, some recommendations might help you make up your mind about it. As a general recommendation, people say that between June and August is the best time to visit.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You get warm weather, and with that, the city’s roses are in full bloom, which is pretty impressive to see. However, this is also a tourist season, so you might want to plan in order to have the desired accommodations.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">On the other hand, you could visit Portland over the winter, there are many tourist attractions closed, but you have Mount Hood not far away, where winter sports are a considerable activity.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">So, if you are a winter sports fan, you might want to visit the city in December or January.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Where You Can Stay</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As with any other rather big city, you can stay in a wide variety of places. There are many options that vary from big hotels to small beds and breakfasts. With many options comes an extensive price range.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You can spend over $4000 in one night, but you can spend that money to be in the city for weeks. So, after you decide how much money you are using for accommodation, you will have a better idea of what you have available.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Here is a list of the best hotels in the city; however, you might find them a little expensive for a regular night:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">The Nine Suites:</span>&nbsp;The cost for this hotel is $4500 a night, but it can get up to $6500 during the summer. While this is a lot of money, you are talking about a 1768 square foot room. The location of this hotel is excellent, being in front of the Willamette River.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Hi-Lo Hotel:</span>&nbsp;Great location and modern rooms while having all of the pillows and bath amenities from local producers. A great option if you want to help local business owners!</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">AC Hotel (Owned by Marriot):</span>&nbsp;The preferred place to go by young professionals. Known for its great coffee!</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Kimpton River Place Hotel:</span>&nbsp;One of the unique places to stay in the city. Right next to the Willamette River, where you can just sit and relax and see the boats passing by.</li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Related Guide:</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/how-to-stay-safe-while-traveling\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">How to Stay Safe While Traveling</a></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What You Can Eat</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As you may already know, Portland is one of the best cities for food and drinks. So, if you are going to visit the city, come hungry! Because you will experience what quality restaurants are like. Here is a list of the restaurant that is a must-go when you go to Portland. You need to try these places!</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">The Shop:</span>&nbsp;A handpicked selection of oysters combined with a cold glass of wine or local beer in an airy space. The price is $1,50 for each oyster; fish ranges from $9-44 and caviar $70. The wine and beer go from $7-12.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Cooperativa:</span>&nbsp;Italian food and also some pantry items and a cocktail bar. They also offer some homemade pizza and a gelato shop. The prices range from $1 pastry to $5,50 for a slice of pizza and $50 for a family meal.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Republica:</span>&nbsp;Is a Mexican restaurant, maybe not too typical for Portland, but worth trying. All Mexican food, from tacos to cakes, soups, and guisados (stewed meats). The price ranges from $6 sweet treats up to $70 for a family dinner.</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How to Get Portland Around</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Like any major city,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.travelportland.com/plan/transportation/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">public transportation</a>&nbsp;is not only great but also cheap. There are many options for you to use. However, many people would argue that walking is the best choice. You will be able to experience and explore the city in a healthy and fun way.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The subway and trains are excellent and cheap. You can get anywhere in the city for a little bit over $2. Also, if you plan to go out of town to Willamette Valley or Mount Hood, renting a car is an option. However, you must know that walking might get tricky during winter because walking in the snow might not be the brightest idea.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Related Guide:</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/protect-yourself-from-the-coronavirus-while-traveling\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">How to Protect Yourself from the Covid-19 While Traveling</a></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How to Own the Portland LBGTQ Night Life</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In Portland, there are many LBGTQ places you could go and enjoy, from quiet and relaxed bars to loud parties. Portland has a very active nightlife compared to other cities, but it is not like New York, where the city never sleeps. The city offers a wide variety of options all around the map. The city is also known for its&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.hasson.com/blog/2019/02/ultimate-music-lovers-guide-portland-oregon/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">indie music scene</a>.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Where to Get Winery</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Portland offers dozens of wineries in the urban setting. So, you do not have to work hard to find one of them. Here is a list of wineries around town which you would like to visit:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Teutonic Wine Company:</span>&nbsp;created in 2002, its wines are German styled. They offer Pinot Noir, Pinot Blanc, and Pinot Gris. It is located in Southeast Portland.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Division Winemaking Company:</span>&nbsp;focused on making nuanced wines.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Coopers Hall:</span>&nbsp;they offer wine, beer, and cider. Also, they offer excellent kitchen service.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Enso Winery:</span>&nbsp;they go for a more exclusive feeling; they produce small batches of their wines, never more than 100 bottles. They offer a tasting room, this a top choice but more expensive than average.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Fullerton Wines:</span>&nbsp;is a family company, and they have been in business since 2011. They produce Pinot Noir and Rose made from Pinot Noir.</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are many attractions in Portland; you can do everything. If you have the chance, do not hesitate to visit. The information handed out here will help you make the most out of this trip.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You will get to know this fantastic city and everything that comes with it. Remember that if you go during winter, you’d better bring your coat and beanie, it is going to get cold.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Portland has everything, and it is a city hard not to like and even love. The city is one of the most exciting cities in the United States. You have countless attractions and places to visit.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Take your time and get to know all of the city, do not miss anything! Portland is a great city! Let this Portland Travel guide be the first step towards a great vacation.</p>', 16, '3', '2021-11-15 07:48:57', '2021-10-26 01:39:02', '2021-11-15 01:48:57', '11/03/2021 1:38 PM', 'Kiprono Langat', 'portland-travel-guide', 0, 'Yes');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(63, 'The Best Ways to Modify Your Car: Step By Step Guide', 'the-best-ways-to-modify-your-car-step-by-step-guide', 'Best-Ways-to-Modify-Your-Car.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are many changes you can make when it comes to your car. Some people might change the color; others will change the engine, and much more! Nowadays, people have found about the wonderful world of car modifications!</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Retail cars might not have the best components or parts in the market. You might want to have a better audio system or better seats. That is why people modify their cars. Here, you will learn about the best ways to modify your car, including which parts and how much it will cost you to do it.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Why It’s Important to Know About Car Modifying</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Many people wonder why modifying a car might be helpful and get negative answers, so they ignore modifying it. Once you take your car out of the dealerships, its value immediately decreases.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If you modify your car, though, you could be increasing its value in the market. So, if you talk with a person that says modifying a car is useless, they are wrong. People won’t just make car modifications to make their car look like a car from the movie fast and furious.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You might want to modify a car to have more space in the back or be safer for kids. Anyways, take a look at all the aspects of your car that you could modify and improve your car.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Also, parts of a car are always worth modifying, and you can do that without even the need of a mechanic or garage store. You could do it in your garage with your tools, and you will be improving the performance of your car significantly.<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2962\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Modify-Your-Car.jpg\" alt=\"car modification \" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Modify-Your-Car.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Modify-Your-Car-300x200.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Modify-Your-Car-768x513.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Best Ways to Modify Your Car</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Here are some of the parts of your car you can modify. In this list, you will see some pretty obvious things, but other ones that you might never have thought could be modified or changed.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The imagination could bring some significant updates to a car. You do not have to stick to what you read, be creative and try new things; you can transform your car into your dream car.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Wheels and Tires</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As you might have initially thought, the wheels and the tires might be one of the most common modifications for a car. There are many aspects of the tires or wheels you can change, and there are so many options.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">For example, you can change the color of the wheel or change the tire’s size. Have you ever seen one of those wheels that keep spinning even after the car stopped?</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">That is a modification just for the car to look “cooler.” However, you can make some modifications that are made for safety. For example, some tires are made bulletproof.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Suspension Upgrades</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The suspension of the car is a pretty big deal. There are cars that, because the suspension system was flawed, had some terrible accidents. So, modifying this part should be made by someone who knows what he is dealing with.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Some rather have a sport suspension, and some may want a rally suspension. There are many options, which means that the price range is pretty wide for this upgrade.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Some suspensions are better than the standard ones, but they are cheaper compared to a sport suspension. Also, some suspensions are sold as upgrades, but they might be worse than your car’s stock system.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Brakes</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As you might know, the brakes get old. If your brakes are old, you should get rid of them and get new ones if you want to avoid an accident. Also, there are some modifications you might want to try that will make your car stop harder. Some competitive brakes will stop the car faster than you can imagine.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Also, there are different types of brakes, so you might want to take a look at what you have. Have you ever seen the brakes on a Formula 1 car?</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">They are amazing, they get up to 1000 degrees, and they cool down so fast! I doubt you can find a brake like those, but a competition one will give you more reaction time.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Exhaust</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are many reasons why you might want to change your vehicle’s exhaust. Nowadays, people are trying to take care of the environment, and car exhausts are not helping.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">That is why there are new ones which help reduce the pollution of the car. Also, the looks; some exhausts look better than others, and people usually modify them for that reason.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The car’s performance can be improved by this change but not as much as you might think. Moreover, you can change only the last part of it or the entire system. The price is way different depending on that. You could spend around $1000 for the change of the entire system or $90 for the last part only.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Stance</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This is a widespread modification for street racing cars. By modifying the car’s stance, you are lowering the car’s entire body and making it much closer to the floor. Also, many people would modify the wheels by adding negative camber for the car to look “stance.”</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However, some stance modifications might be illegal. You should make sure you can make modifications such as these. Some cities have banned modifications of the exhaust because they tend to pollute the air more.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In some places, these cars are banned due to air pollution because they violate the smog standards or the clean air standards, so be sure you can make the modifications before actually doing them.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Seats</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are many options when it comes to seats. You can modify the color, the material, the shape, and even the smell. Some people have seats with a sportier style, the seats might be less comfortable, but they are great to keep the posture right.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Also, you can change the material. Many people do not like the standard seats; they instead have leather. If your car did not come with leather seats, you could also change them.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Also, you can have a more cushioned seat. Some people would change the seat to have a more comfortable one. If you are a person who drives long distances, a well-cushioned seat might be beneficial.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Driver Update</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Every person likes to be comfortable and having the driver side of the car modified to make that happen sounds like a good idea. A variety of parts within the driver’s side can be modified to make you more comfortable.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You can start with the wheel, the pedals, and the seat. Many things make a car comfortable and pleasant to drive, and the position is crucial. Also, the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.yourmechanic.com/article/3-essential-things-to-know-about-your-car-s-gear-shifter\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">gear shift is fundamental</a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Some may prefer a longer one while others a shorter one. Some may like having the inside of the car with many lights, and some would find that distractive.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Window Tint</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Many cars have their windows tinted, and while that is great for many people, some struggle to see outside. That is why a modification might be less tinted or more, depending on the person.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is widespread to add darker window tint, but you need to be sure about the regulations. Some places have limitations, and they won’t let you do more than a particular value.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Having the windows as dark as a limousine might be a risk too, but they also give the passenger more privacy in the car.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Underbody Neon Lights</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">“Stanced” cars and vehicles are commonly found with modifications like these. This is one modification that someone can do at your garage. An expert will do a better job, but the car owner can do it himself if budget is an issue.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Carbon Upgrades</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This material will protect the car at the same time it can make it lighter. It is weird to think that carbon is one of the most complex materials and one of the lightest ones.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Upgrading some parts with this material could make the car lighter and harder to break in the case of an accident. For example, F1 race cars have their cockpits made out of carbon.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Additional More Notes for Car Modify</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">When modifying a car, being sure that all the parts you are modifying are legal should be a concern. Also, doing the job and leaving it halfway could be dangerous, so be sure to complete the modifications when starting.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Every change should be studied first; learn about the process and what the changes will do to your car. Usually, mechanics know what it is all about, but do not hesitate to ask everything to be sure.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Related Topic</span>:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/how-a-car-works\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">How A Car Works: Unveiling Its Mysteries</a></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Advantage and Disadvantage of Car Modifying</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">For more than one reason, having all of the original parts of the car is better, maybe even safer; The company that sells and makes the car tests it to assure a safety standard. So, there are both advantages and disadvantages when modifying your car. The advantages are the following ones:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You control the modifications; you choose how your car will look</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">You can modify the security measures in your vehicle</li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">The disadvantages of modifying your car, on the other hand, are:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Modifications can be expensive</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Some modifications could bring the car’s value down (others might bring it up)</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">If you or the mechanic does the modifications incorrectly, the car par being modified could get ruined</li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">So, be smart and do not ruin your car. Try to bring your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.nhcc.edu/student-resources/library/doinglibraryresearch/cars-checklist\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">vehicle’s value up</a>&nbsp;with your modifications, not bring it down.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Modifications on cars are pretty standard, and they might help you build the car of your dreams. There are many parts you can change in a car, making it look cooler, but it can also be ruined.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Please make sure the person who is working on the car knows what he is doing. Also, it would be best if you double-checked that the modifications you are doing are within legal regulations.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Imagine if, after modifying your car, you find out that all the modifications are illegal? Be sure to make an informed decision and start working on your dream car!</p><div class=\"atbs-article-reactions  js-atbs-reaction\" data-article-id=\"2960\" style=\"margin-top: 45px; clear: both; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><h3 class=\"atbs-reactions-title\" style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px; font-size: 18px;\">What is your reaction?</h3></div>', 16, '3', '2021-11-15 07:49:41', '2021-10-26 01:40:53', '2021-11-15 01:49:41', '10/07/2021 3:30 PM', 'Kiprono Langat', 'best-ways-to-modify-your-car', 0, 'No');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(69, 'Best Laptops in 2021: For Enthusiastic Professionals and Gamers', 'best-laptops-in-2021-for-enthusiastic-professionals-and-gamers', 'Best-Laptops-2021.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">We all know about laptops. As an alternative to PCs, its demand has always been pretty high. That makes it one of the most popular electronics for our daily needs. Every day, we are relying more and more on virtual systems. From educational to business, everything is going through online platforms. Different types of digital machines like pc, laptops, mobile, allow us to access the online world. As we mentioned, the laptop is one of them. We can read, write, watch, transfer and store different types of files or documents. Communication, entertainment, transaction, and all the other necessary needs are possible through a laptop. As a pc alternative, people also use it as a portable gaming platform. So, whether it is professional work or gaming, the laptop is one of the best choices out there.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Here, we have collected a large number of excellent laptops. These are among the best laptops in 2021. We will describe them as efficiently as possible. If you are planning to get a laptop, then this is the right place. Look at each of their specifications and exclusive features.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What are the Best Laptops?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Mentioning a single laptop as the best is not possible. There are so many variants and too many conditions to compare. A laptop may be pretty well-featured, but it will not be suitable for regular usage. Professional business laptops are different from gaming laptops. They carry more stability than exclusive performance. Considerably, business laptops focus only on battery life, stability, full keyboard, and quality metal design.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">On the other hand, a gaming laptop focuses on more powerful features to handle any game. Not only the heavy load but also the heavy graphics and overall power requirement. As we mentioned, all comparison starts with the essential processor clock speed, core count, and generation. The latest generation always provides better compatibility and overall efficiency.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">On the other hand, a professional laptop should have at least 4GB ram. 8GB will provide rather satisfactory performance. A laptop can be considered as best if it combines all the overall features. We are recommending some of the best laptops to help you with the selection. Below, let’s check out our selected best laptops 2021.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Best Performance</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Razor Blade 15 is definitely our best choice, even though it is the most expensive one. However, it is too much for professional business or regular work. Not to mention, its battery backup is only 6 hours.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Indeed, it has powerful graphics that can handle any AAA game. So, if you are looking for the highest performance, then it will be a great deal. Besides, Razer is a famous and reputed brand, so the product quality is fantastic.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Best Professional Choice</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Acer Swift 3 (AMD) is one of the best laptops 2021 for professionals. It does not come with exotic graphics but features many upgraded components. Aside from that, it offers everything a professional would need. Solid and stable performance, high ram capacity, and also a powerful processor. Someone with a heavy workload would love to grab such a great laptop. Even though it is costly, the overall features prove to be an excellent choice for anyone.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Overall Standard</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Our next pick is Lenovo IdeaPad Flex 5. It is a perfectly balanced professional laptop. Not to mention, its comfortable design also comes with the latest Processor. Besides, it comes with a 16GB ram. It ensures smooth data transactions for the most comfortable usage. The soft keyboard and all the top-grade components are excellent for everyday usages.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">How Can You Choose the Perfect Laptops for Your Own?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Considering your demand, choosing a perfect laptop needs some experience. You need to know what features are essential. Although, we are here to make it easier for you. To identify a laptop’s quality, you have to measure different features.</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Processor</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Ram</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Graphics</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Storage device</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Battery Backup</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Screen Resolution and Quality</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Screen size</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Additional features</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Warranty</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Brand Value</li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In our recommended list, Processor is the first thing to look for. There are two popular brands like Intel and AMD. A processor’s clock speed defines the basic power along with its core count. 2, 4,6,8, and more cores are available in the market. Even though different brands have different power and efficiency, you can get their performance chart online.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Ram is the next factor. It starts from 1GB, but recent technologies have updated so much. Usually, even an entry-level laptop has at least 4GB ram. Different brands may offer different rams, but their performance is quite similar.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Graphics is a simple term but a little bit complicated to understand. Any types of video quality like entertainment or gaming depend on the graphics capability. It can be built-in graphics from the brand or even powerful graphics from a reputed brand like Nvidia or AMD.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Storage capability means how much space you have. There are two types like internal and external. Internals are built-in, and you can buy external to add more space. There are also two types of internal space like HDD and SSD. Spaces are like 256GB, 500GB, 1TB, 2TB and more.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Battery backup defines how long a laptop may work from each charge. As for screen resolution, it means the quality of your screen, like how the pixel density it has. The numbers are 1366×768, 1920×1080, 2k, 4k, and more. Considering that, there are many screen sizes as well. Usually, the size starts from 14″ and gets even bigger. However, some mini laptops may have even smaller sizes.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">These are the basic features, but there are more. Wi-Fi, Webcam, Bluetooth, Card reader, Multimedia keys are among the additional standard features. Besides, you should always look for the warranty period. Most laptops come with at least 2-3 years of warranty. In the end, you can ask for brand value. It is not a major factor but reputed brands constantly provide great products to maintain their reputation.</p><table class=\"brand-list\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.6em; width: 710px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><thead><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><th style=\"padding: 0.8em 0.8em 0.8em 0px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid lightgray; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\">Brand Name</th><th style=\"padding-top: 0.8em; padding-right: 0.8em; padding-bottom: 0.8em; text-align: left; border: 1px solid lightgray; background: rgb(242, 242, 242); padding-left: 10px !important;\">Brand Image</th><th style=\"padding-top: 0.8em; padding-right: 0.8em; padding-bottom: 0.8em; text-align: left; border: 1px solid lightgray; background: rgb(242, 242, 242); padding-left: 10px !important;\"></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><td style=\"padding-top: 0.8em; padding-right: 0.8em; padding-bottom: 0.8em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid lightgray; padding-left: 10px !important;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Acer Swift 3 (AMD)</p></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid lightgray; text-align: center; padding: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Acer-Swift-3-AMD.jpg\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 50px; height: auto;\"></td><td style=\"padding-top: 0.8em; padding-right: 0.8em; padding-bottom: 0.8em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid lightgray; text-align: right; padding-left: 10px !important;\"><a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/best-laptops/#brand-box-1\" class=\"read-more\" style=\"background: rgb(34, 34, 34); color: white; position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; padding: 5px 15px; outline: 0px !important;\">Read More</a></td></tr><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><td style=\"padding-top: 0.8em; padding-right: 0.8em; padding-bottom: 0.8em; vertical-align: top; 