and balanced laptop for any professional. The 512GB SSD addition fuels the power even more. The only downside is probably the graphics.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It has built-in graphics. Although, it is pretty good enough to handle regular work. Such a great combination should catch anyone’s interest. Remember, it is rather quite expensive. But the performance makes it one of the best laptops in 2021.</p><div class=\"brand-box brand-box-1\" id=\"brand-box-1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; margin-bottom: 25px; border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); position: relative; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"brand-box-left\" style=\"width: 424.797px; padding: 10px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Configuration or Specification</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">processor: AMD Ryzen 7 4700U</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Graphics: AMD Radeon Graphics</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Ram: 8GB</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Storage: 512GB SSD</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Display Size: 14″</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Resolution: 1920×1080</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Weight: 2.7 pounds</li></ul></div><div class=\"brand-box-right\" style=\"width: 283.188px; overflow: hidden;\"><img src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Acer-Swift-3-AMD.jpg\" class=\"brand-image\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; animation-name: 