ces</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">SSD storage for fast data transfer</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">HD screen resolution</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Smooth clicking keyboard</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Smaller size for easy portability</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">High performing ram capacity</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Affordable to high-end price range</li></ul></div><div class=\"box-cons\" style=\"width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Reason to Avoid</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Only built-in graphics</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Quite expensive for the brand value</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">New generation processors are available</li></ul></div><div class=\"overlay\" style=\"height: 486px; width: 708px; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; z-index: 1; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"></div></div><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Google Pixelbook Go</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Google Pixelbook is getting popular day by day. They are a bit pricey but come with tons of features. Not to mention, it is always up to date with the latest components. As for this one, it has balanced and flexible variants. You can select an entry-level or high-performer.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">A great feature is its screen resolution that comes with HD and 4K quality. The slim and eye-catching design is more than enough to satisfy any professional and business user. It is considered one of the best laptops for students as well.</p><div class=\"brand-box brand-box-3\" id=\"brand-box-3\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; margin-bottom: 25px; border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); position: relative; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"brand-box-left\" style=\"width: 424.797px; padding: 10px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Configuration or Specification</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">processor: 7th Gen Intel Core i3, i5, i7</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Graphics: Intel UHD 615</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Ram: 8GB, 16GB</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Storage: 64,128,256GB</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Display Size: 13.3″</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Resolution: 1080p or 4K</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Weight: 2.3 pounds</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"></h3></div><div class=\"brand-box-right\" style=\"width: 283.188px; overflow: hidden;\"><img src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Google-Pixelbook-Go-1.jpg\" class=\"brand-image\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; animation-name: scale; animation-duration: 3s; animation-iteration-count: infinite; animation-direction: alternate; animation-timing-function: linear;\"></div></div><div class=\"pros-cons-box\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); margin-bottom: 30px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; position: relative; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"box-pros\" style=\"border-right: 3px solid white; width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Reason to Buy</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Multiple processor variants</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Smaller size for easy portability</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Amazing screen quality with slim design</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">HD and 4k resolutions are available</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Suitable for professional usage</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Stable and excellent battery life</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Includes additional features</li></ul></div><div class=\"box-cons\" style=\"width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Reason to Avoid</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Storage could be higher</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Updated processor versions are available</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The sound quality needs improvement</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"></h3></div><div class=\"overlay\" style=\"height: 429px; width: 708px; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; z-index: 1; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"></div></div><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Lenovo IdeaPad Flex 5</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Lenovo is providing many efficient and high-performing laptops over the year. They have a large number of excellent collections, and Idea pad is one of the most popular series. Idea pad Flex 5 is one of the most favorable ones. It is also one of our top recommendations.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The laptop contains excellent HD resolution with a professional design. Its Processor, SSD, and ram support are all up to the mark for the best performance. Not to mention, its battery backup is made for handling heavy workloads. It is also an excellent value for the price.</p><div class=\"brand-box brand-box-4\" id=\"brand-box-4\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; margin-bottom: 25px; border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); position: relative; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"brand-box-left\" style=\"width: 424.797px; padding: 10px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Configuration or Specification</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">processor: AMD Ryzen 5 4500U</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Graphics: Integrated AMD Radeon Graphics</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Ram: 16GB</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Storage: 256 GB SSD</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Display Size: 14″</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Resolution: 1920 x 1080</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Weight: 3.63 pounds</li></ul></div><div class=\"brand-box-right\" style=\"width: 283.188px; overflow: hidden;\"><img src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Lenovo-IdeaPad-Flex-5-1.jpg\" class=\"brand-image\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; animation-name: scale; animation-duration: 3s; animation-iteration-count: infinite; animation-direction: alternate; animation-timing-function: linear;\"></div></div><div class=\"pros-cons-box\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); margin-bottom: 30px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; position: relative; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"box-pros\" style=\"border-right: 3px solid white; width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Reason to Buy</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Great value for the price</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">HD quality</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">SSD storage</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Great ram capacity</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Latest processor variant</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Amazing performance</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">2-in1 touch design</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Up to 10-hours of battery backup</li></ul></div><div class=\"box-cons\" style=\"width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Reason to Avoid</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Storage needs to be a bit more</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Graphics can be improved with an external one</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The brand support is not great</li></ul></div><div class=\"overlay\" style=\"height: 443px; width: 708px; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; z-index: 1; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"></div></div><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Razor Blade 15</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Razor Blade 15 is a dedicated gaming laptop. Unlike our previous picks, it comes with exotic features and an extreme graphics card like RTX 2060. It also offers a higher and latest Processor and all the necessary components for the best gaming experience, although there are few drawbacks.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Even though they are qualified, Razer products cost more than other brands like ASUS, MSI, HP, etc. Moreover, the performance difference is not entirely different. So, if you want to avoid an expensive deal, then look at other brands. Besides, the laptop is quite heavy, so you need to be careful to carry it from place to place. But, if you can go for it, then the performance is worth the price. Thus, it is our top choice as one of the best laptops in 2021.</p><div class=\"brand-box brand-box-5\" id=\"brand-box-5\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; margin-bottom: 25px; border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); position: relative; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"brand-box-left\" style=\"width: 424.797px; padding: 10px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Configuration or Specification</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">processor: Intel Core i7-10750H</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Graphics: RTX 2060</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Ram: 16GB</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Storage: 512GB SSD</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Display Size: 15.6″</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Resolution: 1080p</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Weight: 5 pounds</li></ul></div><div class=\"brand-box-right\" style=\"width: 283.188px; overflow: hidden;\"><img src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Razer-Blade-15-300x300-1.jpg\" class=\"brand-image\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; animation-name: scale; animation-duration: 3s; animation-iteration-count: infinite; animation-direction: alternate; animation-timing-function: linear;\"></div></div><div class=\"pros-cons-box\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); margin-bottom: 30px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; position: relative; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"box-pros\" style=\"border-right: 3px solid white; width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Reason to Buy</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Exotic gaming laptop</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Perfectly balanced to handle any AAA game</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">High-end graphics</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Powerful Processor and 16GB ram capacity</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Great design and stability</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">HD resolution and unique light effect</li></ul></div><div class=\"box-cons\" style=\"width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Reason to Avoid</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Pretty expensive</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Battery backup is pretty low</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Not suitable for professional usage</li></ul></div><div class=\"overlay\" style=\"height: 415px; width: 708px; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; z-index: 1; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"></div></div><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Which Types of Laptops Will be Best for You?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The best choice depends on your preference and usages. Suppose you are a casual user who does only regular work. In that case, the Choice needs to be minimal with more stability. Regular works are like watching videos, exploring the internet, transferring files, video chat, and more. In that case, you better look for a business laptop that comes with a stable processor and at least 4GB ram. Although, 8GB would be better. These types of laptops come with built-in graphics, so they don’t require a lot of energy. Thus, they also provide excellent battery backup for more extended usage.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">On the other hand, if you are a gamer, then a professional one would not be enough. We all know that a game requires high graphics to handle the requirement. External and higher graphics from the Nvidia series, MX series are necessary. Besides, higher core speed for processors and ram count is also essential. For smooth casual usage and gaming, you need better and higher video resolution. At least an HD resolution is necessary. A laptop that contains these features is perfect for the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://geekvibesnation.com/6-items-to-create-the-perfect-gaming-experience/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">best gaming experience</a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Summarizing the ideas, if you have to explore and business works requiring only commercial app usages, we suggest having laptops like Lenovo Idea pad or Acer Swift. As for gaming, we are recommending going for an expensive one like Razor Blade. Check out the recommendation and review the best laptops in 2021.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While selecting your preference, there are more works than just business or gaming. Many people have higher demands with production works like video, audio, animation, rendering, and more. In that case, you need more than just gaming laptops. There are many laptops with specialized processors and graphics for workstation usages.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Another important feature would be the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://engr.ku.edu/cherry-picked-researcher-sees-laptop-cooling-technology-way-less-thirsty-power-plants\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">cooling system</a>. Laptops do not have a dedicated cooling system to manage an external cooler to do so. The higher the working demand, the better the cooling system is necessary. Not only will it prevent component damage but also make the system work for a more extended period.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As expected, they have a much higher price. Sometimes, it is even hard to get all the features together. In that case, try to grab the best possible deal. So, if you demand workstation works, then neither a professional nor gaming laptop would be enough. Make sure to go for a distinct choice with a workstation title.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">The Bottom Line</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As we have described many things about laptops, it is time to review all the things together. We have discussed all the features a laptop can offer, from the Processor to any additional accessories like charger, adapter, cooler and more. Let’s have a quick look again.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Usually, we can categorize a laptop into 3 different types. Professional or casual, gaming and workstation. Although, a workstation laptop is way too expensive, and very few users go for it. So, professional and gaming laptops have the highest demand in the market.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Their difference is stated with the component choice, like the Processor, ram, graphics, storage, screen resolution, and more. While buying a laptop, you have to consider these things. To make it easier, we have recommended some of the best laptops in 2021. The best laptop will focus on the overall balance rather than just putting a single higher component. So, you have to compare their features and also benchmark review. Benchmark is available online, and you can search for it with the laptop model. Make sure to check it before buying any laptop.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">So, what do you think about our review? Check them out and also learn more about the selection from our researched buying guide. It will help you to grab the best laptop deals.</p>', 17, '3', '2021-11-15 07:49:51', '2021-10-26 03:05:26', '2021-11-27 22:17:06', '09/26/2021 3:04 PM', 'Phyllis Olson', 'best-laptops', 1, 'No');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(70, 'Best Waterproof Smartwatches You Can Choose in 2021', 'best-waterproof-smartwatches-you-can-choose-in-2021', 'How-Much-CBD-Oil-to-Take-for-Pain-Relief.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Time maintenance is key to getting things done. We all lead a pretty busy life. A watch helps us to track those schedules. But, a smartwatch comes with way more features. Our daily schedule comes with the morning workout, official work, household work, cooking, playing, sleeping, entertainment, and more.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Besides, there are so many occasional events as well. Maintaining all these is not easy. A smartwatch has not only custom notification but also different measurement options. Thus, we are going to talk about the best waterproof smartwatch to get and its comparison.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">A user can measure the heart rate, traveled distance, and more. Surprisingly, you can even enjoy multiple entertainment features as well. Audio, video, browsing, messaging, calling, and so much more. You will not get such features in a regular watch. But, a smartwatch certainly has them all.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Although, not every smartwatch comes with all-in-one offerings. There are a lot of varieties to go for. Brands, customization, design, build material, and few other factors are there to consider. We are going to talk about them, indicating the pros and cons of every feature.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Besides, we will recommend some of the best smartwatches you should look for.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">An Overview Of Smartwatch</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Before getting a smartwatch, you have to learn about them. Usually, a smartwatch is what the name says. Unlike regular watches, they do much more than showing time.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Usually, smartwatches have a touch screen display. You can get easy access to it through the touch feature. There is no manual control like in the old days. If you are thinking, why is a touchscreen and just a fancy feature or not. The touchscreen is specially made for app access.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Many smartwatches allow different types of app. Among them, social media apps, medical assistance apps, and so on. Manual access to these apps is not just possible. So, you need a touchscreen for the most comfortable experience.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The latest smartwatches are even more impressive. You can insert a sim card to use as a smartphone. There, all types of messaging and calling features are available.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Moreover, you can even use Bluetooth to support wireless devices. Besides, you can use wifi and other web surfing services as well. With all these features coming into one place, a smartwatch is all you need. The best waterproof smartwatch should perform these essential needs with efficiency.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">What Smartwatches Do For Us?</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">We have discussed a lot of things about smartwatches in the overview. All we have mentioned are the features a smartwatch may offer.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Now, we will describe their distinct offerings. A top-quality smartwatch should offer most of these features. You will get a fair idea about their usages. Let’s get into the discussion.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Multimedia For Entertainment</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">A smartwatch offers multimedia services where you can enjoy both audio and video. Any type of popular formats like mp3 and mp4 are all acceptable. You can enjoy them anywhere at any time. Your best smartwatch should have all-rounder multimedia support.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Besides, there are both wired and wireless communication features. You can use cord earphones or wireless ones through it. While traveling or transporting, you can always enjoy your favorite song, music, or movie at any moment.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Sim Support</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Indeed, most smartwatches support micro sim. Thus, you can use the watch just as a smartphone. With sim communication, you can manage calls, send and receive messages, and more.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Thus, it is also one of the most convenient features. You don’t have to go through carrying a long phone.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">App Support</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As there are both android and IOS supported smartwatches, you can enjoy full app support. No matter what type of app it is, you can have it as long as it supports the platform.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Having such a versatile feature in a smartwatch is undoubtedly an advantage in daily life.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Health Support</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">One of the primary reasons for having a smartwatch is to get digital health support. There are built-in features where you can measure different physical conditions. Heart rate, sugar level, idle and active period, diabetes, sleeping period, and a few more.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Usually, we have to go to a clinic to check them. You can easily keep tracking your fitness at every moment. If there is a sudden change, then ask for medical support as fast as you can.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Internet Surfing</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As we said, you can use sim and wifi services in a smartwatch. Thus, you can also explore the internet. Surfing the internet through a smartwatch is probably the last thing you ever expect.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">But, it is available, though. You don’t have to worry about carrying an external internet service system.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Location Tracking</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Usually, a smartwatch comes with GPS tracking along with other features. You can track your location as well as any other device. Devices that enable tracking, like a smartwatch or smartphone, can be pointed out if they are missing.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Customization</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While regular watches have no built-in customizing option, smartwatches are different. They have a lot of customization options. In the apps, you can customize it as much as a smartphone. Besides, you can even change the belt as per choice.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\">Features That You Should Look For In a Smartwatch</h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">We have discussed smartwatches and their usual usages. However, while buying one, you have to know their offerings. Every smartwatch does not come with all the features.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Although, most of them do offer basic features. The ones with all the features are pretty expensive as well.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Let’s grab every feature and compare it with each other.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Build Material</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Surprisingly, you should consider the material quality as much as the supportive apps. Overall build material and top finishing are both necessary to durable usages.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Besides, the belt can also have a leather build, which is even more expensive and classic.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Platform Compatibility</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is the very first feature you have to consider. Depending on this, you may get other compatibility features.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Usually, it is either android or IOS. For android, you can use all sorts of android apps and other features. On the other hand, IOS allows you to get different feature packages.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Among all the smartwatches, Apple watches are the most popular ones. As for android, there are top watches from Samsung and others.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Besides, some variants like Fitbit Versa 2 work with both platforms at the same time.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Display Type</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Usually, smartwatches come with a touch display. So, the touchscreen type matters the most. There is an LCD and LED display. Even though there is no major difference in performance, some useful features depend on it.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are some improved screen variants like OLED and AMOLED displays. They provide a better photo and video resolution. Although, they consume more charges in the process.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Custom Design</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">One of the best reasons for having a smartwatch is its design. It is much different than regular watches. They are way more trendy and professional. If you want to enhance your everyday fashion and style, then the smartwatch is a perfect choice.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You can even get a personalized design from the brand. Moreover, some parts of them are also replaceable. It allows you to get different styles.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">App Support</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Even though smartwatches support different platforms, you can’t just use any app. Due to the smaller screen size and structure, the supported apps are limited. As we mentioned, you can do several physical and other trackings through app support.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Along with them, you can even get ESPN, Uber, and other apps. So, make sure to check the list of supported apps before buying one.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">GPS Tracking</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">GPS Tracking is one of the features that are a must. Not only it helps to track your smartwatch but also other trackable devices as well. It can be a smartphone, smartwatch, or any smart device.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You can also track your location from Google Maps. This feature is beneficial for any traveling. Moreover, it ensures your safety more than anything.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Health Tracking</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Health tracking is the reason behind the growing popularity of smartwatches. We need to spend a lot of time on different fitness improvements. Not only do they take time, but you also need to track the procedure not to overdo it.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Sugar level, heartbeat count, workout period, resting period, and more. There are also different calorie counting features. Using them, you can track fitness with instant efficiency.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Related Topic:&nbsp;</span>Health Tech A New Guide:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/health-tech-a-new-guide\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">How Tech Informs Your Health Better</a></p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Communication Support</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As you are getting a smartphone that features a smartwatch, you can use it for communication like calling, texting, video calling, and more. So, you should check their supportive features for communication.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Payment</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Indeed, most smartphones support the internet and other utility apps. So, you can even pay different bills for utility, shopping, and more through a smartphone. Look for the supportive apps if your selected smartwatch model accepts them.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Bluetooth &amp; WiFi</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Bluetooth and wifi are both available on many smartwatches. It is one of those valuable features that allow you to do a lot of things. Browsing, online communication, app access, completing payment or bill, and other online services.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Moreover, Bluetooth allows us to share data and use wireless devices like an earphone.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Waterproof</h3>