ongest in the market. From design to performance, it stands out more than any other choice. The IOS compatibility unlocks all the unique apple features to enjoy.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The multimedia features are also top-notch, where you get i-tune and other apps to play all the time. Until the next version, this is the best IOS smartwatch in the market.</p><div class=\"brand-box brand-box-1\" id=\"brand-box-1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; margin-bottom: 25px; border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); position: relative; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"brand-box-left\" style=\"width: 424.797px; padding: 10px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Product Specification</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Brand: Apple</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Platform: IOS</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Model: Series 6</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Connectivity: Bluetooth, Cellular, Wifi, NFC, GPS</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Wireless Connectivity: 5GHz</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Color Count: 5</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Color Option: Red, Blue, Gold/Pink, Silver/White, Grey/Black</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Battery Life: 4-years</li></ul></div><div class=\"brand-box-right\" style=\"width: 283.188px; overflow: hidden;\"><img src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/1-Apple-Watch-Series-6.jpg\" class