rgin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Supports ECG app for better health tracking</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Comes with an EDA sensor and stress management</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Specialized temperature tracker</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Free premium Fitbit service for 6-months</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Slim and smooth design</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Supports Alexa for quick access</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Fast charging</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Corning Gorilla Glass 3</li></ul></div><div class=\"box-cons\" style=\"width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Cons:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Age restriction: people under 22-years shouldn’t use it</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Limited country availability for the ECG app</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The premium offering is not that great for the price</li></ul></div><div class=\"overlay\" style=\"height: 573px; width: 708px; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; z-index: 1; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"></div></div><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Huawei Watch GT2</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While picking waterproof smartwatches, Huawei has a pretty good collection. Here, we have the GT2, which comes with some great tracking features. It is a cheaper option than our previous picks.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">With a durable build quality, its AMOLED glass also has a 3D feature. Besides having those standard features, it also has precise GPS tracking.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Another great advantage of it is the double platform acceptance. It supports both Android and IOS. The price tag provides way more value than you would ask for.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Considerably, it is the most valued and best waterproof smartwatch on our list. For the price, it is the best waterproof smartwatch worth consideration.</p><div class=\"brand-box brand-box-4\" id=\"brand-box-4\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; margin-bottom: 25px; border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); position: relative; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"brand-box-left\" style=\"width: 424.797px; padding: 10px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Product Specification:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Brand: Huawei</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Model: GT2</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Supported Platform: Android, IOS</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Connectivity: Bluetooth, wifi</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Color Option: Black, Silver, Coffee</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Battery Life: 2-weeks</li></ul></div><div class=\"brand-box-right\" style=\"width: 283.188px; overflow: hidden;\"><img src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/4.-Huawei-Watch-GT2.jpg\" class=\"brand-image\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; animation-name: scale; animation-duration: 3s; animation-iteration-count: infinite; animation-direction: alternate; animation-timing-function: linear;\"></div></div><div class=\"pros-cons-box\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); margin-bottom: 30px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; position: relative; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"box-pros\" style=\"border-right: 3px solid white; width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Pros:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Both Andoird and IOS support</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Waterproof and durable</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">AMOLED display</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Precise tracking</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">15 different indoor and outdoor modes</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Durable and beautiful design</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Affordable and value for money</li></ul></div><div class=\"box-cons\" style=\"width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Cons:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The sensor does not work precisely over tattoos</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">App support needs improvement</li></ul></div><div class=\"overlay\" style=\"height: 429px; width: 708px; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; z-index: 1; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"></div></div><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\">Amazfit GTS 2/GTR 2</h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Amazfit offers some incredible smartwatches for everyday use. Their GTS and GTR series are the most popular ones. It has the most color variants on our list. There are 12 different colors to go for.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Besides, it has Amazfit OS support. Moreover, the curved screen has both 3d and AMOLED features. A decent choice as a waterproof smartwatch.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Surprisingly, it has way more options than you can expect. There are more than 90 different sports modes. The count is higher than any other option on our list.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It not only helps with health tracking but also additional 3-GB music storage. With all these features, the battery consumption is pretty high. To support that, it has a durable battery life that stays for 7-days.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Although, heavy usage may limit it for 2-3 days. Indeed, it is affordable and valuable compared to the price and features.</p><div class=\"brand-box brand-box-5\" id=\"brand-box-5\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; margin-bottom: 25px; border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); position: relative; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"brand-box-left\" style=\"width: 424.797px; padding: 10px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Product Specification:</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Brand: Amazfit</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Model: GTS 2/ GTR 2</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Supported Platform: Amazfit OS</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Connectivity: Bluetooth, wifi</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Color Option: Midnight Black</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Battery Life: 7-days</li></ul></div><div class=\"brand-box-right\" style=\"width: 283.188px; overflow: hidden;\"><img src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/5.-Amazfit-GTS-2.jpg\" class=\"brand-image\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; animation-name: scale; animation-duration: 3s; 