ion procedure</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Low noise</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">3-years of official warranty</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Conserve the natural flavor and ingredients</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Easy assembly and reverse function</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">UL and ETL certified</li></ul></div><div class=\"box-cons\" style=\"width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Cons</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Needs more time to complete the extraction process</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Needs extra effort</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Customer support needs improvement</li></ul></div><div class=\"overlay\" style=\"height: 573px; width: 708px; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; z-index: 1; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"></div></div><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kuvings_B6000W_Whole_Slow_Juicer\"></span>Kuvings B6000W Whole Slow Juicer<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In the last pick, we have another great product from the Kuvings brand. Indeed, it is one of the most popular and best juicers 2021. Not only is it amazing but also an efficient one. Just like the popular best juicers, it comes with multiple variants. There are three different color choices. Even though it has a plastic build quality, the overall design and features are pretty good. You can clean it easily and get an excellent juice extraction experience. It has a solid motor to do so. Although, it is an expensive one. So, make sure to look at the features before buying one.</p><div class=\"brand-box brand-box-5\" id=\"brand-box-5\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; margin-bottom: 25px; border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); position: relative; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"brand-box-left\" style=\"width: 424.797px; padding: 10px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Products Specification</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Brand: Kuvings</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Material: Plastic</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Color: Red, Silver, White</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Weight: 14.11 pounds</li></ul></div><div class=\"brand-box-right\" style=\"width: 283.188px; overflow: hidden;\"><img src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Kuvings-B6000W-Whole-Slow-Juicer.jpg\" class=\"brand-image\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; animation-name: scale; animation-duration: 3s; animation-iteration-count: infinite; animation-direction: alternate; animation-timing-function: linear;\"></div></div><div class=\"pros-cons-box\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); margin-bottom: 30px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; position: relative; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"box-pros\" style=\"border-right: 3px solid white; width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Pros</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Includes Jay kordich’skordich’s book</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Strong motor and efficient juice extraction</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">3-way ventilation</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Amazing Design and size</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Easy cleaning</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Wide feeder to speed up the procedure</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Suitable for fruits, vegetables, and leaves</li></ul></div><div class=\"box-cons\" style=\"width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Cons</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Cheap build quality</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Often gets jammed</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Manufacturer support needs improvement</li></ul></div><div class=\"overlay\" style=\"height: 487px; width: 708px; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; z-index: 1; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"></div></div><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_are_the_Benefits_and_Risks_of_Juicing\"></span>What are the Benefits and Risks of Juicing?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is no secret that fresh juices are healthier than processed juices bought at food stores. Besides, it saves you lots of bucks while also keeping your vitals healthy. You get the best out of fresh juice, as all&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.open.edu/openlearn/science-maths-technology/biology/nutrition-vitamins-and-minerals/content-section-0\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">the nutrients and vitamins</a>&nbsp;are all richly accounted for without having to consume uncomfortable vast amounts of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.health.harvard.edu/diet-and-weight-loss/drink-your-fruits-and-vegetables\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">fruits and vegetables</a>. Your body also requires&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10638941/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">antioxidants and enzymes</a>, which are hardly available in bottled fruit juices sold at the stores. Plus, they’re way healthier as there are no human-made additives involved. This means you always have control of what you decide to add to your juice. Since all you’re having is a glass of refreshing juice, digestion is way more comfortable.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It would equally be fair to admit that juicing has its risks. Firstly, juicing must not be assumed to be a direct replacement for other foods. Fruits have nutrients that are retained in the juices. However, the skin that is sometimes thrown away after peeling also contains fiber, which helps indigestion. While the peelings are edible, they’re peeled off during juicing and probably gotten rid of.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Juicing may require you to dig deeper into your pockets, causing financial strain. You will have to spend more on fruits and vegetables.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">People generally prefer fruit juices and a few vegetable juices. Fruit juices are sweet hence contain natural sugars. This can still result in increased blood sugar levels in the body. Fruit juices are rich in carbohydrates since they contain sugars—excessive carbohydrate intake results in weight gain.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Some juices aren’t enjoyable to drink, especially those extracted from vegetables. They taste strange and may sometimes have an unfriendly smell despite being healthy for consumption.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"When_You_Should_Replace_Your_Juicer\"></span>When You Should Replace Your Juicer<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Juicer replacement depends on personal preference as well as the juicer’s condition. Usually, there are many important factors regarding a juicer. Earlier, we discussed them. While using them, you may face different types of issues. Those issues can include temporary clogging, broken down, and so on. If the juicer can not perform expectedly, then it needs replacement or servicing. Sometimes the juicer malfunctions. All it needs is simple fixing. Besides, every juicer should do the blending or extraction as its manual says. If the performance gets slower, then you need to have a replacement.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">On the other hand, if there is any problem with the product by default, look at the warranty. Most of these products should come with a limited warranty period. Replace the product if there is any issue within the time. Remember that physical damage caused by the user will not allow a replacement.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As mentioned, another essential replacement issue is a personal choice. If you don’t think the size is good enough for your space, replace it with a better one. Besides, you should know that a juicer requirement is different for personal and commercial usages. So, if the requirement doesn’t match, then you also need a replacement.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Noise is also a significant concern for replacement issues. If the juicer creates a lot of noise, it can hinder families and kids. In that case, replace it immediately with a better version. At last, you have to consider your overall experience. If cleaning, operating, and other stuff regarding the juicer is not performing smoothly, try to replace it. Always make sure to consider the user reviews before getting any of them. We have a collection of the best juicers 2021. Follow them for the best experience.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Conclusion\"></span>Conclusion<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">So, how do you like our selected best juicers 2021? In terms of features, each of them comes with certain promising features. Even though the basic working procedure is similar, their efficiency varies a lot from each product. As we mentioned, there is build quality, working speed, cleaning efficiency, affordability, and more. A good juicer should have the overall balance among them.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">To select such a juicer, we have recommended 5 of the best juicers 2021. They vary from affordable range to expensive choices. If you want to put in some extra effort, then a cheap one would be enough. If you want to go for a more efficient one, then grab an expensive one. Make sure to have a warranty to replace the juicer for any inconvenience issue before buying. Make sure to follow the given buying guide. You will get fresh and natural juice every single time.</p>', 17, '3', '2021-11-15 07:51:02', '2021-11-08 00:20:11', '2021-11-15 01:51:02', '11/08/2021 12:19 PM', 'Phyllis Olson', 'best-juicers-review', 2, 'No');
