(79, 'Best Sandwich Makers in 2021: Top Toasters Reviews', 'best-sandwich-makers-in-2021-top-toasters-reviews', 'Best-Sandwich-Maker.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Sandwiches are excellent snacks that allow you to have a filling and healthy meal in the short term. You can have many variations, and indeed only your creativity and your sandwich-making device limit you. While you can always get a recipe online, finding the best sandwich maker may not be straightforward. There are so many options in the market, and technology keeps changing. What used to be the standard five years ago has got nothing on the modern units.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In choosing the best breakfast sandwich maker, you are looking for something that can make more than just sandwiches. Still, a variety of quick snacks can also add up to whole meals.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_Makes_a_Good_Sandwich_Maker\"></span>What Makes a Good Sandwich Maker?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As you begin your search for a sandwich maker, the question you should answer first is what defines a good sandwich maker? The answer to this is the quality of its cooking, fast cooking times, durability, and safe operation. These aspects cover the basic expectations.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">An excellent sandwich toaster should heat up fast to ensure quick cooking times. It should also cook your snack evenly, ensuring the browning is even and golden, and the slices are crisp. It should also close tightly to keep all the fillings in and prevent leaks. If you are using cheese, it should be melted at the end, and the ingredients should all have the same temperature. You also want a sandwich maker that you can touch the handles without the risk of burning. It should also be easy to clean and maintain.</p><table class=\"brand-list\" style=\"border-spacing: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 1.6em; width: 710px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><thead><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><th style=\"padding: 0.8em 0.8em 0.8em 0px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid lightgray; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\">Brand Name</th><th style=\"padding-top: 0.8em; padding-right: 0.8em; padding-bottom: 0.8em; text-align: left; border: 1px solid lightgray; background: rgb(242, 242, 242); padding-left: 10px !important;\">Brand Image</th><th style=\"padding-top: 0.8em; padding-right: 0.8em; padding-bottom: 0.8em; text-align: left; border: 1px solid lightgray; background: rgb(242, 242, 242); padding-left: 10px !important;\"></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><td style=\"padding-top: 0.8em; padding-right: 0.8em; padding-bottom: 0.8em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid lightgray; padding-left: 10px !important;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">Hamilton Beach Black Breakfast Sandwich Maker</p></td><td style=\"vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid lightgray; text-align: center; padding: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/1-Hamilton-Beach-Black-Breakfast-Sandwich-Maker.png\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 50px; height: auto;\"></td><td style=\"padding-top: 0.8em; padding-right: 0.8em; padding-bottom: 0.8em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px soli