ge whether it is safe to touch. We also looked at the color and evenness of the roasted sandwiches to gauge overall consistency in quality.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">We looked at the convenience of how easy it is to clean and maintain each unit.</li></ol><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Hamilton_Beach_Black_Breakfast_Sandwich_Maker\"></span>1. Hamilton Beach Black Breakfast Sandwich Maker<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The Hamilton Beach Sandwich Maker earns the overall best sandwich maker spot as it shines in critical aspects. It has some standout features, like allowing you to customize the layering of the sandwiches for a healthy family breakfast.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Whether you want to top up the sandwiches with cheese, meat, or eggs, the options are limitless. It also takes under 5 minutes to whip up your favorite morning snack, which is handy when pressed for time. There are plenty of conveniences too. It is an easy-to-use device, and all detachable parts are dishwasher safe. You can make all kinds of snacks with this breakfast maker, including bagels, English muffins, sandwiches, and more.</p><div class=\"brand-box brand-box-1\" id=\"brand-box-1\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; margin-bottom: 25px; border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); position: relative; color: rgba(0, 0