sparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Pros</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">It’s easy to assemble and use</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Excellent for making small sandwiches</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">It does not leave a metallic taste on the sandwiches</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Even cooking across the sandwiches</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">It’s multifunctional, thus saving time</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">It comes with easy and quick to cook recipes</li></ul></div><div class=\"box-cons\" style=\"width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Cons</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">It does not have automatic settings</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">It can get a bit messy when using cheese</li></ul></div><div class=\"overlay\" style=\"height: 444px; width: 708px; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; z-index: 1; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"></div></div><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_GOTHAM_STEEL_Electric_Sandwich_Maker\"></span>2. GOTHAM STEEL Electric Sandwich Maker<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The Gotham Steel electric sandwich maker is perfect for the budget shopper delivering premium quality at a bargain. Its main attraction is the highly non-stick surface courtesy of the titanium and ceramic material. This surface means you do not have to use any oil or butter while cooking, which is healthy for everyone in your home.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Making your ideal four toast pack takes under five minutes, and you do not have to worry about timing. The unit comes with an indicator light that will turn on when the snack is ready. Safety is a priority, and thanks to the cool handle, there is no risk of burning. We also liked the compact size, meaning space and portability will not be a problem.</p><div class=\"brand-box brand-box-2\" id=\"brand-box-2\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; margin-bottom: 25px; border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); position: relative; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"brand-box-left\" style=\"width: 424.797px; padding: 10px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Product Specifications</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Dimensions: 12 x 12 x 6 inches</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Weight: 2.97 pounds</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Brand: GOTHAM STEEL</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Available in black and brown colors</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem