 margin-bottom: initial;\">Easy cleaning</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Allows you to get creative in the kitchen</li></ul></div><div class=\"box-cons\" style=\"width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Cons</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">It does not have&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cde.ca.gov/ls/nu/sf/mbnsdsfsp012008.asp\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">temperature control</a></li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The length of the cord limits movement and placement</li></ul></div><div class=\"overlay\" style=\"height: 343px; width: 708px; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; z-index: 1; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"></div></div><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"7_OSTBA_LED_Indicator_Lights_Sandwich_Maker\"></span>7. OSTBA LED Indicator Lights Sandwich Maker<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The OSTBA sandwich maker is quite a powerful unit for its size. It heats up almost instantly, and with the double-side baking feature, it allows you to make your snack in quick times. It is also sturdy, which makes it highly durable. The compact size makes it easily portable, and storage is not stressful. You store it facing upwards, and the accompanying ridge makes it easy to wrap the cable around, preventing any harm. All these aspects make it take little space in your kitchen. The handle lock further eases carrying it around.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The fast-cooking times mean you need to be watchful, and thankfully, the built-in indicator lights will let you know when your snacks are ready. There is no risk of burning accidents as the handles are heat resistant and cool to touch even while cooking.</p><div class=\"brand-box brand-box-7\" id=\"brand-box-7\" style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; margin-bottom: 25px; border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); position: relative; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"brand-box-left\" style=\"width: 424.797px; padding: 10px; background: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Product Specifications</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Power: 750W</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Dimensions: 8.26 x 8.66 x 3.22 inches</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Plate sizes: 8.46 x 4.92 inches</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Diagonal indentation surface type</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Durable and non-stick coating design</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Plates cooking temperature: 200+/- 20 Fahrenheit</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Available in black color</li></ul></div><div class=\"brand-box-right\" style=\"width: 283.188px; overflow: hidden;\"><img src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/7.-OSTBA-LED-Indicator-Lights-Sandwich-Maker.png\" class=\"brand-image\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; animation-name: scale; animation-duration: 3s; animation-iteration-count: infinite; animation-direction: alternate; animation-timing-function: linear;\"></div></div><div class=\"pros-cons-box\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(242, 242, 242); margin-bottom: 30px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; position: relative; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0px 30px 25px -35px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><div class=\"box-pros\" style=\"border-right: 3px solid white; width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Pros</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">It is easy to set up and use</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">You do not need to use oil on any food</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Excellent quality at a great price</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Children friendly</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Easy cleaning as you can rinse with cold water right after cooking</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">It only takes a minute to heat</li></ul></div><div class=\"box-cons\" style=\"width: 354px; padding: 30px 20px; z-index: 2; transition: all 0.5s ease 0s; background: transparent;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Cons</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">It does not come with an on and off button</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The size is small for regular-sized slices of bread and heavy filling.</li></ul></div><div class=\"overlay\" style=\"height: 415px; width: 708px; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transition: all 0.3s ease 0s; z-index: 1; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"></div></div><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Benefits_of_Using_a_Sandwich_Maker\"></span>Benefits of Using a Sandwich Maker<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Using a sandwich maker presents numerous benefits, including;</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Affordable\"></span>Affordable<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Most sandwich maker units are available at an affordable cost. It is not rare to find high-quality units for a bargain. This factor allows anyone to own them, and you could even go for two units if they offer different utilities that you want.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Excellent_Taste\"></span>Excellent Taste<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Food from a sandwich maker has excellent taste. What’s more, they allow you to experiment with various options, especially for the filling. This aspect enables you to make your favorite snacks just as you want them, and you do not struggle with monotony.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Easy_Clean-up\"></span>Easy Clean-up<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">All good sandwich makers come with a non-stick coating, making it easy to clean as there are no sticky food elements. Most of them are dishwasher friendly or come with removable parts that you can clean in a dishwasher. Some are even simpler to clean, requiring wiping with a damp cloth only.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Healthy_Food\"></span>Healthy Food<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Sandwich makers promote healthy eating:</p><ol style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You can add sufficient vegetable and protein options to help you meet your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.hsph.harvard.edu/nutritionsource/healthy-eating-plate/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">daily dietary requirements</a>&nbsp;through your filling.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Their design means you use little to no oil when making the snacks which prevents too much fat in your body.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">They make cooking home snacks preferable to junk food from fast food outlets.</li></ol><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Multifunctional\"></span>Multifunctional<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Moder sandwich makers are multifunctional. You can cook several snacks in them, not just sandwiches. You can make other foods, including waffles and omelets, among others. Finally, they serve both heating and grilling purposes.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Compact_and_Portable\"></span>Compact and Portable<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Most units are compact, making storage easy, and they do not take much space on the counter when they are in use. Their size also makes them light and easy to carry for picnics and camping.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Fast_Cook_Up_Times\"></span>Fast Cook Up Times<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Whether it is breakfast or just a snack for the day, time is of the essence. Fast cook times are a defining characteristic of sandwich makers, making them convenient for use anytime.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Easy_to_Use\"></span>Easy to Use<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There is no learning curve with sandwich makers, unlike most other kitchen gadgets. You only need a minor assembly of parts, and they are ready to use. There is no much involvement from your end.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_to_See_When_You_Picking_a_Sandwich_Maker_for_Your_Kitchen\"></span>What to See When You Picking a Sandwich Maker for Your Kitchen<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are several key factors to keep in mind when you are choosing a sandwich maker. These include;</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Size of the unit:</span>&nbsp;Sandwich makers come in different sizes, including for one-person use and family use. It also depends on the amount of filling you want to use and the storage space available in your home.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Ease of cleaning:</span>&nbsp;Sandwich makers with non-stick coating only require a damp cloth to wipe them. Others are dishwasher safe, while some low-end ones will require handwashing. Pick a unit that meets your time needs.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Consistency:</span>&nbsp;Look for a sandwich that provides even pressing, uniform browning, and even temperature across all the food.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Storability:</span>&nbsp;A good unit should allow you to store it safely and without taking much space.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Versatility:</span>&nbsp;The proper sandwich should be able to cook more than just toasts. Suitable units can cook vegetables, grill meat, and make waffles, among others.</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Basic_Sandwich_Maker_Instructions\"></span>Basic Sandwich Maker Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is essential to follow the user manual that comes with your unit. If it is not there, then follow the following basic guidelines for use.</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Connect the sandwich maker to a power source and keep the lid closed as it heats up. Most units come with a light indicator or an alternative mechanism to let you know when it is ready.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Prepare your sandwich in your preferred manner.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Open sandwich maker. If you did not spread butter on the outer surfaces of the slices, you could spray a fine mist of oil on both lower and upper plates.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Put the sandwich gently on the bottom plate, taking care not to touch any plate surface.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Close the lid, including the front clamp, if it comes with one.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Give it 3 to 5 minutes or until the indicator light comes up, and then open the toaster.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Pick the sandwich pieces with a silicon or wooden spatula.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Disconnect the sandwich maker and leave it open to cool. Once it is completely cool, wipe the plates or use a dishwasher.</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Conclusion\"></span>Conclusion&nbsp;<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are many options in the market for sandwich makers, and this article gives you the information you need to find the right one. It starts with you defining what you want from your sandwich maker, given your circumstances. You then should consider the various quality of the sandwich maker, including its versatility, durability, cooking time, and the quality of the results. You also should look at convenience aspects such as ease of cleaning and storage.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Once you find the right sandwich maker, you need to follow instructions for use and care. Simple steps like proper cleaning, closing the lid when storing the maker will go a long way in extending the unit’s life.</p>', 17, '3', '2021-11-15 07:51:18', '2021-11-08 00:23:33', '2021-12-08 05:08:46', '11/08/2021 12:22 PM', 'Phyllis Olson', 'best-sandwich-makers', 2, 'No');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(80, 'Smart Devices and How They Affect Our Modern Life', 'smart-devices-and-how-they-affect-our-modern-life', 'Smart-Devices.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Remember the Jetsons, the space-age family? Saturday mornings gave us a portal to life far into the future. It turns out that it was not so far off after all. Smart devices are all around us. They help us get more done in our day and connect us to family and friends that are far away. Additionally, they can help run our homes and lives more efficiently. Furthermore, in a global pandemic, smart devices help children keep learning and adults working.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">But, as Uncle Ben told Peter Parker in Spiderman, “With great power comes great responsibility.” Are we responsible for our smart devices? Is there a downside to all this power at the touch of a finger? Keep reading to find out.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_is_a_Smart_Device\"></span>What is a Smart Device?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">A smart device is an electronic device that can interact with other electronic devices or networks. Also, they can interact with the user and allow the user to interact with other electronic devices. As a result, all this connectivity forms the Internet of Things (IoT). Smart devices are everywhere, and we use them for more than calling or texting. Our smartphones allow us to use social media, surf the internet, check our stocks, etc.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Furthermore, we can equip our homes with smart appliances, smart temperature control, and intelligent lighting. Digital assistants use Artificial Intelligence (AI) to perform tasks and answer queries. At the sound of your voice, they can tell you the weather, the news, and scheduled appointments.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_Do_Smart_Devices_Communicate\"></span>How Do Smart Devices Communicate?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As mentioned previously, smart devices are electronic devices that connect with other electronic devices. But, how do they work, and how do they communicate with us and other devices?</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">First, it’s essential to know how they collect data from their physical environment. They do it with sensors, which observe and measure their physical environment. After observing and measuring, they convert the data they collect to understand other smart devices or human. By observing the environment around them, sensors can measure the distance between current and desired conditions.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">With all these connected devices forming the IoT, they can swap data and provide information to help in decision making. Big Data is the term given to a large amount of gathered information. Companies analyze this data to look at trends and consumer information to adapt and grow.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However, more data comes at faster rates, so analysis also needs to be faster.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-artificial-intelligence/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Artificial Intelligence mimics human intelligence</a>&nbsp;in terms of cognitive thinking and problem-solving. Machine learning involves detecting patterns, making adjustments, and produce analysis at more incredible speeds. Moreover, AI can use its analytical skills and cognition to predict future trends.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Use_Smart_Devices_Safely\"></span>How to Use Smart Devices Safely<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Smart devices collect and share data to keep us entertained, informed, and productive. But, sharing that data may cost us in terms of privacy. You may be concerned about what happens with that data and where it goes. You might wonder if someone may hack your accounts with that information. Your information can be compromised, but there are many things you can do to keep your data (somewhat) private.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">These six tips will help you keep your data more secure.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-41\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Smart-Device.jpg\" alt=\"Smart Device\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Smart-Device.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Smart-Device-300x150.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Smart-Device-768x384.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Have_a_strong_Password_for_your_Home_Wi-Fi\"></span>Have a strong Password for your&nbsp;Home Wi-Fi<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Don’t use something that others can easily guess, such as birthdays, children’s names, etc. Use a combination of lower- and upper-case letters, numbers, and special characters. Adding&nbsp;<a href=\"https://its.uiowa.edu/duo\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">two-factor authorization adds an extra layer of security</a>.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Know_What_Data_is_Being_Collected\"></span>Know What Data is Being Collected<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Before downloading an app, find out what data it is collecting and how it’s shared.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Review_your_Privacy_settings\"></span>Review your&nbsp;Privacy settings&nbsp;<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Go to the settings feature on your smart device. See what information your app is sharing, i.e., location.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Download_and_Install_Updates\"></span>Download and Install&nbsp;Updates<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Both your smart device and its applications occasionally have software updates. Those updates offer new features. Some include added security when a company has found a vulnerability that allows hackers to access your device.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Put_Parental_Controls_in_Place_If_You_Have_Children_in_your_Home\"></span>Put Parental&nbsp;Controls in Place If You&nbsp;Have Children in your Home<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Some devices and software applications allow you to limit what your children can access and share.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Practice_Safe_Connectivity\"></span>Practice Safe Connectivity<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As tempting as it may be to access social media via the wi-fi at your local coffee shop, think twice before doing so. Public networks allow hackers the opportunity to get access to your device.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Smart_Devices_in_the_Workplace\"></span>Smart Devices in the Workplace<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In addition to helping our homes and personal lives to run more smoothly, smart devices can make us more productive at our workplace. Our smart devices can help us manage our schedules and can help colleagues to collaborate on projects. Corporations can use smart devices to regulate a building’s temperature, and lights can be turned on in a room when the light sensor detects movement. The IoT helps industries to monitor and analyze trends to maximize available resources.&nbsp; The best use of IoT lowers cost and increases profit.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Do_Smart_Devices_Make_Us_Lazy\"></span>Do Smart Devices Make Us Lazy?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Smart devices can make our lives easier and give us more free time, but what are we doing with that time? Some people find it difficult to disconnect from their smart devices, thus giving them little interaction with the people around them. Families, where each person has their own device, might find themselves communicating less with each other.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Relying too much on smart technology reduces our critical thinking skills. Allowing a GPS to direct us to our destination doesn’t give us a chance to strengthen our memory, which may lower our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5403814/\" rel=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">cognitive functioning</a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Smart devices don’t make us lazy. As individuals, we can choose what to do with the extra free time that smart devices allow. Some people will put that spare time to good use, such as more time engaged in physical activity or developing new skills. However, if someone has a predisposition to laziness, they will spend extra time sitting in a chair and watching television.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Bottom_Line\"></span>The Bottom Line<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Smart devices are a part of our everyday lives. They are in our homes, our schools, and our workplaces. The IoT will continue to grow at exponential rates as there is an exchange of more data. They can help us become more efficient, lower utility costs, and monitor our health. At the sound of your voice, a video call can be initiated with loved ones and connect across the miles.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">But there are downfalls in the extensive use of our electronic devices if they’re not used wisely. Each time your device shares your data, you will lose some privacy, so you need to decide what personal information you want to share and set controls.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It’s also up to you how to use your time freed up due to greater efficiency. By spending more time with family, engaging in enjoyable physical activity, or pursuing a hobby, we can enhance our lives. Our smart devices can be a great asset or a great liability. It’s up to us to decide which one it is. What are your thoughts?</p>', 17, '3', '2021-11-15 07:51:27', '2021-11-08 00:27:44', '2021-11-15 01:51:27', '11/08/2021 12:27 PM', 'Phyllis Olson', 'how-smart-devices-affect-our-modern-life', 0, 'No'),
(81, 'CANNABIS How to Take CBD Oil: A Beginner’s Guide', 'cannabis-how-to-take-cbd-oil-a-beginners-guide', 'How-to-Take-CBD-Oil.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">CBD or cannabidiol keeps increasing in popularity. However, the popularity of CBD is not surprising at all. After all, CBD is a very safe and very versatile drug, therapeutically speaking. This is currently available in the markets even though CBD does not have psychoactive properties.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Because it does not have THC (tetrahydrocannabinol), it is crucial to figure out How to Take CBD Oil because the dosages vary depending on how the person chooses to consume CBD.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Anyone who desires to learn How to Take CBD Oil effectively needs to look at this guide. Here, they will find information also on how to take CBD oil for different health ailments. Also, they will find a dosage guide in how much CBD oil they should take a day. Of course, information on how often they should take CBD oil a day is in here as well.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Take_CBD_Oil\"></span>How to Take CBD Oil?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There might be a solution for anyone who currently suffers from seizures, insomnia, or anxiety. To find relief, anyone who suffers from these kinds of ailments should take CBD oil. They may also&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-cbd\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">know CBD as cannabidiol</a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Even though there is not much evidence available currently to prove the benefits of consuming CBD oil, there is evidence to prove that the consumption of CBD oil helps with some forms of epilepsy. Nevertheless, scientists continue to research this topic.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Anyone can find CBD oil in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/what-is-cannabis\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">cannabis plant</a>. This generally comes from hemp. Even though CBD is one of the components of marijuana,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/does-cbd-get-you-high\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">CBD oil will not get the consumer high</a>&nbsp;because it does not contain THC or tetrahydrocannabinol. Therefore, it does not have psychoactive properties.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Nowadays, several areas allow people to sell, use, and buy CBD oil. However, this depends on the different areas. This means that anyone who wishes to start consuming this must check the laws in the area.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Several different ways exist to consume CBD oil. A person may use edibles, tinctures, or capsules, among other forms. Regardless of the administration method, the effects of the chemicals remain the same. But it may have a different effect on how they affect the consumer.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Before anyone starts consuming CBD oil, they must consult with their medical practitioners. The same goes if they have any side effects or if they are treating seizures.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3212\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/How-to-Take-CBD-Oil-bb.jpg\" alt=\"Take CBD oil\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/How-to-Take-CBD-Oil-bb.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/How-to-Take-CBD-Oil-bb-300x169.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/How-to-Take-CBD-Oil-bb-768x432.jpg 768w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/How-to-Take-CBD-Oil-bb-400x225.jpg 400w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/How-to-Take-CBD-Oil-bb-600x338.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"9_Best_Ways_to_Take_CBD_Oil_Effectively\"></span>9 Best Ways to Take CBD Oil Effectively<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As it was stated before, there are many ways to take CBD oil. But people want to know which way is the most effective. That is why any person can check here the nine best ways to take CBD oil effectively.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">From tinctures to capsules, smoothies, coffees, salad dressings, inhalation, sweet treats, tropical rubs or balms or creams, to cocktails. Take a look at the differences between the best different ways to take CBD oil effectively.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CBD_Oil_in_Tincture\"></span>CBD Oil in Tincture<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">CBD oil in tincture is helpful to take the cannabidiol sublingually. This means putting the CBD oil under the tongue. The consumer simply needs to put some drops under their tongue.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Then they must hold it inside their mouths for thirty seconds before swallowing. This method is quite discreet and provides calmness and a feeling of well-being as well. It also allows the person to control the amount that they take. However, it does take a longer time for the person to feel its effects.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CBD_Oil_in_Capsule\"></span>CBD Oil in Capsule<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">CBD oil in a capsule is a relatively easy and convenient way to consume it. The label on the capsule container provides information on what the recommended dose is. The label also informs the consumer on how to take them. The person will probably be able to feel the effects around thirty minutes after the consumption.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The foods that the person consumes when they take CBD oil may affect its absorption. They are pretty easy to take and carry around. But they do not provide relief as fast as other delivery methods. However, taking capsules allows the consumer to take the same dose every time.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CBD_Oil_in_Smoothie\"></span>CBD Oil in Smoothie<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are specific CBD oil blends that have a somewhat earthy, pungent taste. Not everybody likes that. Therefore, some try to cover its flavor with other ingredients. Some people like to add half a teaspoon of CBD oil to their morning smoothies. This will give them a calm start to their day.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CBD_Oil_in_Coffee\"></span>CBD Oil in Coffee<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Several CBD coffee brands say that they are infusing their coffee beans with CBD. Because they say that this helps diffuse the anxiety that comes with consuming caffeine. Another option would be to utilize milk that is free of dairy and that is infused with CBD. That allows the person to control easily the dose of CBD that they are taking.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CBD_Oil_in_Salad_Dressing\"></span>CBD Oil in Salad Dressing<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Another easy way to take CBD is to incorporate some CBD oil into their daily cooking. A lot of health benefits can come from this without having to put a significant effort into it. The consumer can add two teaspoons of CBD, 3 or 4 olive oil tablespoons, some lemon juice, pepper, and salt. That will make a very nutritious and delicious salad dressing.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CBD_Oil_in_Inhalation_Vapes_Pre-Rolls\"></span>CBD Oil in Inhalation (Vapes &amp; Pre-Rolls)<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">One of the safest ways to consume CBD is by inhalation. The CBD will go directly into the consumer’s lungs and bloodstream. The person can choose to vape or smoke it.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If the consumer decides to vape, they will need a vaporizer pen. This will give the person the maximum effect the CBD can cause. But they won’t need to suffer through the harsh feeling that comes from the smoke on their lungs and throat. However, it might give the person a higher dose than the one they intended to take.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If the consumer decides to smoke the CBD oil, then they need an oil rig. The consumer will have to heat the nail. After that, they will need to place the CBD oil into the nail. They will need to use a dabber to do this. All of this will produce the smoke that the person then has to inhale.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Otherwise, the consumer can roll a join of high CBD marijuana. This is the quickest way to consume CBD oil due to its high concentration. The consumer can also easily track how much they consume. Yet, using this method entails consuming THC as well. However, smoking does have a harsh effect on the lungs and throat.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CBD_Oil_in_Sweet_Treats\"></span>CBD Oil in Sweet Treats<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Taking CBD oil in sweet treats is very easy to consume and transport as well. The consumer can choose to bake CBD oil into any sweet treats like brownies, cookies, or candy. However, some baked goods could need some refrigeration storage to maintain the freshness of the CBD.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CBD_Oil_in_Topical_Rub_or_Balm_or_Cream\"></span>CBD Oil in Topical Rub or Balm or Cream<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">One of the easiest ways to consume CBD oil is using a topical rub, balm, or cream. The consumer will not need any kind of knowledge or tool to make use of it. The person has to check the dose they need and apply it to the required section of their skin. This method works best for skin conditions, migraines, and sore muscles. If applied to the temple, it can alleviate the pains that come with migraines.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CBD_Oil_in_Cocktail\"></span>CBD Oil in Cocktail<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The person can consume CBD oil in a cocktail without any significant issues because CBD oil can be mixed with any food and drink.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Take_CBD_Oil_for_Different_Health_Ailments\"></span>How to Take CBD Oil for Different Health Ailments?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">CBD oil can help with several different health ailments. But the consumer needs to figure out how to take it. So here are some guidelines for that.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CBD_Oil_for_Pain_Relief\"></span>CBD Oil for Pain Relief<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There are three ways to take CBD oil for pain relief. The person can take it orally, sublingually, or topically.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CBD_Oil_for_Sleep\"></span>CBD Oil for Sleep<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">To help the consumer sleep, the best option would be to use tinctures. This will help them relax and find sleep.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"CBD_Oil_for_Anxiety\"></span>CBD Oil for Anxiety<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">To calm anxiety, the consumer can take CBD oil in 5 different ways. The person can use a sublingual spray, edibles, oil, capsules, cannabis flowers, or vaporized oil.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_Much_CBD_Oil_Should_I_Take_A_Day_Dosage_Guide\"></span>How Much CBD Oil Should I Take A Day? Dosage Guide<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">A CBD oil dosage can be pretty hard to calculate. The main reason for this is that the consumer needs to consider many things. One of the most important ones is the person’s weight. The same goes for the strength of the CBD oil that they wish to take. Every person has a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/human-endocannabinoid-system\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">different endocannabinoid system</a>. Therefore, different amounts of CBD oil might be needed to get the same desired effects.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Before changing the amount that a person intake of their supplement, they need to consult their medical practitioners because they might need less or more CBD, this will depend on what they are battling, whether it is cancer, seizures, anxiety, pain, sleep deprivation, or other issues.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is pretty hard to provide exact serving size and dosage recommendations for CBD. The reason behind this is the variation in the effects that CBD oil may have on different people. That is why the best suggestion would be to check a dosage calculator. That should better indicate to the person how much CBD oil to take.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">After the person finds out their Reference Daily Intake (RDI), the new consumer should begin with the minimum dose recommended. Once they prove that it is not enough, they can slowly start increasing the mg CBD dose that they take. They will eventually find the balance that they need to get the best results for them.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">An essential thing to notice is that overdosing on CBD is possible. Even though overdosing on CBD won’t cause a fatality, it can cause other side effects. The adverse side effects are few, but they still exist. These include diarrhea, nausea, temporary drop in&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/bloodpressure/facts.htm\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">blood pressure</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.vsu.edu/healthservices/upset-stomach.php\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">upset stomach</a>, lethargy, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://medlineplus.gov/ency/article/003208.htm\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">drowsiness</a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However, the exact dose that can lead to having a side effect is not known yet. So that is the reason why any new consumer needs to start with the lowest dose. Then they can go up from there until they get the results that they want.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_Often_Should_I_Take_CBD_Oil_A_Day\"></span>How Often Should I Take CBD Oil A Day?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As previously mentioned in this text, a CBD oil dosage can be pretty hard to calculate since the FDA or Food and Drug Administration is yet to establish a formal nutritional guideline for this. The FDA is also yet to establish the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/cbd-health-benefits\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">health benefits that come from taking any CBD product</a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Therefore, there isn’t an RDI or recommended daily intake yet for CBD oil. Even though the companies establish on their product’s labels serving suggestions. The companies themselves come up with those serving recommendations. That means that they are not following any standard guidelines or any official research.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Bottom_Line\"></span>The Bottom Line<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">To sum up, the person who wishes to start consuming CBD oil needs to know how to Take CBD Oil properly. That is if they want to achieve the best results. Along with this text, several ways to consume CBD oil effectively have been mentioned.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Here, explanations are available on making tinctures, capsules, smoothies, coffees, salad dressings, inhalation, sweet treats, tropical rubs or balms or creams, and cocktails. Therefore, the future consumer can take a look and decide which one they prefer.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Arguably, how much CBD oil should the person take a day is just as important as how to take it. Because, after all, the person does not want to consume too much to deal with unwanted effects. No one wants to consume too little. Because that would prevent them from getting the desired effect, so choose wisely.</p>', 19, '3', '2021-11-15 07:52:49', '2021-11-08 00:54:36', '2021-11-15 01:52:49', '11/08/2021 12:50 PM', 'Terence Watson', 'how-to-take-cbd-oil', 0, 'No');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(83, 'What Is Cannabis? Clear Every Doubt Out!', 'what-is-cannabis-clear-every-doubt-out', 'What-is-Cannabis.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It seems that cannabis has finally broken the “don’t-talk-about-it” barrier. Nowadays, it is everywhere. As proof of this, think of the last national elections. Many candidates made weed legalization or banned a cornerstone of their platforms.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">On the other hand, those who didn’t were still pressured to stand for or against marijuana. Moreover, media outlets periodically held debates with or invited researchers to talk about it. There’s some genuine interest in weed.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However, if you ever wanted to find someone who has utter misconceptions about marijuana, you wouldn’t need to turn many stones. Misinformation abounds, especially in the online era.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Therefore, here we are to clear any doubts and answer the question, “what is cannabis?”. Keep on reading to find everything about it: its history, its uses, its&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/cbd-health-benefits\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">potential health benefits</a>, and whether it is legal or not.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_Is_Cannabis\"></span>What Is Cannabis?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Cannabis is a plant that people have been using for centuries for recreational properties and treating different illnesses. Every part of it is used, from the dried leaves to the seeds. There are several ways of consuming cannabis. Among them can find:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: left;\">Smoking</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: left;\">Eating it raw</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: left;\">Brewing their leaves for tea</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: left;\">Digesting it through capsules</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: left;\">Eating it in cannabis-infused edibles, such as gummies or brownies</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: left;\">Through your skin in topicals, balms, or even in a bath with cannabis bath bombs and</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial; text-align: left;\">Drinking it in cannabis-infused drinks</li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Moreover, the plant is made of different components, called cannabinoids. Although there are&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/top-cannabinoids\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">different types of cannabinoids</a>, two of them caught all the attention. We are talking, of course, of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/cbd-vs-thc\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">cannabidiol and tetrahydrocannabinol</a>, or CBD and THC.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">THC is famous for being responsible for getting people high due to its psychoactive effects. CBD, in contrast, is non-psychoactive and is used in several medical treatments, which we’ll talk about below.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Lastly, we should talk about the plants in the cannabis family. Those who aren’t experts usually mention marijuana and hemp interchangeably.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However, they are not the same. While both plants have the same cannabinoids, the amounts vary. Hemp contains a large amount of CBD and less than 0.3% of THC. Due to this, it won’t make you high. In contrast, marijuana has less CBD and more than 0.3% THC, making it psychoactive.<img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-2947\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cannabis.jpg\" alt=\"cannabis\" width=\"800\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cannabis.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cannabis-300x225.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cannabis-768x576.jpg 768w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cannabis-180x135.jpg 180w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cannabis-400x300.jpg 400w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/cannabis-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_Does_It_Make_You_Feel\"></span>How Does It Make You Feel?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The feelings one can experience vary from person to person. Nevertheless, there are some documented and widely known effects that cannabis has on people. When you incorporate cannabis, in any the possible ways, you might feel:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">A feeling of joy or euphoria, which people know as a “high”</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Relaxation</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Some changes in how you perceive your surroundings, for example, of time, space and colors</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">A sudden craving for a lot of food, also known as “having the munchies” and</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Having more confidence and an eagerness for talking</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Origins_Of_Cannabis_Where_Does_It_Come_From\"></span>The Origins Of Cannabis: Where Does It Come From?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Nowadays, you can find locally-grown hemp and marijuana in the cannabis market, but it wasn’t always this way. Cannabis isn’t original to the Americas but Central Asia.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Therefore, how has this plant arrived on the continent? Let’s dive deep into the history of cannabis to know what it went through to end on your joint finally.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As mentioned above, the cannabis plant comes from the Eastern hemisphere. The first known use of it dates back to 500 B.C. How do we know this? Archeologists have found this plant’s origin in Siberia’s and China’s antique shamans’ graves.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This discovery suggests these cultures knew about the psychoactive effects and used them for religious services and medical treatments. Afterward, nomads began spreading the plant.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As a result, by 800 A.D., hashish, a smokable type of purified cannabis, was already popular throughout Asia and the Middle East. The use of the plant raised a lot of controversies, though, especially in Muslim cultures.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The reason for this is because the Quran prohibits consuming alcohol and intoxicating substances. As cannabis wasn’t mentioned, however, many argued it wasn’t forbidden.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Later, trade with bordering countries introduced cannabis to Africa and Europe. While in Europe, the uses were similar to those of Asia. Nevertheless, Africans consumed their seeds similarly to today, and cannabis was part of some medical treatments.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Moreover, they started making clothes and ropes with the fiber of the plant. With time, Asians also discovered the fiber was great for making paper.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As the plant’s popularity continued growing, it became essential in many societies. Moreover, cannabis doesn’t require special climate conditions. As a consequence, you can grow it anywhere without extreme weather conditions.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Because of this, farmers didn’t hesitate to bring it to the Americas during the colonial era. The rest, as they say, is history.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cannabis_Medical_Uses_As_Medicine\"></span>Cannabis Medical Uses As Medicine<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Researchers are continuously finding new medical cannabis uses. Nowadays, the National Academies of Sciences, Engineering, and Medicine supports cannabis for treating different diseases. Doctors employ cannabis in the treatment of certain illnesses such as:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><a href=\"https://www.health.harvard.edu/blog/chronic-pain-the-invisible-disability-2017042811360\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Chronic pains in adults</a></li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Nausea and vomiting that chemotherapy usually provokes; and</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\"><a href=\"https://www.ninds.nih.gov/Disorders/Patient-Caregiver-Education/Hope-Through-Research/Multiple-Sclerosis-Hope-Through-Research\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Multiple sclerosis symptoms</a></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Moreover, in 2018, the FDA approved Epidiolex. This drug was designed to help treat some types of epilepsy. This was the first step in the fight to regulate. Also, it was a big win for cannabis advocates. We had Charlotte Figi’s parents, whose daughter’s case and treatment with cannabis awoke a nation.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Finally, there is some evidence that hemp oil can be beneficial to people suffering from disorders. These include sleep apnea and eating disorders, such as anorexia and low appetite. What’s more, it can help with mental issues like anxiety disorders,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.cedars-sinai.org/health-library/diseases-and-conditions/t/tourette-syndrome.html\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Tourette’s syndrome</a>, and substance abuse disorders.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Health_Effects_Of_Cannabis\"></span>The Health Effects Of Cannabis<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As not everything that shines is gold, cannabis has also been linked to some symptoms. The side effects you can have from consuming hemp are two-fold: mental and physical. Some of the negative physical symptoms you can feel are:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Breathing problems due to the smoke it produces, which has similar consequences to that of tobacco;</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Increased heart rate for up to 3 hours after smoking it which increases the risk of heart attacks;</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Child development issues when pregnant and after such as lower body weight and damaged brain; and</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Nausea and vomiting for long-term cannabis users who suffer from&nbsp;<a href=\"https://myhealth.ucsd.edu/Library/DiseasesConditions/Adult/134,604\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Cannabinoid Hyperemesis Syndrome</a>.</li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">On the other hand, as these weren’t enough, there’s a series of mental problems you can develop because of cannabis. These are:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Temporary paranoia</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Temporary hallucinations</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Depression</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Anxiety and</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Possibly deteriorating symptoms in schizophrenia patients</li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However, as frightening as it might appear, we need to remember that reported cases of severe side effects tend to be far from ordinary. Moreover, as with any other product, you should permanently suspend the use of cannabis and ask your doctor in case of any doubt.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Potential_Health_Benefits_Of_Cannabis\"></span>Potential Health Benefits Of Cannabis<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">With soaring popularity and an ever-growing market, companies are allocating more money to finance studies. Consequently, cannabis health benefits continue ramping up. The potential benefits this plant has for us are marvelous. Therefore, let’s take a look at what can be achieved with this beautiful plant:</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Weight_Loss\"></span>Weight Loss<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">While cannabis is famous for giving users a vast appetite when they consume it, being overweight is usually not an issue. The reason is that cannabis can aid your body by helping it produce or regulate insulin while also dealing correctly with your caloric intake.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Diabetes_Prevention\"></span>Diabetes Prevention<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">As cannabis is excellent at regulating insulin, it’s only logical it can help with and prevent diabetes. According to a study of the American Alliance for Medical Cannabis, this logic stands. Their research shows that weed can lower blood sugars and pressure levels and improve its circulation.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Stress_and_Anxiety_Management\"></span>Stress and Anxiety Management<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Although cannabis can cause anxiety in people, the proper dosage has shown it helps users relax. Undoubtedly, we always advise you to consult with your doctor, especially if you’re very anxious.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hindering_Alzheimers_Disease\"></span>Hindering Alzheimer’s Disease<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Cognitive degeneration is the leading cause for developing Alzheimer’s disease. Nevertheless, as our hair whitens and wrinkles appear, avoiding it is no easy task. Hopefully, cannabis has anti-inflammatory properties that fight brain inflammation, slowing Alzheimer’s down.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Helps_With_PTSD\"></span>Helps With PTSD<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Although most think of wars and veterans when someone mentions PTSD, these are far from the cases. Anyone who went through a traumatic experience, such as assault, sexual abuse, or maybe a car crash, can develop it. Cannabis has been linked to easing the flight or fight response that can be triggered.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Health_Risk_Of_Cannabis\"></span>The Health Risk Of Cannabis<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Apart from the possible side effects, there are some health risks in the long term. Marijuana users might face:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Judgment Impairment</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This can lead to higher chances of domestic and road accidents. As a consequence, driving isn’t advisable for up to 3 hours after consuming cannabis.</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Gum Disease</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">A study carried out by the American Dental Association showed that smoking weed and gum disease might be connected at some point.</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Loss Of Memory</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Users, especially those who consume marijuana strains with high THC levels, can suffer from acute memory loss. Moreover, chances of having this are higher for under 25-year-olds, whose brains aren’t fully developed.</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Testicular Cancer</span></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In 2018, a study conducted on Swedish men showed the use of cannabis throughout one’s lifetime increases the risk of testicular cancer.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Is_Cannabis_Addictive\"></span>Is Cannabis Addictive?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Despite being widely spread, there are no reported cases of overdoses. Moreover, researchers consider it impossible to consume so much marijuana that you’ll face life-threatening symptoms.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">However, there have been reports of people getting hooked on cannabis and having issues with quitting it. Although it might seem shocking, a Jama Psychiatry carried out a 10-year-old study that showed some discouraging numbers.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Results revealed that between 9 and 30 out of every 100 users could develop marijuana abuse disorders. In other words, people had trouble leaving cannabis even though it impacted negatively on their lives.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">What’s more, these statistics multiply up to seven times in users who began consuming before reaching legal voting age. People who found difficulty in quitting cannabis showed different abstinence symptoms. These include sleep deprivation, grouchiness, and anxiety.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In addition, there are also some possible eating disorders such as an appetite decrease and having solid cravings. For people struggling, group support has shown to be effective.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Is_Cannabis_Legal\"></span>Is Cannabis Legal?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This is probably the public’s favorite question, especially here in the U.S. The answer, nevertheless, depends on where you live. Moreover, the fight against federal and local governments makes it unclear sometimes. However, here the distinction between hemp and marijuana is critical.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Hemp, which has less than 0.3% THC and therefore no psychoactive effects, is legal federally. However, some states have a prohibition that deems it illegal within their borders. As a result, CBD-infused cannabis products (not only the dried leaves) can get you in trouble there.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">On the other hand, marijuana, or cannabis with psychoactive effects and content higher than 0.3% THC, is federally banned. Despite Congress’s prohibition, some states have passed legislation allowing marijuana for medical uses.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Even more, some have gone above and beyond and accept marijuana consumption for recreational uses. It would be best if you remembered that transporting marijuana between borders is still a federal crime.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">All in all, our recommendation is always to check local legislation. In addition, keep in mind that, even though there’s a massive market for them, the FDA doesn’t regulate cannabis products. For this reason, manufacturers can often mislabel their products to sell more.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Hopefully, this situation will change with time as more and more states lift their bans or legalize marijuana altogether.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Bottom_Line\"></span>The Bottom Line<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This ancient plant has several recreational and medical uses most can benefit from. Moreover, stepping back and looking at the bigger picture and how it came to where cannabis is today is also enjoyable. It puts importance into perspective. Therefore, as the battle for legalization rages on, it’s essential to know its effects on us.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Finally, we hope our article has shed some light on cannabis’s health benefits and risks. We highly encourage you to find out if cannabis products are legal in your state and try them out. There’s a ton of benefits waiting for you. So, tell us, what are you waiting for?</p>', 19, '3', '2021-11-15 07:52:59', '2021-11-08 01:00:03', '2021-11-28 00:27:25', '11/08/2021 12:58 PM', 'Terence Watson', 'what-is-cannabis', 9, 'No');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(84, 'ENTERTAINMENT Best Outdoor Games for Kids Which Your Kids Will Loves to Play', 'entertainment-best-outdoor-games-for-kids-which-your-kids-will-loves-to-play', 'Best-Outdoor-Games-for-Kids-min.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Gaming is the ultimate source of entertainment for kids. They just love all sorts of gaming. However, most of us think that gaming means playing only online games. But, that is a false concept. It is more fun if you enjoy real-world games with friends. The joy and feeling are different than anything you can ask for.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Your kids will also learn how to make friends and share a relationship with them. Eventually, those will be your kids’ beautiful memories as well. Thus, we are mentioning the&nbsp;best outdoor games for kids. Although, you are free to think of new&nbsp;outdoor game ideas for kids.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You can inspire them to play these games with friends or family members. Even more, it will help them to grow&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/meditation-for-physical-and-mental-health\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">physically and mentally</a>. You can pick up different types of games from the large list given below. You need a different set of tools to play each game. So, look at the description to learn about the necessary tools and game rules. Let’s get into the most&nbsp;popular outdoor games for kids.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hopscotch\"></span>Hopscotch<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Hopscotch is a game you play by passing a marked area. You need chalk and a small rock or wood piece to play with. You can use any coloring item for the drawing. Besides, you can use any piece of thing as a throwing item. It is a great&nbsp;summer outdoor game for kids.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need to draw a path with different shapes</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Use the chalk or any coloring item to do so</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Kids have to throw their stone or wood pieces on the drawn shapes</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Pieces on the drawn shapes will be considered as blocked space</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Kids have to try jumping over the whole drawn blocks without landing on the blocked space</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Tag_with_a_Twist\"></span>Tag with a Twist<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This tagging game is a bit unique because of the unique rules. Each time you tag someone, you need to trade a color band to win the game.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need a set of color bands for this game. If there are 5 players, then you need 5 types of color bands for each player</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">After selecting the leader, he needs to tag other players</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">When you tag someone, you can trade one of your bands with the tagged player</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Then the tagged player has to be the leader and tag someone else</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The first player to collect all band colors is the winner</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Capture_the_Flag\"></span>&nbsp;Capture the Flag<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Capture the flag is one of the&nbsp;best outdoor games for kids. It is also perfect for team play. Kids will learn how to communicate and work as a team.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-3453 size-full\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Outdoor-Games-for-Kids-min.jpg\" alt=\"Outdoor Games for Kids is very important because its help to develop their mental growth\" width=\"500\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Outdoor-Games-for-Kids-min.jpg 500w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Outdoor-Games-for-Kids-min-250x300.jpg 250w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">This game needs two teams</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Each team can contain any number of players (usually 6)</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Each team will have a flag</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The goal is to capture the opponent’s flag and return it to your base</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Players have to freeze if an enemy touches them</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">An ally can save them by touching back</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kick_the_Can\"></span>Kick the Can<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Kick the Can is a pretty similar&nbsp;tagging game&nbsp;to Capture the flag. It is also a game where many kids can play together.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need a can and open space to play the game</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Put the can in the middle of the space</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">One kid has to be the guard</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Select the guard by rock-paper-scissor or any other method</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">All the other kids have to hide after a countdown</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Hidden kids have to kick the can</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The guard player can tag the hidden kids, and they have to freeze</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Freeze kids can be saved if any other kid touch them</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The kid who kicks the can first is the winner, but the guard kid wins if all the hidden kids are tagged</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"SPUD\"></span>SPUD<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">SPUD is another fun game for kids to play together. A lot of kids can join in this game. All you need is a ball to play it. Any type of ball would do the job.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">One kid has to throw the ball upward</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The kid has to shout out one player name from the rest</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Only that player is allowed to grab the ball</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">When the selected kid grabs the ball, he has to shout “SPUD.”</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Then all the other kids have to freeze</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The selected kid has to hit the ball to any frozen kid</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The losing kid has to throw the ball upward for the next round</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The first one to get 4 hits loses the game</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Disc_Golf_Games\"></span>Disc Golf Games<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Kids with a bit of athletic interest enjoy Disk Golf Games. In this game, throwing a disc to hit something earns you a point.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need a hoop, stand, or ball</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Mark a throwing point with a circle</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Players have to throw the disc when someone lifts the hoop</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">For other hitting points, they have to hit the stand or ball with a disc</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Each successful encounter grants one point</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The first player to earn 4 points is the winner</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ghost_in_the_Graveyard\"></span>Ghost in the Graveyard<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Here is another interesting&nbsp;outdoor game for kids. It is a tagging game, and the rules are quite simple.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">This game needs a base that is considered a safe spot</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">A number of kids can play while one of them has to be the ghost</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Kids stay in the safe spot and do a countdown</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The ghost has to hide by the time</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Everyone leaves the safe spot and start looking for the ghost</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">If someone finds the ghost, then he has to shout “ghost in the graveyard.”</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Everyone has to run toward the safe spot upon hearing the call</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">If the ghost can tag someone, then he will be the next ghost</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">If everyone reaches the safe spot, then the last person to reach becomes the next ghost</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sardines\"></span>Sardines<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Sardines are a bit different, which can be called a reverse tag game. It is a bit funnier, which your kids may love more than regular tagging games.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Any number of players can play this game (Usually 6-7)</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">One has to take the lead who will hide</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The rest of the kids will do a countdown and let the lead kid hide by the time</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">After the countdown, everyone has to find out the leading kid</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Instead of shouting, whoever finds the kid has to hide with them</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The kid to find the hideout will be the next leading kid to hide</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Red_Light_Green_Light\"></span>Red Light, Green Light<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This game requires several kids, at least 5-6. It is more like a command following game which is really fun for kids.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">This game needs a kid as a leader</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">There will be two-color points (green and red light)</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The kid will command other kids by calling it “green light” and “red light.”</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">When the command is “green light,” kids have to run toward a fixed point</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">For “red light,” they have to go for the redpoint</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The winner will be the next leader</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Red_Rover\"></span>Red Rover<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This game needs a bit of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/how-to-increase-strength\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">physical strength</a>. Although, kids love to play such games with lots of other kids.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">This game needs two teams with an equal number of players</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Each team has to form a line</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">One team will shout out red rover and mention one player’s name from the other team</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The mentioned kid has to try to break through the line</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">If the kid succeed in breaking through, then they can take one of the players to their team</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">If the kid can’t break through, then they have to join the opponent team</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The game continues until one single line formed</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Jump_Rope_Copycat\"></span>Jump Rope Copycat<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Jumping over ropes is one of the most popular games for kids. Among all the jump rope games, it is really popular. It is more like copying each other. This is really one of the easiest outdoor games for kids.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need at least two kids to play this game</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The more players you have, there better</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">One player has to show a trick with the rope, and another one has to copy it</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">If the kid fails to do so, then the next kid will try</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The game continues until only one kid is left</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Pickleball\"></span>Pickleball<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is a similar game to tennis, but the rules and equipment are more flexible. So, your kids will enjoy this a lot.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need at least 2 kids to play the game</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Having 4 kids make the game more enjoyable</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Solid racquets and plastic ball is necessary</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You also need stands to set up the net</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The team that gets 11 points first become the winner</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sharks_and_Minnows\"></span>Sharks and Minnows<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This is one of the most&nbsp;fun outdoor games for kids. Probably, this game is going to keep your kid busy with their friends. This game needs as many players as you can have.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">One kid has to be the shark, and the kid will stand in the center of a circle</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need to draw a big circle around it</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">All the other kids will stay out of that line, and they are the minnows</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Upon the shark’s calling, minnows will try to reach on the other side</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">If the shark tag anyone, then the kid will become a shark and try to tag other kids</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The game will continue until everyone becomes the shark</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Soccer\"></span>Soccer<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">There is no need to define soccer. It is not only the most favorite game for kids but also perfect for their growth. Soccer gives fun and builds physical improvement over time. Besides, a lot of kids can play it together. During the class break, soccer is one of the great&nbsp;outdoor games for kids at school.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need a soccer ball, two goal posts (with or without a net)</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">A lot of kids can play together, but you need to divide them into the same number of players</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Each team has to try and score as many goals as possible</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Most scoring team will be the winner</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kickball\"></span>Kickball<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Kickball is a similar game to baseball. But, you need to play with a soccer or rubber ball. Moreover, you need to kick the ball instead of hitting them like a baseball.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need to draw a long distant marking</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Each marking holds a fixed point</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Kids can play individually or as a team</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Each kid has to kick the ball from a fixed spot</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Each kick gives a point depending on the reach point</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The one scores the highest, or the team that scores the most point is the winner</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Football\"></span>Football<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Football is similar to soccer. However, American soccer refers to global football. As for American football, it refers to playing the soccer game with kicking and carrying. Although, it has a professional career. So, it needs a lot of physical equipment. It is not the&nbsp;best outdoor game for kids.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Each team need a fixed number of players</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Both sides of the fields should have a line</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Kicking or carrying the ball beyond that line gives a point</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The highest point-earning team will be the winner</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Crayon_Rubbing\"></span>Crayon Rubbing<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Crayon Rubbing is a fun art game for kids. Kids learn how to draw different objects and enjoy coloring them. Kids can play it indoors and outdoor, while most kids love to do it at home. That makes it one of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/best-indoor-games-for-kids/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">most suitable&nbsp;indoor games for kids</a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Take colorful objects like leaves, fabric, coins, plain arts, shapes and so on</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Put a white paper on them and rub with the crayon paper</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Let your kids change color and paper to experience new arts</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Basketball\"></span>Basketball<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Basketball is one of the amazing&nbsp;outdoor games for kids. They love to throw different things here and there. So, basketball is perfect for satisfying their entertainment.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Playing Instructions</span></p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need to set up the baskets at a suitable height for kids</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Use light ball for kids</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Playing as a team is more fun, so divide the kids into two teams</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">There should be two baskets for two teams</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Every team has to through the ball into the basket, and the opponent has to defend it</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The team that scores the most points is the winner</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Bottom_Line\"></span>The Bottom Line<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The best outdoor games for kids&nbsp;are the games that they enjoy the most. There are a lot of games for kids. But, different kids have different tastes. So, if you see they are not interested in a game, then try another. Inspire them to play as a team and share the moments with others. Tagging games, expression copy, command following, soccer, basketball, drawing, and similar games are the best for kids.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Some games are not just for fun. They also help a kid to grow mentally and physically. So, playing games is also a path of growth for kids. Follow our given list to learn new games and their rules. As an alternative, you can also try some of the&nbsp;best indoor games for kids. Make sure to encourage your kids to play. If possible, participate with them as well.</p>', 18, '3', '2021-11-15 07:53:09', '2021-11-08 01:54:02', '2021-12-08 05:36:46', '11/08/2021 1:53 PM', 'Marcos Heredia', 'best-outdoor-games-for-kids', 3, 'No');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(85, 'Best Indoor Games for Kids to Play Together', 'best-indoor-games-for-kids-to-play-together', 'Best-Indoor-Games-for-Kids.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If your kids are bored being indoors, then why not try some fun games? There are a lot of indoor games that you can let the kids enjoy with family members and friends. We will mention some of the best indoor games for kids and&nbsp;adults.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Our childhood was full of amazing little games that we played indoors. When there wasn’t such influence and growth of social media, those games were the best thing we got. Not only are they enjoyable, but also pretty easy to get into. So, kids or adults, anyone can enjoy together. We have a huge mixed list where some games are common, and some are uncommon. Thus, it is a great opportunity for you to learn some new games and try them up.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">You should understand that games for kids are&nbsp;meant to inspire or encourage them. It is not only about fun but also getting them into new and interesting things. Kids love to discover new things. It would be even more appealing if they could learn through different games. Building, creating, keeping up with friends are part of the growth. As we are mentioning a large game list, you can find a lot of them suitable for your kids. Make sure to provide enough time for the kids. It will help you to build a deeper connection with them through these cheerful events. Let’s get into the games and their instructions real quick.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Pitching_Pennies\"></span>Pitching Pennies<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Pitching pennies is a simple game with coins. In this game, you just have to throw coins. Usually, two players compete against each other. You can add more people to make it even more fun.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Marker or anything to draw the boundary</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Pennies/ any currency coin</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Fresh floor if you want a bit of fairness</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Players have to throw coins to the wall.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You have to get the coin as close as possible to the wall.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Draw a boundary/ throwing point.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Give a fixed number of coins to each player.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">After each round’s throw, check the winner.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The winner of every round takes all the other coins.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Usually, it goes for five rounds.</li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3435\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Indoor-Games-for-Kids.jpg\" alt=\"Best Indoor Games for Kids\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Indoor-Games-for-Kids.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Indoor-Games-for-Kids-300x188.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Indoor-Games-for-Kids-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Balancing_Beam\"></span>Balancing Beam<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is a simple game of reaching from one corner to another over a plain surface. Usually, it is too easy for adults but more fun for kids. Besides, it is a type of exercise as well. That makes it one of the top indoor exercise games for kids.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-2\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Colored tape or marker</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Plain space</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-2\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need to mark or use tape to draw lines over the plain space</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Make sure to use different colors for the lines</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Each color has a different rule</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">The Player has to run over the line and follow the rules depending on the color</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Falling over the line or making a wrong move fails the player</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"In_and_Out_Hangman\"></span>In and Out Hangman<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is a question/answer or trick play that perfectly suits kids. This game can be played in two ways.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-3\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Writing board or papers</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Set of questions/hints</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-3\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need to ask a set of questions to the player</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You may provide hints to guess the answer</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">A Player has seven chances to guess the answer</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Indoor_Bowling\"></span>Indoor Bowling<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Indoor Bowling is one of the best indoor games for kids. You just need to create a small bowling space and let them enjoy themselves.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-4\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Plain and straight space</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">10 empty cans, bottles, or stands</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Rubber, plastic, or softball (tennis)</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Marker or spray</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-4\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Prepare a straight and plain surface with a closed side</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Place the bottles or cans accordingly</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Roll the ball and smash the cans</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Let the kid arrange bottles after every round</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Sock_Toss\"></span>Sock Toss<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This game is similar to basketball but uses socks and a basket. This is one of the ultimate fun indoor games for kids.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-5\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">A little or medium space</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Socks</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Bucket</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-5\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You have to roll the sock to turn it into a ball</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Throw the sock into the bucket</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Move the bucket a bit further after each turn</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">You can set a score goal and the first one to do it is the winner</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Pictionary\"></span>Pictionary<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Pictionary is one of my most favorite celebrity games. So, there is no need to mention how cool it is for kids.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-6\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Drawing board</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Question sets</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-6\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need to draw something</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Ask the player to guess the word depending on the picture</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">You can do it otherwise as well</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Puzzles\"></span>Puzzles<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Undoubtedly, puzzles are the best game for kids. Not only it entertains them, but it also helps to unlock more intelligence. Besides, there are a lot of varieties. So, you can go for any puzzle that your kids seem to like.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-7\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Puzzle pieces</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The puzzle can be a picture or word</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-7\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Let the kids know what&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.melissaanddoug.com/blogpost?postId=choosing-puzzles-for-your-child\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">type of puzzle</a>&nbsp;they are given</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Make sure to explain how to play with them</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">If they are not interested, then change the puzzle with something new</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Indoor_Obstacle_Course\"></span>Indoor Obstacle Course<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The indoor obstacle course is not only fun for kids but also pets as well. It is rather a fun thing to do for kids. They do love to mess up a lot of things. These games are highly active indoor games for kids.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-8\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need different types of obstacles like chairs, tables, stands, blankets, balls, tools</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Softcover for extra protection</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-8\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">You need to choose a couple of obstacles that will not be harmful to kids</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Make sure to check the obstacles</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Place the obstacles in different shape</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Reward them after completing an obstacle course successfully and unsuccessfully</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Follow_the_leader\"></span>Follow the leader<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This is rather an impressive play for kids. Even a lot of kids can play this game together. It is one of the best indoor party games for kids.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-9\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">A set of activities, gestures, or expressions to do</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">A bigger place if there are more kids</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-9\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">A group of kids has to follow one kid as their leader</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">They have to follow the set of acts as leader</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">There is no winner or loser in this game</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Continue the following process with a new leader in each round</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Card_Games\"></span>Card Games<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Several types of card games are really fun for kids. But, you should not give them complicated card games for adults. UNO, color cards, and portrait cards are really great. It will be even better to let them play pokemon, Digimon, or similar types of cards. They are the best card games for kids.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-10\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Suitable cards for kids (color or number matching, monster play or power play)</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Select a number of players</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-10\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Select the suitable cards for kids</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Distribute a fixed number of cards</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">The one who wins most rounds become the winner</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ice_Tower_Excavation\"></span>Ice Tower Excavation<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This game is highly popular during&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.climate.gov/news-features/climate-qa/does-global-warming-mean-it%E2%80%99s-warming-everywhere\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">warm climates</a>. It is more like building and breaking ice blocks. The game is more enjoyable as there will be toys inside.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-11\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Water Container</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Different types of toys</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-11\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Put water and toys into the container</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Let it be frozen</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Take out the block and melt it using salt or warm water</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Building_a_Fort\"></span>Building a Fort<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It is one of the most favorite games for kids. A lot of kids love to build something. It uncovers their intelligence and also innovative creativities. You should give the kids enough opportunities to enjoy this game.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-12\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Any possible building tool</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Card</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Box</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Pillow</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Blanket</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Toys</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Tapes</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Ropes</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-12\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Teach them the basics of building a fort</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Add one thing with another to build a boundary and base</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Add one thing over another to build a fort</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Let kids do it together or individually to compete with others</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dominoes\"></span>Dominoes<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Domino’s play is not only popular among kids but also for adults. A lot of kids and adults are addicted to it pretty dearly. Many world records are there. You kid can enjoy a lot of things out of it.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-13\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Dominoes pieces</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-13\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Teach the kid how to build a shape with dominoes</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Let them build anything as they want</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Read\"></span>Read<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Reading can be the most amusing thing for growing kids. So, getting them into the habit is surely important.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-14\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Any storybook or poem</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Visual or only text</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-14\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Inspire your kid to enjoy the stories or poem</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Let them read or recite</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Inspire them by reading or reciting for them</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Listening_Game\"></span>Listening Game<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This is a game that builds from deep interaction with kids. Through the listening process, you need to build a close relationship with them.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Things_You_Will_Need-15\"></span>The Things You Will Need<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Something interesting to read that will attract kids</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Playing_Instructions-15\"></span>Playing Instructions<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Readout some interesting stories or poems for your kids</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Try different stories or poems if they don’t get interested</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Bottom_Line\"></span>The Bottom Line<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Games are fun and an important part of our childhood. So, you should give your kids a lot of games to enjoy. There are many games like expression copy, building shapes, or creating ice. Even more, there is something like enjoying stories, reciting poems, and so on. You can even let them do interesting things like wearing costumes, dancing, and singing. During their time at home, they will not be bored. Because of that, we mentioned the best indoor games for kids.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">These activities can also unlock a child’s hidden talent and intelligence. Besides, playing with family and friends builds a strong bond and connection. So, make sure to let your kids enjoy a lot of games. If you can, join in the game as well. It will be even more fun for them. As an alternative, you can try&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/best-outdoor-games-for-kids/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">some outdoor games for kids</a>&nbsp;as&nbsp;well.</p>', 18, '3', '2021-11-15 07:53:20', '2021-11-08 01:57:21', '2021-11-28 05:27:13', '11/08/2021 1:56 PM', 'Marcos Heredia', 'best-indoor-games-for-kids', 1, 'No');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `title`, `slug`, `image`, `description`, `category_id`, `user_id`, `published_date`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `posting_date`, `author_name`, `permalink`, `read_count`, `featured`) VALUES
(86, 'How to Get Disney Plus On TVs: All In One Service', 'how-to-get-disney-plus-on-tvs-all-in-one-service', 'Disney-Plus-TV.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">At the end of 2019, it began broadcasting in the United States; in March of this year, it made its triumphant arrival in Spain and other European countries; and since November 18, 2020, it is finally available in Latin America. Disney Plus, in a nutshell, is a streaming service that you can enjoy on your smart TV, computer, tablet, and other devices compatible with this type of transmission.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Disney+ is a streaming video service owned by Disney. It is similar to services like Netflix, Apple TV+, and Amazon Prime Video in that it is a video-on-demand service. You will find yourself with a library of movies and TV shows that can be watched anytime and on a wide range of devices. It was announced in September 2017 and finally launched last November 12, 2019. Keep reading to learn how to get Disney Plus on TV.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Best_Ways_To_Get_Disney_Plus_On_Different_Smart_TVs\"></span>The Best Ways To Get Disney Plus On Different Smart TVs<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"On_Roku_TV\"></span>On Roku TV<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Disney+ is the exclusive and permanent destination for the most complete and best selection of Disney, Pixar, Marvel, Star Wars, and National Geographic movies and series. As well as original productions. Also is the only streaming service where available Disney, Pixar, Marvel, and Star Wars movies can be accessed. The long-awaited Disney+, the Walt Disney Company’s subscription streaming service, has arrived on the Roku platform.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3082\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Roku-TV.jpg\" alt=\"Roku TV\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Roku-TV.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Roku-TV-300x188.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Roku-TV-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">By subscribing to Disney+, users will stream ad-free and on-demand on up to four devices simultaneously. And also add up to seven individual profiles. Subscribers will also enjoy personalized recommendations. Parents will create Kids Profiles, which offer an easy-to-navigate, kid-friendly interface where they can find age-appropriate content. Disney+ can be downloaded from the Roku Channel Store. You can also find it in the movies category on the Roku home screen.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"On_Samsung_Smart_TV\"></span>On Samsung Smart TV<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Disney+ is compatible with 2016 and later Samsung TVs that support HD video and use the Tizen OS. Unfortunately, Disney+ is not compatible with Samsung TVs that use the Orsay OS or have a built-in web browser. For the best experience, a high-speed internet connection is recommended. In addition, a smart TV with the latest version of the operating system is recommended.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3083\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Samsung-Smart-TV.jpeg\" alt=\"Samsung Smart TV\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Samsung-Smart-TV.jpeg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Samsung-Smart-TV-300x188.jpeg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Samsung-Smart-TV-768x480.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">For the best quality Disney+ experience, all components must support high-bandwidth digital content, including HDMI cables. Check with the manufacturer for specific details on the capabilities of your devices.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"On_Sony_Smart_TV\"></span>On Sony Smart TV<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Disney Plus or Disney+ is a new streaming service (launched in November 2019) that brings together many movies and TV shows. From Disney, Marvel, Star Wars, Pixar, 20th Century Fox, and National Geographic. With compatible devices, it lets you stream everything from Disney Walt Studios.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3084\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Sony-Smart-TV.jpg\" alt=\"Sony Smart TV\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Sony-Smart-TV.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Sony-Smart-TV-300x188.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Sony-Smart-TV-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The service also allows offline streaming. So, you can download and stream your favorite Disney movies in offline mode anytime, anywhere. The Disney Plus service is accessible on various devices and streaming consoles, including the Sony Smart TV and smartphones and tablets. Since Sony Smart TVs run on the Android operating system, you can easily download and use the Disney+ app. The best way to watch Disney Plus on your Sony Smart TV is to install the standalone app. The Disney+ app can be easily downloaded from the Google Play Store.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"On_LG_Smart_TV\"></span>On LG Smart TV<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">LG TVs do offer a native app, but not for everyone. Only those using webOS version 3.0 or higher can access Disney+. Suppose your TV is recent or you have activated the option to install new updates automatically. In that case, you will probably have already seen how access to the service appears in the bottom bar of apps. In case not, go to the LG app store and click install.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3085\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/LG-Smart-TV.png\" alt=\"LG Smart TV\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/LG-Smart-TV.png 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/LG-Smart-TV-300x188.png 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/LG-Smart-TV-768x480.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If you have never accessed the LG Content Store before, don’t worry because it is not complicated at all. You have to use the search engine and type Disney. The application will appear on the screen, and as with any other app from any other store, hit install, and that’s it. In a matter of seconds and access all the benefits of the service, and if your TV supports 4K UHD and HDR content, you will also enjoy the best possible quality.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"On_Philips_Smart_TV\"></span>On Philips Smart TV<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Currently, not many intelligent TVs support Disney + directly. However, there are many platforms available to help you stream the service to your TV anyway. Unfortunately, if you want to get the service directly on your smart TV, you may encounter some problems. However, this is not a reason to worry.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3086\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Philips-Smart-TV.jpg\" alt=\"Philips Smart TV\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Philips-Smart-TV.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Philips-Smart-TV-300x188.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Philips-Smart-TV-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Some Philips intelligent TVs have a built-in Chromecast that should make it easy for you to cast Disney + from your smartphone or PC directly. However, even if your TV doesn’t have a built-in Chromecast, you can still get the dongle and follow the same process:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Get the Disney + app from Play Store (Android), App Store (iOS), or open the website from your Google Chrome web browser.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Open the Disney + app on your device.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Switch to Chromecast (HDMI input) on your Philips TV.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Press the “Stream” button on your app.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Choose your Philips TV from the list of available devices.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Your TV should mirror the Disney + screen.</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"On_Chromecast_Built-in_Smart_TV\"></span>On Chromecast Built-in Smart TV<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The first method is through the official Disney+ app for Android and iOS, as both versions can use Google’s Chromecast. In addition, you can also cast content from your computer using Google’s Chrome browser, which is also capable of taking advantage of Google Cast technology. Before choosing the content you want to watch, all you have to do is click on the Google Cast icon in the upper right corner of the screen. It is that icon in the shape of a screen with the WiFi symbol on the side.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">When you click on the Google Cast button, you will see a pop-up window Transfer to, which will list the devices compatible with this technology that you have turned on in your WiFi network. Here, click on the name of the Chromecast you have connected to your TV in the list to tell the app that this is where you want to send the content. All you need to do is choose the series or movie you want, and it will start playing on the TV. You can also start the playback before sending the content to Chromecast. Because when you are watching the series or movie, at the top right in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.slashgear.com/disney-plus-app-update-adds-important-playback-controls-23601271/\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">playback controls</a>, you will also have the Google Cast icon to start the sending process.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"On_TV_Using_A_Streaming_Device\"></span>On TV Using A Streaming Device<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This is one of the easiest and most popular ways. For this, you need to:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Open the Disney+ app.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Select the content you want to watch.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Choose VIEW.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Select the Chromecast logo at the top of the screen.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Choose the streaming device.</li></ul><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"On_Fire_TV_Or_Fire_Stick\"></span>On Fire TV Or Fire Stick<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The way to proceed is straightforward since you have to download the Disney+ app. However, you won’t see it on the main screen, and if you don’t update your device first, you may not even see it in the list of apps to install.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">When you turn on your Fire TV Stick, it is expected that on the main screen, you will not see the Disney+ application. This doesn’t mean that you can’t use it, but you will need to install it first. To do this, in the top menu, go to the Apps section. Once in the Apps section, find and click on the Disney+ app, which should appear directly in the Featured tab or the Entertainment category.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"On_Apple_TV\"></span>On Apple TV<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3087\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple-TV.jpg\" alt=\"Apple TV\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple-TV.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple-TV-300x188.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Apple-TV-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Thanks to the cooperation between Disney and Apple, we can now enjoy Disney+ content directly on the Apple TV app on our iPad, iPhone, Mac, or Apple TV. Unlike&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/best-music-streaming-service\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">other streaming providers</a>, the Disney+ content does not appear, at least for now, as a channel in the Apple TV app but as direct integration. We can link both services through the invitation email Apple has sent or when trying to play Disney+ content from the app. Once this step is completed, the Disney+ content will appear directly in the app, as Apple TV+.</p><h3 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.3; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 25px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"On_Panasonic_Smart_TV\"></span>On Panasonic Smart TV<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Panasonic Smart TV devices do not yet have the option to watch Disney Plus directly. But as you saw with other devices, you can access Disney Plus via other devices. You can stream Disney Plus via Chromecast or whatever option you find easiest!</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Which_Devices_Are_Not_Supported_For_Disney_Plus\"></span>Which Devices Are Not Supported For Disney Plus?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Thanks to its wide range of exclusive content designed for all audiences, it is nowadays one of the most downloaded apps on Smart TVs. With Disney+, it is possible to enjoy famous sagas such as Star Wars, Toy Story, Cars, X-Men, or Iron Man.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Also, of course, there are classics available for the little ones, such as The Lion King, Snow White, The Little Mermaid, etc. And of course, here, you will be able to see the upcoming exclusive releases made by Disney and other production partners such as Avatar 2, among others. If you have any of these devices, you will not use them to enjoy the Disney+ catalog. Check here if your cell phone, tablet, computer, or TV meet the technical requirements of the platform.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The question is which devices are compatible since they are the majority. Here is the list of compatible ones, and if yours is not, it will not be compatible,</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Roku</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Amazon Fire and Amazon Fire TV</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Apple TV</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\"><a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/apple-airplay-2\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">Apple AirPlay</a></li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Android TV</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Chromecast</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">LG WebOS Smart TVs</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">Samsung Tizen Smart TVs</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">Sony Android-based smart TVs</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_To_Use_Group_Watch_On_Disney_Plus\"></span>How To Use Group Watch On Disney Plus?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Group Watch will work across the entire Disney+ catalog, so you can organize a “<em>virtual get-together</em>” regardless of the title you want to play. Its operation is effortless: choose a movie, series, or documentary, click on the Group Watch button (the icon with three people) and send the link to the users.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Bottom_Line\"></span>The Bottom Line<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Disney has been one of the entertainment giants for years and can now boast Pixar animation or the famous Disney Princesses and the entire Star Wars catalog, all the Marvel content or exclusive series and movies that come to its streaming platform. Disney Plus works since November 12 works in the United States, Canada, and the Netherlands. Since November 19, 2019, it works in Australia, Puerto Rico, and New Zealand.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In Spain, it has been operating since March 24, 2020, as in other European countries. It has also been available in Latin America since November 2020. Expansion in Asia will be in 2021. It is a comfortable interface similar to that of platforms that we already use as Netflix or HBO. When accessing Disney Plus, we can choose between several profiles (which we can customize with 200 Disney avatars, as it could not be otherwise). Each one has recommendations, a series history, and favorites.</p>', 18, '3', '2021-11-15 07:53:37', '2021-11-08 02:04:57', '2021-11-25 03:33:30', '11/08/2021 2:04 PM', 'Marcos Heredia', 'how-to-get-disney-plus-on-tv', 1, 'Yes'),
(87, 'Why Messi Leaves FC Barcelona: Global Impact', 'why-messi-leaves-fc-barcelona-global-impact', 'Messi-Leaves-FC-Barcelona.jpg', '<p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">That day that you thought would never come, or at least not in the short term, finally came true this Sunday. A very emotional Lionel Messi said goodbye to the Club of his life. Even you don’t believe it yet, Messi leaves FC Barcelona. He had to make an effort to hold back the tears before he could begin to speak. He stood before the press, his family, the Barcelona management, his teammates. He began to explain the reasons for his departure.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">A departure that, every time he had the opportunity, he made it clear that he never imagined. Although he admitted that in the last summer market, after the famous burofax, he was determined to leave the Club, this time he felt convinced and sure of his continuity:&nbsp;<em>“What is clear to me is that I did everything possible. Laporta said that it was not possible because of the League issue. Still, I heard many things said about me, why I did not continue. But I can assure you that I also did everything I could to continue, to stay”.</em></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">He even acknowledged that the contract was already closed and with a significant salary reduction. His salary had been reduced by 50%. I had closed the contract, and then nothing more was asked of me. It was believed that it was said that I was asking for 30% more; that’s a lie, that didn’t happen, Messi said. According to him, he did everything possible, but it was not possible.<br>And to finish clearing up doubts and cut off speculation, he also referred to the famous photo he took a few days ago with the PSG players. Neymar, Leandro Paredes, Angel Di María, and Marco Verratti, all players of Paris Saint Germain, would be his next destination. He clarified that it was a meeting with Neymar and Di Maria arranged at the Copa America.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Why_is_Messi_Leaving_FC_Barcelona\"></span>Why is Messi Leaving FC Barcelona?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3628 aligncenter\" src=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Why-is-Messi-Leaving-FC-Barcelona.jpg\" alt=\"Why is Messi Leaving FC Barcelona\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Why-is-Messi-Leaving-FC-Barcelona.jpg 800w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Why-is-Messi-Leaving-FC-Barcelona-300x188.jpg 300w, https://sunbizweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/Why-is-Messi-Leaving-FC-Barcelona-768x480.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block; margin: 20px auto;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">When everything seemed to be on track for Messi to sign a new contract, everything turned upside down. These are the reasons for Leo Messi’s departure from Barcelona and why the Argentine star has left. The end of Leo Messi’s glorious era at Barcelona seems to be closer than ever to come.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Everything seemed on track and closed for Leo Messi to sign his new contract with Barcelona. However, the bombshell exploded on Thursday afternoon. Barcelona communicated the departure of its captain due to the severe economic problems of the entity. These prevent them from registering him for next season.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">All even though an agreement had already been reached between the two parties to continue. This is explained in the Club’s press release. Although you still don’t believe it, Messi leaves FC Barcelona.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Barcelona had been moving all summer to make Leo Messi’s registration possible. The big obstacle was the salary cap. To do this, it has certified departures such as Aleña, Todibó, Junior Firpo, Trincao, Miranda, or Konrad. Movements that are not enough.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">In addition, from the azulgrana offices, a negotiation has been established with players like Sergi Roberto, Busquets, Piqué, or Jordi Alba to lower their salaries. But the income from sales and these salary reductions (which have not yet been agreed upon) is not enough. The pandemic has seriously affected Barcelona’s economic situation.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Camp Nou’s coffers have been seriously depleted with a 30 percent reduction in income. This, plus the abysmal economic policy of the board chaired by Josep Maria Bartomeu. That had the Club drowned with very high salaries among the staff and a liability that has the Club tied up.<br>His economic report reflects the delicate situation that the Club is going through in this aspect. The short-term debt amounts to 730 million euros, of which 126 million are outstanding payments to other clubs for transfers made. Total liabilities amounted to 1,173 million.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">LaLiga regulations require that the wage bill be less than the amount obtained from the difference between the Club’s income and the Club’s expenses unrelated to the workforce. This difference must be used to pay first and second-team players, technical staff, and the annual amortization of signings.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Since some players have signed such long contracts, the problem is that their amortization continues to be paid. Pjanic, Coutinho, Braithwaite, Griezmann, Dembélé, De Jong are some of these cases. These amortizations further complicate Messi’s renewal.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Beyond the delicate economic situation, Leo Messi values having a competitive squad that allows him to fight for everything in his last years as a professional. Last summer, he did not understand the departure of Luis Suárez, mainly because of his behavior. The Uruguayan played a vital role in the Atlético de Madrid title shows that he could have been a key player at Barcelona.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This summer, the arrival of Agüero, a close friend of Messi and a pivotal move to convince the Argentinian, has been closed. In addition, Memphis and Eric Garcia have also strengthened the team. However, we are back to the same thing. They are players who are not guaranteed to be able to be registered. That uncertainty only creates more insecurity.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">This season Barcelona won the Copa del Rey. Still, the reality is that they have not competed in Europe for several seasons and have had some terrible defeats. Roma, Liverpool, the 8-2 defeat of Bayern Munich, this season PSG. Messi knows that to win the Champions League again, Barcelona needed the arrival of top players, which is impossible.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_Has_FC_Barcelona_said_on_Messi_Leaving\"></span>What Has FC Barcelona said on Messi Leaving?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">News of the century: Lionel Messi will not remain in Barcelona. The Club announces this in a press release. It went around the world in a matter of minutes. The Argentine ten could not close his renewal, and his future is uncertain.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Last week the news began to circulate. But nobody wanted to risk taking it for granted. Until the Club issued a statement in which they took the facts for granted, in the communiqué, you could read what it said. Messi leaves FC Barcelona because of financial fair play.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The Club stated that it was due to economic and structural reasons. In addition, it blamed La Liga for this significant drop. For regulations that have to do with contracts and so on, Messi leaves FC Barcelona. He also reported that the two parties wanted to reach an agreement but could not. The Club communicated that both parties intended to continue. But due to FC Barcelona’s economic problems and financial fair play, it was not possible.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><em>“Despite having reached an agreement between FC Barcelona and Leo Messi and with the clear intention of both parties to sign a new contract today, it could not be formalized due to economic and structural obstacles. Given this situation, Lionel Messi will not continue in FC Barcelona. Both parties deeply regret that in the end, it will not be possible to fulfill the wishes of both the player and the Club.”</em></p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_Did_Messi_Said_in_His_Farewell_in_Barcelona\"></span>What Did Messi Said in His Farewell in Barcelona?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Messi’s farewell press conference was dramatic all around the world. The Argentinean was very emotional and, at times, could not hold back his tears. Accompanied by his wife and children, Messi said goodbye to FC Barcelona. Also,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://sunbizweekly.com/lionel-messi-join-paris-saint-germain\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">he confirms that PSG is a real possibility</a>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It was through a not very long press conference in which he explained the reasons. Reasons that are already public knowledge and that the Club had previously stated. The famous financial fair play.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Messi was accompanied by his family, his teammates, managers, and employees of the Club. It was a very emotional conference in which the ten did not hold back. Both at the beginning and the end, Messi let some tears fall. And after the applause of all those present, Messi put an end to an era that seemed endless.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">If there was one thing present at the ceremony, it was thanks. Messi did not stop thanking the fans, his teammates, and all who were part of his stay in Barcelona.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Shortly after his press conference, La Pulga dedicated a few thanks to the Barcelona fans on his personal Instagram account.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_Did_Lionel_Messi_Achieve_at_Barcelona\"></span>What Did Lionel Messi Achieve at Barcelona?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Messi leaves FC Barcelona. The Argentinean says goodbye to the institution where he was born. Lionel Messi leaves a legacy for the history of Barcelona. With the Club, he achieved a significant number of titles. He marked a before and after for the Catalan institution. Undoubtedly, every time we hear the name Barcelona, the first thing we imagine is Messi.<br>He has a record number of titles for any soccer player, winning tournaments of great importance on several occasions. Here is a review of all of Lionel Messi’s titles with FC Barcelona.</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">10 La Liga championships: 2004-05, 2005-06, 2008-09, 2009-10, 2010-11, 2012-13, 2014-15, 2015-16, 2017-18, 2018-19.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">7 Copa del Rey: 2008-09, 2011-12, 2014-15, 2015-16, 2016-17, 2017-18, 2020-21.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">4 UEFA Champions League: 2005-06, 2008-09, 2008-09, 2010-11, 2014-15.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">3 Club World Cups: 2009-10, 2011-12, 2015-16.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">3 UEFA Super Cups: 2009-10, 2011-12, 2015-16.</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">8 Spanish Super Cups: 2005-06, 2006-07, 2009-10, 2010-11, 2011-12, 2013 14, 2016-17, 2018-19.2¨</li></ul><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Lionel_Messi_Historic_Record_Breaker_at_FC_Barcelona\"></span>Lionel Messi Historic Record Breaker at FC Barcelona<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">The bombshell of Messi’s non-renewal at Barcelona shook the whole world. August 5, 2021, will go down in history as the end of one of soccer’s most powerful love stories. Leo will no longer wear the Barcelona shirt that filled him with so much glory. Many wonder what will happen to his future, but here you look back at all the records he set at Barça.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Twenty years have passed. A relationship that seemed unbreakable, but that was wearing out as the summers went by. Today, the thin thread that resisted with strength and had a tendency to rebuild itself ended up breaking. From September 17, 2000, to today, Thursday: all Leo’s records broke at Barcelona.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Undisputed leader on and off the field, Leo is a fan of Barcelona. He is the player who has played the most games with his shirt. On March 15 of this year, he equaled Xavi’s maximum number of appearances in the institution, with 767 matches. Then, he was alone: he reached 778.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">He is also the Club’s and Spanish soccer’s all-time top scorer (474). With Barça, he scored a total of 672 goals, which made more than one person delirious. There are goals for all tastes and colors: left-footed, right-footed, headed, with the hip and with the hand, ahem.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">He even scored with the chest! Not to mention the delightful free-kicks he has sent into the net. The last one? In the 2-1 defeat against Celta on the last day of&nbsp;<em>“La Liga.”</em></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">He also managed to surpass Pelé at Santos as the top scorer in a single team. The Brazilian star scored 643 goals for Santos, but Lionel managed to score 672 goals.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Leo’s record at Barcelona is unprecedented. With the Catalan club, he won 35 titles. No more, no less. A gigantic figure that makes his figure even bigger. He is the greatest champion in the history of the Club.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_Will_Happen_Next\"></span>What Will Happen Next?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Messi’s future is not entirely uncertain. It seems that all roads lead to PSG in France. All the media are saying the same thing: Messi is going to be a new PSG player.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Some time ago, a photo with 4 of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://bleacherreport.com/psg-players-on-social-media\" style=\"color: rgb(221, 51, 51); position: relative; border-bottom: 2px solid black; outline: 0px !important;\">PSG players was on social media</a>. However, he clarifies that this had no ulterior motives. But the economic power of the French Club and its relationship with Di Maria and Neymar facilitates everything.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">It seemed impossible to see Messi with any other jersey than Barcelona’s. But everything indicates that it will be so. Lionel Messi will surely be a PSG player, trying to win a new Champions League.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Bottom_Line\"></span>The Bottom Line<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Messi, whose contract expired on June 30, had planned to remain at his lifelong Club. But Barcelona could not make the renewal official due to the financial fair play proposed by the Spanish league.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Messi held a press conference at Camp Nou, which he entered into tears. His wife Antonela Roccuzzo, his three children, president Joan Laporta, the professional squad, and the local and international press.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">Lionel said that&nbsp;<em>“he was convinced that he was going to stay at Barcelona.”</em>&nbsp;He shared a desire with his family, but he regretted that it could not materialize&nbsp;<em>“due to a league issue.”</em></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\">After 17 seasons in the professional squad, the Argentine star leaves with impressive statistics: 672 goals, 268 assists, 778 games, 35 titles, and 79 personal awards, including six Ballon d’Or awards.</p><h2 style=\"font-family: Poppins, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 30px;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"References\"></span>References<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h2><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.6em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.8em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85); font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17.0001px;\"><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;\">https://www.msn.com/en-us/sports/soccer/messi-leaves-barcelona-5-key-quotes-from-farewell-press-conference/ar-AAN4yvY?ocid=msedgntp</li><li style=\"margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: initial;\">https://www.msn.com/en-us/sports/soccer/lionel-messi-in-tears-as-he-confirms-barcelona-departure-in-tv-address-i-never-imagined-having-to-say-goodbye/ar-AAN4iFf</li></ul>', 18, '3', '2021-11-15 07:53:52', '2021-11-08 02:10:07', '2021-12-08 04:38:14', '11/08/2021 2:05 PM', 'James Trotta', 'why-messi-leaves-fc-barcelona', 7, 'No');

